\id MAT
\h MATYU
\toc1 Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim
\toc2 Matyu
\toc3 Mt
\mt1 Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim
\is1 Akar Faragha Zuim
\ip Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim, a 4 plan ak…®nafaribar faragha zui. Egha ak…®nafarir 4 plan kaba, da Iesus…®n akar aghuim m…®g…®a, egha dughiar Iesus nguazim…®n ikiava amir bizir otivizibagh eghari.
\ip Matyun ak…®nafarim, a Maria Iesus batezir dughiam…®n otivizir bizibagh egharava, egha ghua dughiar me Iesus m…®soghez…® an aremezim…®n tu. Egha a ua mozim…®n d…®kavigha, uan adarazi ategha God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabo.
\ip Ez…® bizir ekiar mam Matyu anekakaghasa, a kamak…®n, Iesus bizir God fom…®ra d…®k…®rizir akam…®n dagh amigha g…®fa. Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Ghurim…®n da osiriz…®, da iti. God akam ak…®righa ghaze, a Israelba ua me inis…® gumazitam amadaght…® a izam. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n en aka, Iesus a gumazir kamra. Egha Matyun ak…®nafarir otevir av…®rav…®rir mabar, akaba kamagh…®n en m…®g…®a ghaze, bizir Iesus amiziba, da bar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar God…®n akam n…®gha izir gumaziba fom…®ra m…®kemezir akabar m…®raram otogha g…®fa. N…® gans…® Matyu 1:22-23, 2:4-6, 2:14-15, 2:23, 4:13-16, 8:16-17, 12:15-21, 13:34-35, 21:2-5, 21:16, 26:24, 26:31, 26:54, 27:6-10.
\ip Ez…® bizir ekiar igharazir mam, Matyun ak…®nafarim a m…®gei, a God Bizibar Ativamin Dughiam m…®gei. God kamagh…®n ifonge, Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n a bar gumazamizibar at…®rivim…®n ikiasa, eght…® gumazamiziba bar an ifongiam…®n g…®n mangam.
\ip Ez…® Matyun ak…®nafarim…®n aven, Iesus m…®kemez…®r akar ruarir 5 pla, da iti. Faragha zuim, a sapta 5 ko 6 ko 7…®n iti, ez…® akar Iesus m…®ghs…®ar mam gis…®n ikia, m…®kemeziba an iti. Ez…® akar kam a guizbang…®ra God gumazamizibar arazibar en aka. Namba 2…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 10…®n iti. Kar akar Iesus uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngizim. Dughiar kam, me mang…®va Iesus…®n akam gumazamizir igharazibav k…®masa, ez…® Iesus me mang…® damuamin bizibav gei.
\ip Ez…® namba 3…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 13…®n iti, Iesus God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n gumazamizibav gei. Ez…® namba 4…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 18…®n iti, Iesus gumazamizir guizbang…®ra an suren gumazibar itir arazibar gun m…®gei. Egha namba 5…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 24 ko 25…®n iti, Iesus dughiar abuananam…®n bizibar gun m…®gei.
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam uab…®, gumazir ak…®nafarim osirizim…®n gun m…®kemezir puvat…®. Ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n ziar kam ini, Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim. Guizbang…®ra, me gumazir dag…®aba isir Matyu, a g…®n…®ghn…®si. (Mt. 9:9-13…®n gan.)
\c 1
\ms1 Iesus nguazir kam…®n oto
\mr (Sapta 1:1-4:16)
\s1 Iesus…®n inaziba ko ovavibar ziaba
\r (Luk 3:23-38)
\p 
\v 1 Kar Krais Iesus…®n inaziba ko ovavibar eghaghanim. Iesus a Devit…®n ovavim. Ez…® Devit Abraham…®n ovavim.
\v 2 Abraham Aisak…®n afeziam. Ez…® Aisak, Jekop…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jekop Juda ko an aveghbuabar afeziam.\f + \ft (1:2) Juda uan aveghbuaba ko, me Israel…®n ik…®zir 12 plan inaziba.\f*
\v 3 Ez…® Juda, Peres ko Seran afeziam. Aning…®n amebam Tamar. Ez…® Peres Hesron…®n afeziam, Ez…® Hezron, Ram…®n afeziam.
\v 4 Ez…® Ram Aminadap…®n afeziam, Ez…® Aminadap Nason…®n afeziam; Ez…® Nason Salmon…®n afeziam.
\v 5 Ez…® Salmon Boas…®n afeziam. An amebam Rahap. Ez…® Boas Obet…®n afeziam, an amebam Rut. Ez…® Obet Jesin afeziam, Ez…® Jesi Atrivim Devit…®n afeziam.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Devit Solomon…®n afeziam, an amebam Urian amuim.\f + \ft (1:6) Amizir ziar kagh otiviziba, Israelian amiziba puvat…®. Me Israel…®n gumazibar iti. Tamar ko Rahap aning Kenan…®n amizimning. Rut, a Moab…®n amizim. Betseba Solomon…®n amebam uab…®ra Israel…®n amizim. A faragha Urian ike, Uria Hitit…®n gumazim.\f*
\v 7 Ez…® Solomon Rehoboam…®n afeziam. Ez…® Rehoboam Abiyan afeziam, Ez…® Abiya Asan afeziam.
\v 8 Ez…® Asa Jehosafat…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jehosafat Jehoram…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jehoram Usian afeziam.
\v 9 Ez…® Usia Jotam…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jotam Ahas…®n afeziam. Ez…® Ahas Hesekian afeziam.
\v 10 Ez…® Hesekia Manasen afeziam. Ez…® Manase Emon…®n afeziam. Ez…® Emon Josaian afeziam.
\v 11 Ez…® Josaia Jehoiakin ko an aveghbuar mabar afeziam. Dughiar kam…®n Israelba ghua Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ghue.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® me Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ghuez…®, g…®n Jehoiakin Sealtiel…®n afeziam. Ez…® Sealtiel Serubabel…®n afeziam.
\v 13 Ez…® Serubabel Abiut…®n afeziam. Ez…® Abiut Eliakim…®n afeziam. Ez…® Eliakim Asor…®n afeziam.
\v 14 Ez…® Asor Sadok…®n afeziam. Ez…® Sadok Akim…®n afeziam. Ez…® Akim Eliut…®n afeziam.
\v 15 Ez…® Eliut Eleasar…®n afeziam. Ez…® Eleasar Matan…®n afeziam. Ez…® Matan Jekop…®n afeziam.
\v 16 Ez…® Jekop Josep…®n afeziam, a Marian pam.
\p Ez…® Maria Iesus bate, ez…® me ziar kam Krais a gat…®. A Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim.
\v 17 Kamagh…®n Abraham…®n dughiam…®n ikegha ghua Atrivim Devit…®n dughiam…®n tu, 14 plan ovaviba otifi. Ez…® Devit…®n dughiam…®n ikegha ghua dughiar Israelba Babilon…®n nguibam…®n Kalabus…®n ikezim, 14 plan ovaviba otifi. Ez…® dughiar me kalabus…®n ikezim…®n ikegha ghua God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, Krais…®n dughiam…®n tuzim, uaghan 14 plan ovaviba otifi.
\s1 Maria Krais Iesus bate, a God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim
\r (Luk 2:1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Krais Iesus otozir eghaghanimra kara, a God Uam e Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim. An amebam Maria, me Josep…®n ikiasa a ginaba. Egha aning t…®ghar uaning inigh ikiasava amima, Maria navim asangi. God…®n Duamra borim a gat…®.
\v 19 Ez…®ma Josep God…®n damazim derazir gumazim an averara Maria ataghraghasa n…®ghn…®si. An azenim…®n Maria aghums…®zim a dan…®ngan aghua.
\v 20 Egha a kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha itima Ekiam…®n ensel…®n mam irebam…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJosep, n…® Devit…®n ovavim, n…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® Maria inigh an ik…®. A navim asangizir borim, a God…®n Duam da ize.
\v 21 An otarim bateght…®ma, eght…® a uan gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh men akurvagham. Kamagh…®n n…® ziam Iesus a dat…®gh.‚Äù\f + \ft (1:21) Ziam Iesus Hibrun akam…®n bar rogh…®ra m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam, ‚ÄúEkiam, a gumazamiziba ua me iniamin gumazim.‚Äù Ziam Iesus Grigh…®n akam. Me Hibrun akam Iesus, Josua a gar…®si.\f*
\p 
\v 22 Arazir kabanagh kamagh…®n otiva, egha God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®raram otifi.
\v 23 A kamagh m…®keme, ‚ÄúAmizir gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zim navim asegh, otaritam bategham. Eght…® me ziar kam Emanuel a dar…®gham, ziar kam…®n m…®ngarim kara, ‚ÄòGod e ko iti.‚Äô‚Äù
\v 24 Ez…® Josep daguraguim…®n d…®kavigha, Ekiam…®n ensel irebam…®n aven a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ghua Maria inigha an iti.
\v 25 A poroghamiba uari isava akuir arazitam Maria gamizir puvat…®gha, ghua an otarim bate. Ez…® a ziam Iesus a isa a gat…®.
\c 2
\s1 Saghon itir fofozir gumaziba Iesus bagha ize
\p 
\v 1 Maria Distrigh Judian aven itir nguibam Betlehem…®n Iesus bate. Dughiar kam…®n Herot, Atrivim…®n iti. Amebam Iesus batez…®ma fofozir gumazir maba aruem anadi nagh…®n ikegha Jerusalem…®n ize.\f + \ft (2:1) Atrivim Herot Judia ko Judian borogh…®n itir distrigh bar gari. Herot Atrivim…®n ikia, uaghan Rom…®n Atrivir Ekiam Sisar…®n apem…®n iti.\f*
\v 2 Egha me kamagh…®n azai, ‚ÄúBorir Judabar Atrivim…®n ikiamim, amebam a batez…® a managh iti? E an gun m…®geir m…®kovezim aruem anadi nagh…®n an ganigha an ziam fasa izi.‚Äù
\v 3 Ez…® Herot akar kam baregha an d…®ghorim a b…®ra. Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir darazi uaghan kamagh…®n ami.
\v 4 Egha Herot ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumazibar diagha me akuvagha kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúGod Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, an amebam managh a batam?‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúJudian Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam Betlehem…®n, an amebam a batam. E bizir kam kamagh…®n a g…®fo, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n osizirim kamagh…®n iti,
\b
\q1 
\v 6 ‚ÄòN…® Betlehem, n…® Judan nguazim…®n aven iti.
\q1 N…® Judabar nguibar ekiabar tong…®n uaghan ziam iti,
\q3 n…®n aven atrivir ekiatam azenim giram,
\q3 egh a nan gumazamiziba Israelbagh ativagham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Herot averara aruem anadi nagh…®n izezir gumazibar diagha m…®kovezim otozir dughiam bagha men azai. A me faraghav…®ra m…®kovezim…®n apizir dughiam g…®fogha,
\v 8 egha me isa Betlehem…®n me amadagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® borim bativs…® deraghv…®ra rui. Ia a batogh…®va ua na bagh m…®g…®r…®g…®am amadagh. Eght…® k…® uaghan mang…®, an ziam fam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Me Herot baregha zuima m…®kovezir me faragha aruem anadi nagh…®n ganizim, men faragha ghua borim itir danganim batogha a gis…®rara iti.\f + \ft (2:9) Betlehem a Jerusalem…®n saghon itir puvat…®. Aning t…®zim 8 kilomitan iti.\f*
\v 10 Me m…®kovezim…®n ganigha bar akonge.
\v 11 Egha me d…®penim…®n aven ghua borim bato, a uan amebam Maria ko. Me tevibar p…®righa avigha ghuaghira borim…®n ziam fe. Egha me uan m…®tariba kuigha bizir aghuir a bagha inigha izezibar an ekarim gami. Me gol ko mughuriar aghuim itir borem ko avir m…®gharir muguriar aghuim gamim da isava a gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® God irebam…®n me batogha Herot bagh ua mangan me anogoroke. Ez…® me tuavir igharazim…®n uamategha uan nguibam…®n ghue.
\s1 Josep ko Maria borim inigha Isip…®n zui
\p 
\v 13 Fofozir gumaziba ghuez…®ma Ekiam…®n ensel…®n mam irebam…®n Josep batogha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh borim iniva an amebam sara inigh…®va ia ar…® Isip…®n mang…®. Herot borim bagh ruiva am…®sueght…® an aremeghasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia mang…® magh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…®, dughiar k…® ua n…® m…®k…®mamim.‚Äù
\v 14 Ez…®ma Josep d…®kavigha borim isa an amebam inigha me d…®magarir kamra Isip…®n ghue.
\v 15 Egha Josep Isip…®n ikia ghua, dughiar Herot ovengezim. Arazir kabanagh otiva Ekiam…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n akatorim…®n m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®n otifi. A kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúNan Otarim Isip…®n itima k…® an diaz…®ma a ize.‚Äù
\s1 Atrivim Herot m…®kemez…®ma, me borir av…®ribav soghez…®ma da ariagh…®re
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Herot garima, fofozir gumazir aruem anadi nagh…®n izeziba a gifara. Ez…® Herot bar puv atara uan m…®dorozir gumaziba amadagha, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim me gan…®ga, me amadima me ghua, Betlehem koma an borogh…®n itir nguibaba bar dar ghua borir otarir azenir pumuning ko an apengan itiba, me m…®sozima me ariagh…®re. Kar ana aruem anadi nagh…®n izezir fofozir gumazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n g…®n ghua kamagh…®n ami.
\v 17 Arazir kabanagh otiva God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, otifi. A ghaze,
\v 18 ‚ÄúMe Raman nguibam…®n tiarir mam barasi, azir akam ko tuatem. Resel…®n boriba ua itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®ra a uan ovengezir boriba bagha azi. An navir am…®rizim inian aghua.‚Äù
\s1 Josep amuim ko Iesus inigha uamategha uan nguibam…®n ize
\p 
\v 19 Herot ovengez…®ma, Josep Isip…®n itima, Ekiam…®n ensel irebam…®n Josep bato.
\v 20 Egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBorim m…®soghasa amir darazi me ovenge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® d…®kavigh borim koma an amebam inigh ua Israel…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\v 21 Ez…® a d…®kavigha borim isa an amebam inigha me ua Israel…®n ghue.
\p 
\v 22 Egha an orazima, Arkelaus uan afeziam Herot…®n danganim inigha Judian Atrivim…®n iti. Ez…® Josep Judian Distrigh…®n mangan atiatingi. Egha God da irebam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am inigha egha Galilin Distrigh…®n ghu.\f + \ft (2:22) Herot ovengez…®ma Rom…®n gavman a garir kantri ab…®gha an otaribagh an…®ngi. Ez…® Arkelaus atrivim…®n ikia Distrigh Galili ko Distrigh Judian gari. A 10 plan azenibar atrivim…®n ike.\f*
\v 23 A ghua Galilin Distrigh…®n nguibar mam, Nasaret…®n apera. Bizir kaba otiva God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n otifi, a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe Nasaretian gumazim, a dar…®gham.‚Äù
\c 3
\s1 Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, akam akuri
\r (Mak 1:2-8 ko Luk 3:1-18 ko Jon 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kamnagh…®n Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim Jon izava, Judian gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia akam akuri.
\v 2 Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, a rogh…®ra ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia navibagh iragh.‚Äù\f + \ft (3:2) Ziar kamning, ‚ÄúKingdom Bilong God‚Äù o ‚ÄúKingdom Bilong Heven,‚Äù aning God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam m…®gei. Ez…® kagh Matyu osiriz…® Akar Aghuim…®n aven e ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam.‚Äù\f*
\v 3 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia fom…®ra Jon…®n gun m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir tiarir mam gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n dia ghaze, ‚ÄòIa Ekiam bagh…®va tuaviba azen…®va, dar k…®r.‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Jon kemel…®n ar…®ziba ingarizir korotiaba aghuigha as…®zir inim uan ivariam ike. An odeziba ko ruarim…®n haniba api.\f + \ft (3:4) Jon apir dagheba ko an azuir korotiaba an akakagha ghaze, a God…®n akam inigha izezir gumazim Elaijan m…®n iti. Akar 2 King 1:8…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\v 5 Ez…® gumazamiziba, me Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ko Judian Distrigh ko Jordan…®n danganim…®n ikegha, bar a bagha zui.
\v 6 Me iza uan arazir kurabar gun m…®geima, Jon Jordan d…®pam…®n me rue.
\p 
\v 7 Egha a gari, Farisiba ko Sadyusibar men av…®rim a gumaziba ruer danganim…®n izi. Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa kuruzir divir anababa, tina ia m…®kemez…®, ia God…®n an…®ngagharir g…®n izamim…®n ar…® mangasa?
\v 8 Ia navim g…®razir arazibar amu.
\v 9 Egh ia pura uarigh n…®ghn…®gh suam ‚ÄòE Abraham…®n ovaviba.‚Äô K…® ia m…®gei, God dag…®ar kabara amight…® da Abraham…®n ovavibar m…®n otivighamin gavgavim iti.
\v 10 Sobiam dat…®r…®gh…®n temer povibar iti, eght…® temer dagher ov…®zir aghuiba itir puvat…®ziba, God bar da okegh…®va da is…®va avim m…®k…®nam.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEz…® k…® ia navibagh irazir arazim akakaghasa k…® d…®pam…®n ia rue. Ez…® nan g…®n izir gumazim, an gavgavim nan gavgavim gafira. Ez…® k…® an dagarir asuabar ateramin gavgaviba puvat…®. Gumazir kam God…®n Duam ko avim…®n ia ruam.
\v 12 A witba m…®sevir savol an agharim…®n iti, eght…® a uan witba m…®s…®va dar daghebar ar…®gh…®va, witba m…®sevir d…®penim…®n wit…®n m…®seviba aviva, egh dar m…®seviba avir munger puvat…®zim…®n da akunt…®ma, da isiam.‚Äù
\s1 Jon Iesus rue
\r (Mak 1:9-11 ko Luk 3:21-22)
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® dughiar kam Iesus Galilin Distrigh ategha Jon a ruasa, Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n zui.
\v 14 Ez…® Jon an anogorogha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh sua, uab…® ruasa na bagha izi? N…® na rut…®, kamagh…®n deragham!‚Äù
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus an m…®g…®r…®g…®am ikaragha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…® m…®gei mogh…®n n…® damu. Ga arazir kam…®n, God ifongezir araziba dar g…®n t…®ght…®, da ot…®vam.‚Äù Ez…® Jon an m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus ruegha g…®vagha zuam…®ra d…®pam ategha azenim…®n ize. Ez…® overiam kuiaghr…®z…® a garima, God…®n Duam bunbam…®n m…®n m…®ghegha izaghira a gis…®n apera.
\v 17 Ez…® tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikia d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar nan Otarim, k…® bar a gifonge. K…® a bagha bar akonge.‚Äù
\c 4
\s1 Satan Iesus gifarasa a gakaghori
\r (Mak 1:12-13 ko Luk 4:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n God…®n Duam Iesus inigha ghua Satan a gifarasa danganir gumaziba itir puvat…®zim…®n ghu.
\v 2 Ez…® Iesus 40 plan arueba ko d…®magaribar daghetam inizir puvat…®. Ez…® m…®tiriam an azi.
\v 3 Ez…® gumazir ifavaribagh amim Satan iza a batogha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® guizbang…®ra God…®n Otarim, n…® dag…®ar kaba akar gavgavim dav kemeght…® da bret…®n rubuzibar m…®n otogh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus Satan ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazamiziba daghebara dam…®va dar gavgavim…®n ikian kogham. Puvat…®. Me God m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar dar g…®n mang…®va me ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim iniam.‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Satan Iesus inigha Jerusalem…®n ghua a isa God…®n D…®penim…®n p…®n mar anefa.
\v 6 Egha Satan a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄòA n…® bagh uan enselba akar gavgavim me m…®k…®mt…®ma me deraghv…®ra n…®n ganam. Egh me uan dafaribar n…® fueght…®, n…® uan dagarim dag…®atam…®n aneseghan kogham.‚Äô Kamagh…®n n…® guizbang…®ra God…®n Otarim, n…® kagh uab…® ekunigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® uan Ekiam God a gifar…®va, a gakaghont…®, a n…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mangan mark…®.‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Satan ua Iesus inigha ghua m…®ghs…®ar bar p…®n itir mam…®n ghua nguazir kam…®n kantriba bar, ko dar bizir aghuiba an akakagha ghaze,
\v 9 ‚ÄúN…® tevemning ap…®righ nan ziam feght…®ma, bizir kaba k…® bar da n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúSatan n…® na gitagh! God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® uan Ekiam God, n…® an apengara ik…® an ziamra fam.‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Satan Iesus ataghiz…® enselba iza an akura.
\s1 Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n ingari
\r (Mak 1:14-15 ko Luk 4:14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus orazi, me Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim a isa kalabus gat…®, ez…® a uamategha Galilin Distrigh…®n ghu.
\v 13 Egha a Nasaret…®n nguibam ategha ghua Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n iti. Nguibar kam d…®par ekiam Galilin dadarim…®n Sebulun ko Naptalin nguazir as…®zim…®n iti.\f + \ft (4:13) Israel…®n inazir pumuning Sebulun Ko Naptali fom…®ra Galilin d…®par dadarim…®n ike. Egha Iesus…®n dughiam…®n aning Galilin Distrigh…®n aven iti.\f*
\v 14 Arazir kabanagh otiva fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n otifi. A ghaze,
\v 15 ‚ÄúIa gumazamizir Sebulun…®n nguazim ko Naptalin nguazim…®n itiba, nguazir kam a tuavir ongarim…®n zuim borogh…®ra itir danganim ko Jordan…®n d…®par dadarir vong…®n itir danganim, a Galilin Distrigh…®n nguazim. Danganir kam Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazir av…®riba uaghan an aven iti.
\v 16 Kar, gumazamizir arazir kurabar m…®tatem…®n aven itiba, me angazangarir ekiam…®n gani. Egha gumazamizir ovengamin m…®tatem…®n aven ikeziba, angazangarim me gisira.‚Äù
\ms1 Iesus akar aghuim akuri
\mr (Sapta 4:17-9:34)
\s1 Iesus suren gumazir 4 plan diaz…®, me an g…®n zui
\r (Mak 1:16-20 ko Luk 5:1-11)
\p 
\v 17 Dughiar kam…®n Iesus ingarim foregha akam akura gumaziba me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam a rogh…®ra ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia navibagh iragh!‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Iesus Galilin d…®par dadarim…®n ghua gari aveghbuar mamning iti. Saimon, me ‚ÄúPita‚Äù a gar…®si. A uan dozim Endru ko, aning iver ekiaba d…®pam…®n da kuri. Aning osiriba isa da amadir gumazimning.
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua nan g…®n iz…®t…®ma k…® guan akakaght…®ma, gua osiriba isi mogh…®n gumaziba iniam.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® aning an akam baraghav…®ra, uan iveba ategha an g…®n zui.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus mong s…®vagha ghua aveghbuar mamning…®n api. Jems, a Sebedin otarim, a uan dozim Jon ko iti. Aning uan afeziam Sebedi ko me bot…®n mam…®n iti. Men iveba d…®ghoraghrez…®, me dar toribar k…®ri. Ez…®ma Iesus aning diaz…®ma,
\v 22 aning magh…®ra uan afeziam ko bot ategha Iesus…®n g…®n zui.
\s1 Iesus akam akura ar…®mariabar k…®ri
\r (Luk 6:17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus Galilin Distrigh bar a garua me God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven men sure gami. Egha a God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar aghuim akura, men ar…®mariaba ak…®rava men m…®karzibar itir bizir os…®mt…®ziba a uaghan da gefi.
\v 24 Ez…® an biarim Sirian Provins bar an ghu. Ez…®ma gumazamizir ar…®mariaba itiba, me bar me isa a bagha izi. Gumazir aria m…®zazir kuraba baraziba, ko duar kuraba apazaziba, ko gumazir ar…®mariar in…®r…®zibagh amiba, ko gumazir agharapaniba ariaghreziba, me bar me inigha a bagha izi. Ez…® Iesus men ar…®mariaba bar da g…®fa.\f + \ft (4:24) Judan Nguibam Rom…®n gavman…®n apengan itir dughiam…®n, kantri Israel a Rom…®n Provins…®n ekiam Sirian aven iti.\f*
\v 25 Ez…® gumazamizir b…®zir dafam, me a koma arui. Galilin itir darasi ko Distrigh Dekapolis…®n itir darazi ko Jerusalem ko Judian Distrigh, ko Jordan…®n vong…®n itir danganim…®n itiba me an g…®n arui.
\c 5
\s1 Iesus m…®ghs…®am…®n akam akuri
\p 
\v 1 Iesus gari av…®rir ekiam an g…®n izima a m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n anabogha, egha apera. Ez…® an suren gumaziba a bagha izi.\f + \ft (5:1) Judabar arazim, men tisaba apiava akam akuri. (Matyu 13:2 ko 24:3 koma Luk 4:20…®n gan.)\f*
\s1 Iesus gumazamizibar sure gami
\r (Luk 6:20-23)
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibar sure gamua ghaze,\f + \ft (5:2) Matyu 4:23-25 koma 9:35 ghaze, Iesus ingangarir pumuning gami. A faragha gumazamizibar sure gamigha g…®n men ar…®mariaba batosi. Kamagh…®n e Matyu sapta 5…®n ikegha ghua sapta 7…®n tu Iesus, God Bizibagh Ativamin akabar men sure gami. Egha g…®n Matyu sapta 8 ko 9 e gari, Iesus men ar…®mariaba batosi. Matyun Osirizir Akar Aghuim…®n aven Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar ruarir 5 pla akuni, sapta 5-7…®n itir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ruarim a 5 plan kabar faragha otifi, ez…® 4 pla ikiav…®ra iti. Akar sapta 5-7…®n itiba a m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n ikia da akuni.\f*
\v 3 ‚ÄúIa God…®n damazim…®n ia fo ia an bizibagh asa, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mangam. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 4 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n azia itir gumaziba, ia bar akuegham. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 5 Ia gumazir uan gavgaviba ko ziaba fer puvat…®ziba, God nguazim bar ia dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 6 Ia gumazir arazir aghuiba baghav…®ra ikia egha mati gumazim m…®tiriam an azi, egha mati gumazim kuarim an p…®ri, God ian m…®tiriam a g…®vagham. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 7 Ia gumazir apangkuvim igharazibar itiba, God ian apangkuvam. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 8 Ia gumazamizir navir averiar zueziba, ia God…®n ganam. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 9 Ia gumazamizir adariba ko m…®doroziba ageviba, me ‚ÄòGod…®n Boriba‚Äô ia dar…®gham. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 10 Ia gumazamizir arazir aghuibagh amiba, ez…® me arazir kam bagha os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zaziba ia gan…®di, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, a iananam. Kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 11 Me ian gari ia na ko iti, ez…® bizir kam bang…®n me paza arazir os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zaziba ia gan…®di, egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ifavarir av…®riba ia gasi, kamagh…®n ian naviba deragh.
\v 12 Ivezir bar ekiam ia m…®zua God…®n Nguibam…®n iti. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir ian faragha ghueziba, me uaghan kamagh…®ra os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zaziba me gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n ia naviba deragh bar akongegh.‚Äù
\s1 Ia amangs…®zim ko angazangarim…®n m…®n iti
\r (Mak 9:50 ko Luk 14:34-35)
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus ua me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazamiziba bar me bagha, amangs…®zim…®n m…®n iti. Ia uan is…®ngt…®zim ateght…®ma e manmagh…®n a damut…® a ua s…®ngigham? Amangs…®zir kamagh…®n otiviba ingangariba puvat…®. Me a is…® nguazim…®n anekunigh a d…®kab…®nam.
\v 14 Ia mati nguazir kam…®n angazangarim. Ia kamagh n…®ghn…®gh! Nguibar ekiar mam m…®ghs…®am…®n ik…® modoghan kogham.
\v 15 Egha gumazitam lam tam a gaborogha a isa m…®netam…®n aven anet…®zir puvat…®. An a is…® dakozim dafaght…®ma, an angazangarim gumazir d…®penim…®n itiba bar me gisiragham.
\v 16 N…®n angazangarim kamagh…®ra is…®ght…®ma, gumaziba bar an ganam. Egh me ian arazir aghuir kabar gan…®va ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, me an ziam fam.‚Äù
\s1 Moses Osirizir Arazibar akaba
\p 
\v 17 Egha Iesus ua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, egh suam, k…® Moses Osirizir Araziba ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba batoghasa ize. Puvat…®. K…® iz…® dar amut…® dar dagheba guiz…®n otivam.
\v 18 K…® bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, Moses Osirizir Arazibar akar muziaritam g…®vaghan kogham, mang…® nguazim ko overiam g…®vaghamin dughiam otogham. Dar osizirir otevir muziariba ko ababanir me osiriziba, da kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® bizir otivamiba bar otivigham.
\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir manam Moses Osirizir Arazitam…®n kuragh egh suam, a pura bizim, egh kamagh…®ra igharaz darazi men sure damuva, gumazir kamagh…®n amim, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n an ziam bar g…®n ikiam. Eght…®ma gumazir manam Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®va egh kamagh…®ra ua igharaz darazir men sure damut…® me an m…®n arazir kabar g…®n mang…®t…®, gumazir kamagh…®n amizim, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, a ziar bar ekiam iniam.
\v 20 Kamagh…®n k…® ia m…®gei, ia God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n t…®ghan kogh…®va ian arazir aghuiba Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisibar arazir aghuiba dagh afiraghan kogham, eght…® ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mangan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus akabar k…®rir arazim m…®gei
\r (Luk 12:57-59)
\p 
\v 21 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ian ovaviba iniziba, ia da baregha g…®fa egha dagh fo, ia tav m…®sueght…®ma an aremeghan mark…®. Ian tav gumazitam m…®sueght…®ma an aremegham, a kotiam…®n otivam.
\v 22 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, gumazir manam uan aveghbuam…®n atari, a kotiam…®n mangam. Egh gumazitam m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurabar uan aveghbuam m…®k…®m suam, a Kotiar Ekiam…®n otivam. Egh gumazitam gumazir mam…®n atar suam, a gumazir onganim, a hel…®n avir ekiam…®n mangam.
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄúEgh n…® ofa damus…® ofa gamir danganim…®n mang…®, egh n…® n…®ghn…®gham, n…® uan aveghbuam ko m…®g…®r…®g…®ar os…®mt…®zim iti,
\v 24 egh n…® uan ofaba ofa gamir danganim…®n dar at…®gh. Egh…®va uamategh mang…® aveghbuam ko m…®g…®r…®g…®abar k…®righ. Gua dar k…®righ, egh n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® uan ofa is…® God dan…®ng.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúEgh n…®n apanim n…® inigh kotiam…®n mang…®t…®, n…® a ko os…®mt…®zir kam ak…®rs…® tuavim…®n a m…®k…®m mang…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, a n…® inigh jas…®n damazim…®n mangam. Eght…® jas n…® inigh polis…®n agharim dat…®ght…®ma, polis n…® inigh kalabuziam dat…®gham.
\v 26 Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® azenim giran kogham, ik…® mang…® n…® ivezim bar anek…®righamin dughiam…®n g…®n, azenim giram.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus poroghamiba uari bakeir arazibav gei
\p 
\v 27 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oraki, me fom…®ra ghaze, ia poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim, damuan mark…®.
\v 28 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, n…® gumazitam n…® amizir mam…®n gara paza a g…®n…®ghn…®si, n…® poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim uan navir averiam…®n aven, a ko a gamigha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúEght…® n…®n damazir guvim…®n itim n…® gami, n…® arazir kuram damight…®, anesigh a makunigh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…®n m…®karzitam dutught…®, n…® arazir kuratam damighan kogham. Puvat…®ght…®ma, me n…®n m…®karzim bar a is…®va hel…®n anekunigham.
\v 30 Eght…® n…®n dafarir guvim n…® damut…® n…® arazir kuratam damight…®, n…® anetugh a makunigh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…®n m…®karzitam dutugh deragham, egh n…® arazir kuratam damuan kogham. Puvat…®ght…®ma, me n…®n m…®karzim bar a is…® hel…®n anekunigham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, gumaziba uan amuiba ataghraghan kogham
\r (Matyu 19:9 ko Mak 10:11-12 ko Luk 16:18)
\p 
\v 31 Egha Iesus ua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe fom…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazir manam uan amuim ataghraghs…®, an a bagh ak…®nafarim osirigh egh anetegham.‚Äô
\v 32 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, Gumazir manam uan amuim…®n garima, a gumazir igharazitam ko akuiz puvat…®z…® a pura anetaki, gumazir kam uan amuim gamima a poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami. Eght…® amizir kam gumazir igharazitam…®n ikiam, a poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami. Eght…® gumazitam amizir pam ataghizim…®n ik…®va, egh gumazir kam uaghan poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, ia bizibav k…®m egh guizbang…®ra dar…®gh God…®n Nguibam…®n akakaghan mark…®
\p 
\v 33 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúM…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam ian ovaviba a iniz…® ia a baraki, a kara. ‚ÄòIa ifar…®va God…®n Nguibam…®n akakagh m…®k…®man mark…®. Egh ia Ekiam…®n damazim…®n m…®geir akam…®n m…®rara mang…®, arazir kam deragh a damu.‚Äô
\v 34 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, bizir katam…®n akakagh m…®k…®man mark…®. Bar markiam. Ia God…®n Nguibam akakagh egh m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra,‚Äô ia kamagh…®n damuan mark…®. Bar markiam. Kar God…®n Atrivir Dabirabim.
\v 35 Ia uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, nguazir kam d…®ponan mark…®. God nguazim…®n uan suemning ar…®si. Egh ia uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, Jerusalem d…®ponan mark…®. Jerusalem Atrivir Ekiam…®n nguibar ekiam.
\v 36 Egh ia uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…® uan dapanibar akakaghan mark…®. Ia fo, ian tav uan dapanir ar…®zitam damut…® a pigham, o ghurghurighan kogham.
\v 37 Ia pura kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòGuizbang…®ra‚Äô o ‚ÄòPuvat…®.‚Äô A kamagh…®n dera. Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar igharazir isafuraziba, da Satan…®n otivaghirir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, arazir kuraba ikarvaghan mark…®
\r (Luk 6:29-30)
\p 
\v 38 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oraki, me fom…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄòTav igharaz tav…®n damazim a gas…®ghasight…®, eght…® me uaghan an damazim gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® tav tav…®n ataritam asight…®, me uaghan an ataritam asigham.‚Äô
\v 39 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, gumazim arazir kuratam ia damight…®ma, ia a ikarvaghan mark…®. Egh gumazitam ian koviatam apezeght…®, ia koviar vuem sara a dan…®ngigh.
\v 40 Eght…® tav ian korotiar azenan azuim bagh ia is…® kotiam dat…®ght…®, ia uaghan uan aven azuir korotiam sara a dan…®ngigh.
\v 41 Eght…® tav uan biziba iniasa n…® bagha gavgava ghaze, n…® an biziba atera an aku tuavir as…®zitam…®n mangam, eght…® n…® an aku tuavir as…®zir ruarir pumuning…®n ang…®.
\v 42 Eght…® tav biziba bagh ian azangs…®ght…®, ia a dan…®ngi. Eght…® gumazitam pura ia da biziba iniasa ian azai, ia ak…®rim ragh a gasan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, ia uan apanibagh ifongegh
\r (Luk 6:27-28 ko 6:32-36)
\p 
\v 43 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oraki, me fom…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa uan namakabagh ifongegh, egh paz…® uan apanibar amu.‚Äô\f + \ft (5:43) M…®g…®r…®g…®ar uan akar gumazibara ifongeghamim Wok Pris 19:18…®n iti. Ez…® akar uan apanibagh ifongeghan koghamim itir danganim e a g…®fozir puvat…®. Pura Lo 7:2, ko 20:16; koma Song 139:21-22…®n gan.\f*
\v 44 Ez…® k…® kamagh ia m…®gei, ia uan apanibagh ifongegh, egh me bagh God…®n azang, eght…® God gumazir os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zaziba ia gan…®dibar, men apangkuvigham.
\v 45 Arazir kam kamagh…®n ian akagham, ia guizbang…®ra uan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, ia an boribara. Guizbang…®ra, an aruem gamima, a gumazir kuraba ko aghuiba bar me gis…®si. Egha an amozim gamima, a gumazir aghuiba ko gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba sara me gizi.
\v 46 Eght…® ia gumazir ia ifongezibagh ifuegh…®va ia ivezir manatam iniam? Puvat…®. Gumazir dag…®aba isiba uaghan arazir kabagh ami.
\v 47 Egh ia dughiam is…® uan adarazira an…®ng, egh ian arazir manam igharaz darazir arazim gafiragham? Gumazir God g…®fozir puvat…®ziba ti uaghan ia amir arazibagh ami!
\v 48 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, an arazir aghuibara dagh ami mogh…®n, ia uaghan arazir aghuibar amu.‚Äù
\c 6
\s1 Iesus igharazibar akurvazir arazim m…®gei
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra gan. Ia gumazamiziba gans…® osam…®va, arazir aghuibar amuan mark…®. Ia kamagh damu, uan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim da ivezitam inighan kogham.
\p 
\v 2 ‚ÄúEgh ia bizitam is…® gumazir asaghasazitam dan…®ngs…®va, tav amadaght…®ma a mang…® ian arazir aghuir kam an gun m…®k…®man mark…®, egh mati gumazir maba me God ko m…®geir d…®peniba ko tuavibar tuiva odava ami mogh…®n. Ia men m…®n damuan mark…®. Kamagh amir darazi, me gumazamizibar damazibar uan araziba akakaght…®ma, me men ziaba fasa. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, me uan ivezim inigha g…®fa.
\v 3 Ia asaghasazitam…®n akurvaghs…®, ian agharir guvim arazir kam damut…®, agharir ik…®riam arazir kam g…®foghan kogham.
\v 4 Eght…® ian akurvazir arazir kam averara ik…®t…®, ian Afeziar bizir mogomebar garim, ian arazir aghuim ikaragham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus God ko m…®geir arazibagh eghari
\r (Luk 11:2-4)
\p 
\v 5 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God ko m…®k…®ms…®, gumazir ifavariba ami mogh…®n damuan mark…®. Me God ko m…®geir d…®peniba ko tuavir ekiabar akabar tuiva, God ko m…®k…®masa bar akonge. Me odava, egha ghaze, gumazamizir av…®riba nan ganigh nan ziam fam. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, me uan ivezim inigha g…®fa.
\v 6 Egh ia God ko m…®k…®ms…®, uan d…®penir averiam…®n mang…® tiam asaragh, egh modogh ia uan Afeziam ko m…®k…®m. Kamagh…®n, ian Afeziar bizir mogomebar garim, a ian ivezim ia dan…®ngam.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa God ko m…®k…®ms…®va m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…®nir av…®ribar amuva, God g…®fozir puvat…®zir darazi ami mogh…®n damuan mark…®. Me ghaze, me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar amuam, eght…® kamagh…®n God me baragham.
\v 8 Ia me ami mogh…®n damuan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, bizir ia puvat…®ziba, dughiar ia t…®ghar uan Afeziam da bagh an azangs…®ghamim, ana dagh fogha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kamagh…®n God ko m…®k…®m:
\b
\q1 ‚ÄòEn Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim,
\q2 n…®n ziam bar zue,
\q2 ez…® arazir kuraba an saghon iti.
\q1 
\v 10 Eght…® Dughiar N…® Bizibagh Ativamim, a iz…®.
\q1 Eght…® n…®n Nguibam…®n itir darasi n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n zui mogh…®n,
\q2 e uaghan nguazir kam…®n n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mangam.
\q1 
\v 11 Eght…® n…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n damamin dagheba da is…® e dan…®ng.
\q1 
\v 12 Eght…® me e gamir arazir kuraba e da g…®n amadi mogh…®n,
\q2 n…® en arazir kuraba g…®n amang.
\q1 
\v 13 Egh e ateght…®, e os…®mt…®zibar aven ik…®t…® bizitam en navim b…®raght…®ma,
\q2 e arazir kuratam damuan kogham.
\q1 N…® arazir kurabar gavgavim da e inigh.‚Äô\f + \ft (6:13) Fofozir gumazir maba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ‚Äúarazir kuraba,‚Äù a ghaze ‚ÄúGumazir arazir kurabagh amim,‚Äù a Satanra. Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir mam uaghan vez…®n kam…®n ikiam. M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam kamak…®n: ‚ÄúAtrivir arazim koma, gavgavim koma, ziar ekiam bar n…® nanabara, egh zurazurara ikiam.‚Äù\f*
\b
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, ia gumazamiziba ia gamir arazir kuraba g…®n amangt…®, ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, ian arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.
\v 15 Ia men arazir kuraba g…®n amangan koght…®ma, ian Afeziam uaghan ian arazir kuraba g…®n amangan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus dagheba ataghrazir arazibav gei
\p 
\v 16 Egha Iesus ua m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa dagheba ataghrazir dughiam…®n ia gumazir ifavaribar m…®n uan guabagh ekuan mark…®. Gumazir ifavariba dagheba ataghrazir dughiam…®n, gumaziba men ganasa, me uan guaba ruer puvat…®gha pughpurighav arui. Me odava arazir kabagh ami. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, me uan ivezim inigha g…®fa.
\v 17 Eght…® ia dagheba ataghrazir dughiam…®n, ia borem uari agh…®va uan guaba ru,
\v 18 eght…® gumaziba ia dagheba ataghrazir arazir kam g…®foghan kogham. Eght…® ian Afeziar danganir mogomem…®n itim, anar…®ra ian ganigh fogham. Egh g…®n ian Afeziar bizir mogomebar garim, a ian ivezim ia dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus biziba akumakuir arazibav gei
\r (Luk 12:33-34)
\p 
\v 19 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa nguazim…®n ikia uari bagh bizir aghuiba akumakum dar pozibav k…®nam mark…®. Nguazir kam…®n, barereba ko omebaba dar am…®t…®, da maz…®va akughregham. Eght…® ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba b…®riba akar da ok…®mam.
\v 20 Ia God…®n Nguibam…®n uari bagh bizir aghuiba pozibav k…®n. God…®n Nguibam…®n barereba ko omebaba bizibar aman koght…®ma, da mazigh, akughran kogham. Eght…® ok…®mak…®ar gumazitam b…®ritam akarigh…®va da okemeghan kogham.
\v 21 Danganir manam n…®n bizir aghuiba iti, danganir kam n…®n navir averiam…®n aven itir ifongiam, a uaghan ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Damazim a namnam…®n angazangarim
\r (Luk 11:34-36)
\p 
\v 22 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúDamaziba, da lam…®n m…®n namnam…®n angazangarim…®n m…®n iti. Damazim deragham, angazangarim bar n…®n namnam giz…®vaght…®, n…® arazir aghuibar amuam.
\v 23 Eght…® n…®n damaziba ikuvigham, n…®n namnam bar m…®tarmeght…®ma, n…® arazir kurabar amuam. Eght…® n…®n angazangarim m…®tarmegham, m…®tarmer kam bar p…®righam.‚Äù
\s1 Ingangarir gumazitam, gumazir ekiar pumuning bagh ingaran kogham
\r (Luk 16:13)
\p 
\v 24 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazitam, ingangarir gumazir ekiar pumuning bagh ingaran kogham. A tav…®n aghuagh, tav gifuegham. O, a tav bagh…®v…®ra ik…®, tav ak…®rim a gasaragham. Ia God ko dag…®aba bagh uaghara ingaran kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Ia pamten biziba bagh d…®ghorim isiva dagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®
\r (Luk 12:22-31)
\p 
\v 25 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia m…®gei, ia pamten uan ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va, kamagh…®n azangan mark…®, e dagher manatamra damam, o e d…®par manatamra damam? Egh ia pamten uan nivaf…®zibagh n…®ghn…®gh m…®k…®man mark…®, inir manatam uan nivaf…®zim avam? Gumazim…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim ti daghebagh afira, ez…® gumazim…®n namnam ti inibagh afira.
\v 26 Ia kuarazibar gari, da dagheba oparir puvat…®, egha da dar pozibagh aghua da isa dagher d…®penibar amadir puvat…®. Ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, dagheba me gan…®di. Ez…® ian dabirabim ti kuarazibar dabirabim gafirazir puvat…®?
\v 27 Egh ian tav deraghv…®ra ik…®s…® n…®ghn…®gh kamagh…®n a ti uan ik…®r…®m…®rim damut…® a tong ruaragham? Bar puvat…®.
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúIa tizim sua, pamten korotiabagh n…®ghn…®si? Ia ak…®marir aghuaribagh n…®ghn…®gh. Da manmagh…®n otifi? Me ingangarir ekiatam gamir puvat…®. Egha me korotiatam isamizir puvat…®.
\v 29 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, fom…®ra Atrivim Solomon bizir bar av…®riba ikiava an azuir adiariba bar dera, egha an korotiatam ak…®marir kabar m…®n otozir puvat…®.
\v 30 E fo, graziba pura biziba, da iti, gurum…®n gumazitam dar akoregh…®va da is…®va avitam m…®k…®nigham. Grazir k…®nir kabanagh God adiariba me gazui. Ia bizir kam g…®fogh, God uaghan adiariba ia dan…®ngam. Ia gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir muziarim itiba!
\v 31 Kamagh…®n, ia pamten n…®ghn…®gh m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄòE dagher manatam ramegham? O, d…®par manatam ramam? O, e inir manatam ikegham?‚Äô
\v 32 Gumazir God g…®fozir puvat…®ziba pamten bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®si. Ez…® ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim fo, ia bizir puvat…®zir kaba, ia da iniam.
\v 33 Ez…® bizir ia bar faragh damuamimra kara: Ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam bagh…®v…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, egh God ifongezir arazir aghuibar amut…®, a bizir kaba ko maba sara bar ia dan…®ngam.
\v 34 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia pamten gurum…®zaraghan bagh d…®ghorim isiva n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Gurum izamin dughiam, a mar uan bizibara n…®ghn…®gh. Dughiar manam…®n otivir os…®mt…®ziba, da anar…®ra ik…®. Aruer manam…®n otivamin biziba, mar an biziba.‚Äù
\c 7
\s1 Ia munen araziba tuis…®ghan mark…®, egh suam, men araziba ikufi
\r (Luk 6:37-38 ko 6:41-42)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod ia tuis…®gh ian kuraghan koghs…®, kamagh…®n ia munen araziba tuis…®ghan mark…® suam, men araziba ikufi.
\v 2 Ia me tuis…®gha men ikurvagha ami mogh…®ra, God kamagh…®ra ia tuis…®gham. Egh ia men gara me g…®n…®ghn…®zi mogh…®ra, God ia g…®n…®ghn…®gham.
\v 3 Tizim bagha, m…®nezir bar muziarim n…®n aveghbuam…®n damazim…®n itima, n…® ti an gara egha temer ararir ekiar n…®n damazim…®n itim…®n garir puvat…®?
\v 4 Ter ararir ekiam n…®n damazim…®n ik…®t…®, n…® manmagh…®n uan aveghbuam m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòAveghbuam, k…® n…®n damazim…®n itir m…®nezim asigham?‚Äô
\v 5 N…® bar ifari! N…® faraghv…®ra ter ararir n…®n damazim…®n itim asigh, egh deragh gan…®va m…®nezir n…®n aveghbuam…®n damazim…®n itim asigh.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúIa God baghav…®ra itir biziba inigh, afiabar an…®ngan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, da ua raghr…®gh ia givigham. Egh ia uan manmaniar ikar…®zir aghuiba is…® dabav k…®nan mark…®. Da pura da d…®kab…®nigham.‚Äù
\s1 God bizir aghuiba is…®va, gumazir a ko m…®geibar an…®ngam
\r (Luk 11:9-13)
\p 
\v 7 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God ko m…®k…®m, egh biziba bagh an azang, eght…® a da is…® ia dan…®ngam. Egh ia biziba bagh ruiva, ia da bativam. Egh ia tiam gafughafught…®, God ia bagh tiam kuigham.
\v 8 Gumazir God…®n azaiba, me biziba isi. Ez…® gumazir biziba bagha ruim, a biziba batifi. Ez…® gumazir itiam gafughafuzim, God a bagh akuigham.
\v 9 Eght…® ia afeziaba, ian boritam bretba bagh ian azangt…®ma, ia ti dag…®atam a dan…®ngam? Puvat…®.
\v 10 Eght…® boritam osiriba bagh uan afeziam…®n azangt…®, a ti kuruzitam a dan…®ngam? Bar puvat…®.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúIa afeziar arazir kurabagh amiba, ia zurara bizir bar aghuiba uan boribagh an…®di. Egh ia kamagh deraghv…®ra fogh, guizbang…®ra ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim bar akueghv…®ra bizir aghuiba is…® gumazir a ko m…®geibar an…®ngam.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n, ia arazir aghuir igharaz darazi me ia damuasa ia ifongeziba, ia arazir kabara me damu. M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba, Moses Osirizir Araziba ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar osiziriba, dagh is…®n tu.‚Äù
\s1 Tiar akar asuvazim ko aroghezim
\r (Luk 13:24)
\p 
\v 13 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tiar akar asuvazim…®n aven mang…®. Tiar akar aroghezim nguibar ikuvt…®zim…®n zui. Ez…® nguibar kam…®n zuir tuavim an aruegha bar ekefe. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim an zui.
\v 14 Ez…® nguibar aghuim…®n zuir tiar akam bar asufa, egha tuavir an zuim bar p…®ri. Ez…® gumazamizir vaghvaziba tuavir kam batogha an zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tiar akar asuvazim…®n aven mang…®.‚Äù
\s1 Ia akar ifavarim akurir gumaziba bagh derav…®ra gan
\r (Luk 6:43-44 ko 13:25-27)
\p 
\v 15 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa akar ifavarim akurir gumaziba bagh derav…®ra gan. Me ia gifars…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibar amuam. Egha me guizbang…®ra ia gas…®ghas…®ghasa izi. Me guizbang…®ra afiar atiabar m…®n ikia, egha me ifara en damazibar sipsipbar m…®n sipsipbar ar…®ziba aghui.
\v 16 Ia men arazibar gan me g…®fogh, egh suam, me akar ifavarim akurir gumaziba. Gumaziba ter ataghataritam…®n wain…®n ov…®zitam kuarizir puvat…®. Egha me ti figh…®n ov…®zitam kuarasa ghua, d…®konir ataghatarim…®n, da isi? Bar puvat…®.
\v 17 Ez…® kamagh…®ra temer aghuiba ov…®zir aghuiba bati, ez…® temer kuraba ov…®zir kuraba bati.
\v 18 Eght…® temer aghuitam ov…®zir kuratam bateghan kogham. Eght…® temer kuratam ov…®zir aghuitam bateghan kogham.
\v 19 Temer ov…®zir aghuiba batir puvat…®ziba, me da oka da isa avim m…®k…®ri.
\v 20 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia men arazibar gan fofogh suam, me akar ifavarim akurir gumaziba, o akar aghuim akurir gumaziba.
\v 21 Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, gumazamizir ‚ÄòEkiam, Ekiam‚Äô na gar…®ziba, me bar mogh…®ra God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikiam. Puvat…®. Gumazir nan Afeziam…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n zuiba, merara God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikiam.
\v 22 God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, gumazamizir av…®rim kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòEkiam, Ekiam, e n…®n ziam…®n God…®n akam akuri.‚Äô Egh m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòE n…®n ziam…®n duar kuraba batoke,‚Äô egh m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòE n…®n ziam…®n mirakel…®n bar av…®ribagh ami.‚Äô
\v 23 Eght…® k…® Dughiar kam…®n bighv…®ra me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòK…® tong ia g…®fozir puvat…®. Ia gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, ia na gitagh!‚Äô‚Äù
\s1 D…®penir ingangarir arazir pumuning
\r (Luk 6:47-49)
\p 
\v 24 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir nan akam baragha an g…®n zuim, a mati gumazir mam fofozir aghuim ikia, egha uan d…®penim ingara gavgavim a dan…®ngasa dag…®am gis…®n an ingari.
\v 25 Ez…® amozim izima, aperiam otoz…®ma, am…®nir ekiam d…®kavigha d…®penir kam givava a munamadi. Ez…® d…®penir kam d…®p…®riaghr…®zir puvat…®. D…®penir kam me dag…®am gis…®n an ingari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ir…®zir puvat…®.
\v 26 Ez…® gumazir manam nan akam baregha an g…®n zuir puvat…®, a mati gumazir onganim…®n m…®n gigim…®n uan d…®penim okore.
\v 27 Ez…® amozim izima aperiam otoz…®ma, am…®nir ekiam d…®penir kam pamtem a givai. Bizir kaba d…®penir kam gunabagha a munamadima, a ir…®. A guizbang…®ra bar pazav…®ra ir…®.‚Äù
\v 28 Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabav m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, gumazamizir av…®rir ekiam d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 29 Me fo, Iesus Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ami mogh…®n m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ziar ekiam itir mam…®n m…®n men sure gami.
\c 8
\s1 Iesus lepa itir gumazim gamiz…®, a ua dera
\r (Mak 1:40-44 ko Luk 5:12-14)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus m…®ghs…®am ategha ghuaghirima av…®rir ekiam an g…®n zui.\f + \ft (8:1) Akar Matyu 5:2…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\v 2 Ez…® gumazir lepa itir mam, Iesus bagha iza uan tevimning ap…®righa a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® fuegh…®va na damut…®, k…® God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ua deragham.‚Äù\f + \ft (8:2) Moses osirizir akaba m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazim o amizir lepan ar…®mariam itim, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. An ar…®mariam g…®vaght…®ma a ua mang…® uab…® is…®va, ofa gamir gumazibar akagh, eght…® me an gant…®ma an ar…®mariam g…®vagham, eght…® me a m…®k…®m suam, a God…®n damazim…®n zuegha ua dera. Wok Pris 13 ko 14…®n gan.\f*
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus uan agharim isa gumazir kam gat…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ifonge. N…®n m…®karzim zuegh, egh ua deragh.‚Äù A kamagh…®n m…®g…®av…®ra itima, gumazir kam…®n lepan ar…®mariam zuam…®ra anetaghiz…®ma gumazim ua dera.\f + \ft (8:3) Judabar akar mam ghaze, gumazim ar…®mariam lepa ik…®t…®ma n…® an suiragh, n…® uaghan God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. Ez…® Iesus uan dafarim isava gumazir lepa itir kam gat…®, egha God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. A gumazim…®n ar…®mariam a g…®fa, ez…® gumazim ua dera.\f*
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, n…® batozir bizir kam…®n gun m…®k…®man mark…®. N…® mang…® uan m…®karzim is…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n akagh, egh Moses fom…®ra e m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® ua bagh God…®n ofa damu. Eght…® gumaziba fogh suam, n…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus m…®dorozir gumazim…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n ar…®mariam a g…®fa
\r (Luk 7:1-10)
\p 
\v 5 Egha Iesus ghua nguibar ekiam Kaperneam…®n aven ghu. Ez…® 100 plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir ekiam iza, Iesus gaghora ghaze,
\v 6 ‚ÄúEkiam, nan ingangarir gumazim ariava muna d…®penim…®n iti. An soroghafariba bar ariagh…®re, ez…® a m…®zazir kuram barasi.‚Äù
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® mang…® a damight…®, a ua deragham.‚Äù
\v 8 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir ekiam Iesus…®n akam ikaragha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® gumazir aghuir manam, n…® nan d…®penim…®n aven izam? Mark…®. N…® pura m…®k…®mt…®ma, nan ingangarir gumazim deragham.
\v 9 K…® uab…® m…®dorozir gumazir mabar apengan iti, egha uab…® mabar garima, da nan apengan iti. Ez…® k…® me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa mang…®,‚Äô eght…® me mangam. O, k…® me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa iz…®.‚Äô Eght…® me izam. Egh k…® uan ingangarir gumazir mam m…®k…®m suam, n…® ingangarir kam damu, eght…® an a damuam. Egha k…® fo, n…® m…®k…®mt…®, nan ingangarir gumazim ua deragh.‚Äù
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha, d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha ragha a ko izir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, k…® Israel…®n aven kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir gumazitam…®n ganizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®gei, gumazamizir av…®rim uan nguibabar aruem anadir danganim ko aruem ghuaghiri danganim ategh, iz…® Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop dukuagh, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven dakozim…®n daperagh damam.
\v 12 Egh God faragh uan Nguibam…®n ikiasa m…®sevezir darazi, God me batuegh me is…®va danganir m…®tatem me akunigham. Eght…® me tuang…®va arang…®va atariba kuskugh danganir kam…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\v 13 Egha Iesus 100 plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir ekiam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®. Bizir n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itim, a n…® bagh otogham.‚Äù Dughiar kamra, gumazir kam…®n ingangarir gumazim ua dera.
\s1 Iesus Pitan ivozir amizim gamiz…®, a ua dera
\r (Mak 1:29-31 ko Luk 4:38-39)
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus ghua Pitan d…®penim…®n aven ghua garima, Pitan asamim…®n m…®karzim an feima, an aria dakozim gir…®ghav iti.
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus an dafarim suiraz…®ma, an ar…®mariam magh…®ram anetaghiz…®ma, a d…®kavigha Iesus bagha isai.
\s1 Iesus gumazamizir av…®rim gamiz…®, me ghuamaghe
\r (Mak 1:32-34 ko Luk 4:40-41)
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® aruem gevima, me gumazamizir av…®rir duar kuraba apazaziba inigha, Iesus bagha izi. Ez…® Iesus duar kurar kabav g…®a me batozima, me an akam…®n gumazamiziba ataghrasi. Ez…® Iesus ar…®mariaba itir gumazamiziba bar men ar…®mariaba ag…®fa.
\v 17 God…®n akam inigha izezir gumazim Aisaia ghaze, ‚ÄúA uab…® e bativir ar…®mariaba ko m…®zaziba da batoghez…®, da ghue.‚Äù Iesus Aisaian akam damight…®, an otivasa, arazir kabagh ami.
\s1 Iesus uab…®n g…®n mangamin arazibav gei
\r (Luk 9:57-60)
\p 
\v 18 Egha Iesus garima, av…®rir ekiam anekufa. Ez…® a uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE d…®pam giregh vong…®n mangam.‚Äù
\v 19 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir mam iza, kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® danganir manam…®n mangam, k…® uaghan n…® ko mangam.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAfiar atiaba nguazir toribar itima, kuaraziba m…®konibar iti, ez…® Gumazibar Otarim danganir dakuamiba puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 21 Ez…® gumazir mam, a uaghan Iesus…®n suren gumazim, a kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® faragh na amamangat…®ght…®ma, k…® mang…® uan afeziam mozim dafaka.‚Äù
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®. N…® nan g…®n iz…®, gumazir ovengeziba uari uan gumazir kuabar af…®.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus m…®geima, am…®nir ekiam g…®fa
\r (Mak 4:36-41 ko Luk 8:22-25)
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus bot…®n anaboz…®, an suren gumaziba an g…®n zui.
\v 24 Me ghua ongarim…®n torim…®n am…®nir bar ekiam d…®kava ongarim gamima, a d…®p…®ra kurim avasava ami. Ez…® Iesus akuav…®ra iti.
\v 25 Ez…® an suren gumaziba agaghuragha a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® en akuragh, e ar…®m…®ghiregham!‚Äù
\v 26 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar sufi. Ia tizim bagha atiati?‚Äù Egha a d…®kavigha am…®nim ko ongarim m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim aning gan…®ngiz…®, am…®nim g…®vaz…®ma, d…®pam uam am…®raghir…®.
\v 27 Ez…® an suren gumaziba n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua ghaze, ‚ÄúKar gumazir manmagh…®n amizim? A m…®geima, am…®nim ko d…®pavs…®zim an akam barasi!‚Äù
\s1 Iesus gumazir pumuning…®n duar kuraba batoke
\r (Mak 5:1-17 ko Luk 8:26-37)
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus ghua Galilin ongarir dadarim…®n vong…®n itim…®n oto. Kar Gadaran nguazir as…®zim. Egha iza gumazir pumuning duar kuraba apazimning bato. Aning matmat…®n tong…®n ikegha izi. Egha aning bar ikuviz…®ma, gumazamiziba aning…®n atiatigha tuavir kam garuir puvat…®.
\v 29 Egha aning pamten dia ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n Otarim, n…® tizim ga damuasa? Dughiam t…®ghar…®, n…® kagh iz…® ga gas…®ghas…®ghasa?‚Äù
\v 30 Ez…® dar b…®zir ekiar mam mong saghon apa iti.
\v 31 Ez…® duar kurar kaba pamten Iesus gakaghora ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® e batosi, kamagh…®n n…® e ateght…®ma, e mang…® dar b…®zir munam…®n aven mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Ez…® Iesus me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mang…®.‚Äù Ez…®ma duar kuraba gumazir kamning ategha ghua dabar aven ghue. Ez…® dar b…®zir ekiar kam puv ara ghua davarir kurar mam…®n ghuaghira d…®pam apa bar ariagh…®re.
\v 33 Ez…® gumazir dabar gariba men ganigha ara ghue. Me ghua nguibar ekiam…®n otivigha bizir kabar gun gumazamizibagh eghari. Me uaghan gumazir duar kuraba apazazir pumuning bativizir bizibagh eghari.
\v 34 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguibar ekiar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba Iesus bagha izi. Me iza an gara a gakaghora ghaze, a men nguazim ategh danganir igharazitam…®n mang…®.
\c 9
\s1 Iesus gumazir soroghafariba aremezim ak…®riz…®, a ua dera
\r (Mak 2:1-12 ko Luk 5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus ua bot inigha uamategha ongarir dadarir vong…®n itim…®n ghua uan nguibam…®n oto.
\v 2 Ez…® me soroghafariba aremezir gumazir mam inigha a bagha izi. Gumazir kam akuriam…®n iti. Ez…® Iesus men garima, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itima, a kamagh…®n ar…®mariar gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan borim, n…®n navim bar am…®ragh ik…®. K…® n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada.‚Äù
\v 3 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir maba Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha kamagh uariv gia ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam God…®n danganim inigha kamagh…®n m…®gei.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus men n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha g…®vagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha n…®ghn…®zir kurar kaba uan navir averiabar dagh ami?
\v 5 K…® akar manam m…®k…®mam? Pura gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, k…® n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada. Egh uaghan gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n a m…®k…®man kogham, n…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh mang…®, egh ua deragh.
\v 6 Eght…® k…® ia kamagh…®n foghasa k…® ifonge, Gumazibar Otarim, a nguazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù Iesus kamagh…®n m…®kemegha soroghafariba aremezir gumazim…®n gara kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®!‚Äù
\v 7 Ez…® gumazir kam d…®kavigha uan d…®penim…®n ghu.
\v 8 Ez…®ma gumazamiziba arazir kam…®n ganigha bar d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha me God…®n ziam fa ghaze, ‚ÄúGodra gavgavir kam isa gumazibagh an…®di.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus Matyun diaz…®, an an g…®n zui
\r (Mak 2:13-17 ko Luk 5:27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus danganir kam ategha ghua garima, gumazir mam dag…®aba isir d…®penim…®n aperaghav iti. An ziam Matyu. Ez…® Iesus a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù Ez…®ma Matyu d…®kavigha an g…®n zui.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus d…®penim…®n ikiava apima, gumazir dag…®aba isiba ko gumazir arazir kurabagha amir av…®riba, me iza Iesus ko an suren gumaziba ko api.\f + \ft (9:10) Matyu osirava m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ab…®zir puvat…®. Me ti tinan d…®penim…®n api? Av…®rir ekiam ghaze, ti Matyun d…®penim (Mak 2:15) Marazi ghaze Iesus…®n d…®penim.\f*
\v 11 Ez…® Farisiba kamagh…®n gara Iesus…®n suren gumazibar azai, ‚ÄúIan Tisa, a tizim bagha dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba koma api?‚Äù\f + \ft (9:11) Farisiba bar akar gavgavir av…®ribagh amigha dar g…®n zui. Egha ghaze, gumazir manam men m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®n zuir puvat…®, egha arazir kuram gami, kamagh…®n me God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. Egh gumazir igharazitam gumazir kam ko ikegham, a uaghan God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. Farisiba uaghan ghaze, gumazir Rom…®n gavman bagha dag…®aba isiba, me zurara Rom…®n itir darazi ko iti, kamagh…®n me God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.\f*
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúAr…®mariaba puvat…®zir gumaziba, dokta bagha zuir puvat…®. Gumazir ar…®mariaba itibara, me dokta bagha zui.
\v 13 Ia mang…®, God…®n Ak…®nafarir osizirim da fofozim inigh. K…® ia ofa gamir arazibagh ifongezir puvat…®. Nan ifongiamra kara, ia arazir aghuibar gumazir igharazibar amu.‚Äù Egha Iesus ua me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumaziba bagha izezir puvat…®. K…® gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar d…®masa ize!‚Äù
\s1 Iesus dagheba ataghrazir arazim m…®gei
\r (Mak 2:18-22 ko Luk 5:33-39)
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n suren gumaziba iza, kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®, e ko Farisiba, e God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ataghrazima, n…®n suren gumaziba dagheba ataghrazir puvat…®?‚Äù
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa n…®ghn…®gh. Gumazitam amuim…®n ik…®s…® damu, uan adarazi ko ik…®t…®ma, me ti amughamugh, dagheba ataghraghan kogham. Puvat…®. Me dagheba ataghrazir dughiam iti. Gumazitaba g…®n iz…®, gumazir kam…®n aku mang…®t…®, a me ategham, eght…® dughiar kam…®n me dagheba ataghragham.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúGumazitam inir av…®zir igiatam inigha korotiar ghuritam porogha a isamizir puvat…®. A kamagh damigh g…®n korotiar kam rueght…®ma, inir av…®zir korotiar b…®b…®zim ap…®rizim akuvagh…®va korotiar ghurim bar anebigham.
\v 17 Eght…® gumazitam wain…®n igiam inigh, a is…®va as…®zir inir m…®sevir ghuritam agurighan kogham. A kamagh…®n damight…®ma, wain…®n d…®pam g…®n buva anangva as…®zir inir ghurir kam abight…®, wain…®n d…®pam nguazim giregham. Eght…® wain ko as…®zir inim v…®rara ikuvigham. Kamagh…®n me wain…®n igiam isa as…®zir inir igiabaram azui, eght…® aning v…®rara deraghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù\f + \ft (9:17) Judaba as…®zir memeba m…®soghava dar iniba isava dar d…®pav k…®v…®zibagh ami, egh me da inigh wain…®n d…®pabar aghuam. Wain…®n ov…®ziba, me igiamra da m…®rm…®righ…®va, da is…®va wain…®n m…®sevibar aghuam, egh aneteght…® a dughiatabar ikegham. Egh wain, onganim itir d…®pam…®n otogham. Wain memen inir kam…®n aven ik…® buv mang…®, egh memen inir ghurim abigham. Me wain…®n m…®sevir bar igiam a guright…®, wain derav…®ra ik…®, egh inir igiam abighan kogham.\f*
\s1 Iesus guivir aremezim gamiz…®, a ua d…®kafi. Egha uaghan amizir mam…®n ar…®mariam ag…®fa
\r (Mak 5:22-43 ko Luk 8:41-56)
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Iesus Jon…®n suren gumaziba ko m…®g…®av…®ra itima, gumazir dapanir ekiar mam iza Iesus…®n borogh…®n tevemning ap…®righa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivim dat…®r…®ghrama areme, ez…® n…® iz…® uan dafarim a dat…®ght…®ma a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus d…®kavigha an g…®n zuima, an suren gumaziba a ko zui.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…®ma amizir mam, a 12 plan azenibar, zurara ghuzim bati. Amizir kam Iesus…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n iza an korotiar av…®zim…®n suira.
\v 21 A kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ti an korotiar av…®zim…®n suiraght…®, nan ar…®mariam ti g…®vagham.‚Äù
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus ragha an gara a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan guivim, n…® navim bar am…®ragh ik…®. N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti, kamagh…®n, n…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa.‚Äù Dughiar kamra, amizir kam…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa.
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus ghua gumazir dapanir ekiar kam…®n d…®penim…®n otogha gari, amiziba ko gumaziba azia iti. Gumazir maba s…®ghabagh ivima, gumazamiziba azia n…®g…®nir ekiam gami.
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus me batogha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa d…®kavigh mang…®. Guivim aremezir puvat…®. An akui.‚Äù A kamagh…®n m…®geima, me a d…®pofi.
\v 25 A me batoghez…®, me azenan ghuez…®ma, Iesus aven ghua guivim…®n dafarim…®n suiraz…®ma, a d…®kafi.
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus amizir bizir kam…®n eghaghanim nguibaba bar dar ghu.
\s1 Iesus gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zir pumuning, ko gumazir m…®geir puvat…®zir mam, me gamiz…®, me ua dera
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus danganir kam ategha zuima, gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zir pumuning an g…®n iza kamagh…®n an dei, ‚ÄúN…® Devit…®n Otarim, n…® gan apangkufigh.‚Äù\f + \ft (9:27) Judaba ghaze, Gumazir God ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezim, Atrivim Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n otivam. Gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zir kamning n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus ikia ghaze, Israelba gumazir kamra m…®zuai. Kamagh…®n aning dia ghaze, ‚ÄúDevit…®n Otarim.‚Äù\f*
\v 28 A ghua d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®ma, gumazir kamning a bagha izima, a kamagh…®n aning…®n azai. ‚ÄúGua bizir k…® damuamin kam, gua n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti, o puvat…®?‚Äù Ez…® aning ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, Ekiam ga n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti.‚Äù
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus uan dafarim isa aning…®n damazimning gat…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Kamagh…®n, gua ua gan.‚Äù
\v 30 Ez…® aning…®n damaziba kuiaghrez…®, aning ua gari. Ez…® Iesus aning…®n anogorogha aning…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua tong bizir gua batozir kam tav…®n m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù
\v 31 Puvat…®. Aning ghua Iesus amizir arazir aghuir kam…®n gun bar distrigh…®n kam…®n itir gumazamizibav keme.
\p 
\v 32 Gumazir kamning Iesus ategha zuima, gumazamiziba m…®geir puvat…®zir gumazir mam inigha, Iesus bagha izi. Gumazir kam, duar kuraba a gapasa.
\v 33 Ez…® Iesus an duar kuraba batoghez…®ma, gumazir kam ua m…®gei. Ez…® gumazamiziba d…®gavir kuram gamua ghaze, ‚ÄúFom…®ra, kantri Israel…®n aven, bizir kamagh garitam otozir puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 34 Ez…® Farisiba ghaze, ‚ÄúA duar kurabar gumazir dapanim…®n gavgavim…®n duar kuraba batosi.‚Äù
\ms1 Iesus ingangarim isa uan suren gumazibagh an…®di.
\mr (Sapta 9:35-10:42)
\s1 Iesus gumazamizibar apangkufi
\p 
\v 35 Ez…® Iesus nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar doziba bar dagh arua, men God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven ghua, gumazamizibar sure gami. A God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akam me m…®g…®a men ar…®mariaba ko os…®mt…®zir men namnabar itiba bar da gefi.
\v 36 A gumazamizir av…®rir dafam…®n garima, men n…®ghn…®ziba tintinibar itima, me os…®mt…®zibar aven arua, mati sipsipba ghuaviba puvat…®zir mogh…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a bar men apangkufi.
\v 37 Egha a uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDagher bar av…®rim anigha g…®vagha azenim…®n iti. Ez…® ingangarir gumazir da iniamin av…®riba puvat…®.
\v 38 Kamagh…®n, ia azenir kam…®n ghuavim…®n azangs…®ght…®, a ingangarir gumaziba amangt…®ma, me an azenim…®n mang…®, dagheba iniam.‚Äù
\c 10
\s1 12 plan suren gumazibar ziaba
\r (Mak 3:13-19 ko Luk 6:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumazir 12 plan diaz…®, me izima, a duar kuraba batogh…®va ar…®mariar gumazamizibar itibar ak…®ramin gavgavim me gan…®ngi.
\v 2 Aposel…®n 12 plan ziabara kara: Men faragha zuim, Saimon, an ziar mam Pita, ko an dozim Andru. Ko Jems, Sebedin otarim, ko an dozim Jon,
\v 3 Filip ko Bartolomyu ko Tomas ko Matyu, a gumazir dag…®aba isim, ko Jems, an Alfius…®n otarim, ko Tadius,
\v 4 ko Saimon, a marazi ko me Selot…®n ik…®zim…®n iti, koma Judas Iskariot, gumazir Iesus isava, apanibagh an…®ngizim.
\s1 Iesus ingangarim isa, 12 plan aposelbagh an…®di
\r (Mak 6:7-13 ko Luk 9:1-5)
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus gumazir 12 plan kaba amaga akar kam me gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba bagh mangan mark…®. Egh Samarian nguibar ekiabar mangan mark…®.\f + \ft (10:5) Kar Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ruarir mam, Namba 2. Akar 10:5-42…®n itiba, da suren gumaziba God…®n akam akun darut…®ma arazir me bativamibav gei.\f*
\v 6 Ia sipsip…®n ovengezir Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n itiba bagh mang…®.
\v 7 Ia mang…®, akam akun suam, ‚ÄòGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam a rogh…®ra izegha g…®fa.‚Äô
\v 8 Ia mang…® gumazamizibar ar…®mariaba ag…®va; egh gumazir aremeziba me damut…® me ua d…®kav, egh lepa itir gumazibar amut…® me ua zuegh, egh duar kurar gumazamizibagh apazaziba da batogh. Bizir ia inizim ia purama a ini, ia a g…®vezezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®ra ia pura a is…® gumazamizibar an…®ng. Ia a bagh ivezitam inian kogham.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúIa gol tam o silvan dag…®atam o kapan dag…®atam inigh mangan mark…®.
\v 10 Ia daruamin dughiabar, ia biam…®taritam inian mark…®. Egh ia siotiar pumuning, o dagarir asuatam o difizitam inigh mangan kogham. Bar puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, ingangarir gumaziba, me damamin dagheba, me da is…® me dan…®ng.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEgh ia nguibar ekiatam…®n mangam, o nguibar dozitam…®n angs…®va, ia deraghv…®ra azangs…®gh fogh, gumazir manam an arazir aghuibagh amua egha bar dera. Egh ia gumazir kam ko ik…® mang…®, dughiar ia nguibar kam ategh mangamim.
\v 12 Egh d…®penir ia aven zuim, ia kamagh…®n an aven itir daraziv k…®m, ‚ÄòGod deragh ia damuam.‚Äô
\v 13 Egh gumazamizir d…®penir kam…®n itiba, ia gifuegh…®va ia inight…®, ia me ko ik…®, egh ia God…®n azaraght…®, ian navir am…®r…®zim me ko ik…®. Me ian aghuaght…®, ia uan navir am…®r…®zir kam me da uam a inigh.
\v 14 Egh gumazitam ia inigh uan d…®penim…®n mangan aghuagh, egh ian akam baraghan koght…®, eght…® dughiar ia d…®penir kam o nguibar kam ataghraghamim, ia uan dagaribar itir m…®neziba ap…®sigh.\f + \ft (10:14) Suren gumaziba arazir kam damut…®ma, nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamiziba gan fogh suam, me arazir kuram gami. Mak 6:11 ko Aposel 13:51…®n gan.\f*
\v 15 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, God gumazamizibar arazir kuraba tuis…®gh…®va, eght…® gumazamizir nguibar kam…®n itiba iniamin os…®mt…®zim, a Sodom ko Gomora uan arazir kuraba bagh inizim…®n os…®mt…®zim bar a gafiragham.‚Äù
\s1 Os…®mt…®zir av…®riba otivam
\r (Mak 13:9-13 ko Luk 21:12-17)
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oragh, k…® sipsipbar m…®n ia isava afiar atiabar tong…®n ia amadi. Eght…® ia kuruzibar araziba iniva derav…®ra bizibagh n…®ghn…®gh ia g…®n dar amu. Egh ia kuarazir bunbabar arazibar amu, kamagh…®n ia arazir kuratam damus…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.
\v 17 Ia deraghv…®ra uari bagh gan. Me ian suiragh, uan kaunselbar damazibar ia is…® kotiam dar…®gh…®va, egh uan God ko m…®geir d…®penibar ia fozorogham.
\v 18 Egh me nan ziam bang…®n, ia iniva gavmanba ko atrivibar damazibar mangam. Egh ia akar aghuim…®n gun gumazir ekiar kabav k…®m. Egh uaghan Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba, ia uaghan me m…®k…®m.
\v 19 Egh me ia inigh kotiam…®n mang…®t…®ma ia atiating kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, ‚ÄòE m…®g…®r…®g…®ar manatam damuam? O, e manmagh…®n men akaba ikarvagham?‚Äô Puvat…®. God uab…® dughiar kam…®n ia m…®k…®mamin akaba ia dan…®ngam.
\v 20 Ia uari m…®k…®man kogham, puvat…®. Ian Afeziam…®n Duamra, ian akatoribar aghu m…®k…®mam.
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúGumaziba uan aveghbuaba is…® kot dar…®gh…®va, egh me m…®sogh…®va ar…®m…®ghr…®s…® me m…®k…®mam. Eght…® afeziaba kamagh…®ra uan boribar amuam. Eght…® boriba uan afeziaba ko amebaba paz…® me damuva, me m…®soght…®, me ar…®m…®ghr…®s…®, gumazibav k…®mam.
\v 22 Eght…® gumaziba bar nan ziam bang…®n ian ikuvigham. Me bar paza ia damut…®, eght…® gumazamizir gavgavigh ik…® mang…® dughiar abuananam…®n otoghamiba, God men akurvagham.
\v 23 Egh gumazamiziba nguibar ekiar mam…®n paz…® ia damut…®, ia ar…® nguibar ekiar igharazim…®n ang…®. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia Israel…®n nguibar ekiar kabar aven damuamin ingangariba, da g…®vaghan koght…®ma Gumazibar Otarim uamategham.
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúSuren gumazitam uan tisa gafirazir puvat…®, ez…® ingangarir gumazitam uan gumazir ekiam gafiraghan kogham.
\v 25 Eght…® suren gumazim uan tisan m…®n otogh…®va, egh deragham. Egh ingangarir gumazim uan ekiam…®n m…®n otogh…®va, a uaghan deragham. Me ziar kam Belsebul a isa d…®penim…®n ghuavim gat…®, ez…® e kamagh…®n fo, me uaghan bar ziar kuraba da is…®va an adarazi dar…®gham.‚Äù\f + \ft (10:25) Ziam Belselbul, a Satan…®n ziar mam. Matyu 12:22-28…®n gan.\f*
\s1 Gumaziba Godrama atiatingam
\r (Luk 12:2-7)
\p 
\v 26 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúGumaziba paz…® ia damut…®, ia men atiatingan mark…®. Bizir mogomebar aven ikeziba, bar azenim giram. Eght…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aven ikeziba, gumaziba bar dagh fogham.
\v 27 K…® m…®tatem…®n ia m…®kemezir akaba, ia angazangarim…®n dav k…®m. Egh sighsirir akar ia oraghiziba, ia mang…® d…®penir nogoribar tuiv dar gun gumazamizibav k…®m.
\v 28 Ia gumazir namnar k…®nibav sozibar atiatingan mark…®. Me ian duabav sueghan kogham. Puvat…®. Ia Godram atiating. A namnam ko duam uaghara aning is…®va avim…®n aning gas…®ghas…®ghamin gavgavim iti.
\v 29 Ia fo, gumaziba kuarazir dozir pumuning wan toean v…®rara aning givezegham. Ez…® ian Afeziam deraghav…®ra kuarazir kabar gari. Ian Afeziam ifueghan koght…®ma, kuarazir katam nguazim giran kogham.
\v 30 Egha God uaghan ian dapanir ar…®ziba dar pone, egha a bar deraghav…®ra ia g…®fo.
\v 31 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia atiatingan mark…®. Ia kuarazir dozir kabar m…®n itir puvat…®. Ia God…®n damazim…®n bar ekevegha dagh afira.‚Äù
\s1 E Iesus…®n adarazir ik…®va aghums…®ghan kogham
\r (Luk 12:8-9)
\p 
\v 32 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir manam gumazamizibar damazim…®n ghaze, a nan anav, eght…® k…® uaghan uan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim…®n damazim…®n m…®k…®m suam, gumazir kam a nan anav.
\v 33 Eght…® gumazitam gumazamizibar damazim…®n m…®k…®m suam, a nan anav puvat…®, eght…® k…® uaghan uan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim…®n damazim…®n m…®k…®m suam, gumazir kam nan anav puvat…®.‚Äù
\s1 Ia Iesus bar a gifuegh, faragh anet…®gh
\r (Luk 12:51-53 ko 14:26-27)
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, k…® navir vam…®ran arazim inigha, nguazir kam…®n ize. Ez…® ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. K…® adariba ko m…®doroziba g…®vasa izezir puvat…®. Puvat…®. K…® m…®dorozir sabam inigha ize.
\v 35 K…® bizir kam bagha ize, k…® gumazim damut…®, a uan afeziam…®n apanim…®n ikiam. Eght…® guivim uan amebam…®n apanim…®n ikiam, eght…® amizir pam…®n itim uan ivozir amebam…®n apanim…®n ikiam.
\v 36 Gumazim…®n anababa uari, an apanim ik…®va, an ikuvigham.
\p 
\v 37 ‚ÄúGumazir manam uan afeziam ko amebam bar aning gifongegha, faragha aning ar…®gha, egha na isa g…®n ar…®gha, a guizbang…®ra nan namakam puvat…®. Egha gumazir manam uan otarim o guivim bar aning gifongegha, faragha aning ar…®gha, egha na isa g…®n ar…®si, a nan namakam puvat…®.
\v 38 Egh gumazir manam uan ter ighuvir an ovengamim a gisaghpugha nan g…®n zuir puvat…®, a nan namakam puvat…®.\f + \ft (10:38) Rom…®n gavman, nguibar gumazir igharaziba koma pura ingangarir gumazir arazir kurabagh amiziba, me me isava ter ighuvibar me dui. Me faragh uan ter ighuvim gisaghpugh mang…® danganir me m…®seviz…®m…®n otogham. Iesus akar is…®n zuir kam…®n uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, tina guizbang…®ra an suren gumazim…®n otivs…®va uaghan ovengamin n…®ghn…®zim ik…®.\f*
\v 39 Ez…® gumazir manam derav…®ra uan ik…®r…®m…®rim anek…®riva, gumazir kam g…®n ikian kogham. Eght…® gumazir manam na bagha n…®ghn…®gha uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ak…®rizir puvat…®, a guizbang…®ra ik…®r…®m…®rim bativam.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazir manam Krais…®n adarazi deragha me gami, a uan ivezir aghuim iniam
\r (Mak 9:41)
\p 
\v 40 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir manam ia inigha arazir aghuibar ia gami, a na inigha arazir aghuibar na gami. Egha gumazir na inizim, a God…®n na amadaz…® k…® izezim a ini.
\v 41 Eght…® gumazitam suam, k…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazitam…®n akurvaghasa, egha God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam…®n akua uan d…®penim…®n ghua an akurvagha deragha a gami, God gumazir kam, bizir aghuir an akam inigha izir gumaziba isiba, God da is…®va a dan…®ngam. Eght…® gumazitam suam, k…® gumazir aghuitam…®n akurvaghasa, egha gumazir aghuitam inigha uan d…®penim…®n ghua deraghav…®ra an akurvaki, God gumazir kam uaghan, bizir aghuir gumazir aghuiba isiba, God da is…®va a dan…®ngam.
\v 42 Eght…® tav suam, k…® Iesus…®n suren gumazitam…®n akurvaghs…®, egh pura d…®par orangt…®zim a is…®va suren gumazir ziaba puvat…®zir katam a danigam, bar guizbang…®ra k…® ia m…®gei, God gumazir kam ivezir aghuim a dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\c 11
\ms1 Iesus bar tinara
\mr (Sapta 11:1-16:20)
\s1 Jon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, uan suren gumaziba amadaz…® me Iesus bagha ghue
\r (Luk 7:18-35)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus akar kaba uan 12 plan suren gumazibagh ganiga, egha danganir kam ategha nguibar igharazibar ghua men sure gamua God…®n akam me m…®k…®ri.
\p 
\v 2 Jon kalabus…®n ikia kamagh…®n God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim…®n ingangariba baregha uan suren gumaziba a bagha me amada.
\v 3 Egha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia mang…® kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azang, ‚ÄúTi n…®rara, gumazir God faragha amangasa m…®kemezim? O, e ti ua gumazir igharazitam m…®zuamam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus men azangs…®ziba ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, bizir ia garava orazibar gun Jon m…®k…®m suam,
\v 5 ‚ÄòGumazir damazir okav…®r…®ziba ua gari, ez…® gumazir suer am…®r…®ziba uam arui. Ez…® gumazir lepa itiba ua zuegha dera, ez…® gumazir kuarir orazir puvat…®ziba uam orasi. Ez…® ovengezir gumaziba ua d…®kavima, ez…® gumazir onganarazibagh amiba akar aghuim barasi.‚Äô\f + \ft (11:5) God…®n akam inigha izezir gumazim Aisaia fom…®ra ghaze, God uan adarazi Israelian akurvaghamim dughiam, arazir kaba otivam. Aisaia 35:1-7 ko 61:1-4…®n gan.\f*
\v 6 Gumazir nan ganigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim, an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®v…®ra ik…®, eght…® an navir averiam deraght…® a bar akuegham!‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Jon…®n suren gumaziba an ategha ghuez…®ma, Iesus an gun gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghua tizim…®n ganasa ghue? Ia ti ghurunir am…®nim vaim…®n ganasa ghue? Puvat…®.
\v 8 Ia tizimra ganasa ghue? Ia ti gumazir korotiar aghuiba aghuiz…®tam…®n ganasa ghue? Puvat…®. Gumazir korotiar aghuiba azuiba, atrivibar d…®penibar iti.
\v 9 Ez…® ia tizim…®n ganasa ghue? Ia God…®n akam inigha izir gumazitam…®n ganasa ghue? Bar guizbang…®ra! Ki ia m…®gei, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igharaziba, bar me gafira.
\v 10 Gumazir kam baghav…®ra God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa oragh. K…® uan abuir gumazim amadaght…®ma, a faragh mang…®va n…® bagh tuavim ak…®ram.‚Äô
\v 11 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, Jon Gumazibar Ruer Gumazim, gumazir nguazim…®n itiba, bar me gafira. Ez…® gumazir God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikia ziaba bar puvat…®zim, a bar Jon gafira.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄúJon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, gumazir kuraba God Bizibagh Ativamin Arazim iniasa puv ingara m…®sosi. Egha me m…®dorozir arazir anabar igharazibagh amua, egha os…®mt…®zir av…®riba a gan…®di.\f + \ft (11:12) Grigh…®n akam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam me deragha aneb…®ghizir puvat…®. Marazi n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Iesus ghaze, gumazitaba otivigh Rom…®n gavman ko m…®sogh me batuegh egh…®va God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam damight…®ma, a nguazim…®n ikiam.\f*
\v 13 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar osiziriba ko Moses Osirizir Araziba, da God…®n akam akura iza Jon otozir dughiam…®n tu.
\v 14 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dar akam baraghs…® ifuegh, a baragh, ‚ÄòGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elaiza izam,‚Äô kar a Jon baghav…®ra m…®gei.
\v 15 Tina kuarimning iti, an oragh.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEght…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamizibar arazibar gun m…®k…®ms…®va akar is…®n zuir manam m…®k…®mam? Me boribar m…®n biziba amadir danganim…®n apiaghav ikia uarir dei,
\b
\q1 
\v 17 ‚ÄòE ia bagha marvibagh ivima,
\q2 ia ighian aghua.
\q1 Ez…® e ongerakar am…®r…®zibagh amima,
\q2 ia azir puvat…®.‚Äô
\b
\m 
\v 18 Dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumaziba, borir kabar m…®n ami. Jon izava pamten apir puvat…®ghava wain…®n d…®paba apir puvat…®z…®ma, me ghaze, ‚ÄòDuar kuraba a gapasa.‚Äô
\v 19 Ez…® Gumazibar Otarim izava dagheba ko wain…®n d…®paba api. Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄòIa gan, a gumazir puv daghem ko wain…®n d…®pam apim. Egha a dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, a men roroabagh amua me ko iti.‚Äô Me kamagh…®n m…®geima, gumazamiziba men gara fo, God…®n fofozim a guizbang…®ra bizim.‚Äù
\s1 Navibagh irazir puvat…®zir gumazamiziba, me bar ikuvigham
\r (Luk 10:13-15)
\p 
\v 20 Iesus nguibar ekiar mabar mirakel…®n av…®ribagh amiz…® me uan navibagh irazir puvat…®. Ez…® Iesus dughiar kam…®n nguibar kabar gumazamizibar atara ghaze,
\v 21 ‚ÄúIa Korasin…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba, Iavzika! Ia kuram iniam. Ia Betsaidan nguibam…®n itir adarazi, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham. Gumazitam Tair…®n nguibam ko Saidon…®n nguibam…®n ghua, mirakel…®n k…® amiziba men tong…®n dagh amighai, Tair ko Saidon…®n itir darazi ti fom…®ra navibagh iragha, egha azir adiariba aghuigha, averenim gapiava aguruava, egha uan arazir kam…®n uari akakagha ghaze, me uan arazir kuraba ataki.
\v 22 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir ia iniamim, an os…®mt…®zir Tair ko Saidon iniamim gafiragham.
\v 23 Ez…® ia Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n itir darazi, ia ghaze, ia uari fegh God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiam, a? Bar puvat…®, God ia akunight…® ia Hel…®n avim mag…®ram. Ez…® gumazitam ti Sodom…®n nguibam…®n ghua mirakel…®n k…® ian tong…®n amizibagh amiz…®, kamagh…®n Sodom ti ikiav…®ra ikiai.
\v 24 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir ia iniamim, an os…®mt…®zir Sodom inizim gafiragham.‚Äù
\s1 Ia na bagh iz…®va aghuvsazim iniam
\r (Luk 10:21-22)
\p 
\v 25 Egha dughiar kam…®n Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziam, n…® nguazim ko overiam gativazir Ekiam! N…® fofozim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itir gumaziba bizir kaba men modo, egha boribar m…®n itir gumazibar aka. Kamagh…®n k…® n…® m…®nabi.
\v 26 Guizbang…®ra Afeziam, n…® uan ifongiam…®n kamagh…®n ami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Egha Iesus ua kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan Afeziam biziba bar ada isa nan dafarim gat…®. Ez…® gumazitam Otarim g…®fozir puvat…®. Afeziam uab…®ra a g…®fo. Egha tav Afeziam g…®fozir puvat…®. Otarim uab…®ra, koma gumazir Otarim ifuegha Afeziam isava men akaziba, merara Afeziam g…®fo.
\v 28 Ia, gumazir ingangarir ekiabagh amua os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateriba, ia bar mogh…®ra na bagh iz…®. Eght…® k…® aghuvsazim ia dan…®ngam.
\v 29 Ia na da fofozim iniva nan m…®g…®r…®g…®abar apengan ik…®, egha mati temer ruarir me bulmakauning…®n tuemning gat…®z…®ma aning uaning inigha ingangarim gami mogh…®n, ia nan apengan ik…®. Ia na g…®fo, k…® uan navir averiam…®n aven uab…® d…®kab…®ragha, egha k…® gumazibar asughasusi. Egh k…® ia damut…® ia aghuvsazim iniam.
\v 30 Ter ruarir k…® ian tuebagh ar…®zim, ia a gumuam, ez…® bizir k…® aterim an osemezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\c 12
\s1 Farisiba Sabat…®n dughiam bagha Iesus adoghadosi
\r (Mak 2:23-28 ko Luk 6:1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus Sabat…®n dughiar mam…®n uan suren gumaziba ko, raiz…®n m…®n garir dagher mam wit, an azenir ekiam…®n torim…®n zui. An suren gumaziba m…®tiriam men azima, me wit…®n ov…®zir maba kuara da api.
\v 2 Ez…® Farisiba men ganigha kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan, arazir n…®n suren gumaziba amim, en Judabar Araziba ghaze, me Sabat…®n dughiam…®n dar amuan kogham.‚Äù\f + \ft (12:2) Moses Osirizir Araziba, Sabat…®n ingangaribar amuasa Judabar anogorosi. Me Sabat…®n damuan koghamin ingangarir mam, a dagher and…®ziba iniamin ingangarim. N…®, Kisim Bek 34:21…®n gan. Farisiba ghaze, Iesus…®n suren gumaziba arazir kam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.\f*
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa ti Devit fom…®ra amizir arazim…®n eghaghanim…®n ganizir puvat…®? Devit dughiar kam…®n uan adarazi ko m…®tiriam men azi,
\v 4 ez…® Devit God…®n Averpenim…®n aven ghua me ofa damuasa at…®zir bret inigha uan adarazi ko me aneme. E fo, me bret…®n kam raman kogham. Puvat…®, Moses Osirizir Araziba ghaze, ofa gamir gumazibara bret…®n kam ramam.
\v 5 Egha ia ti Moses Osirizir Arazibar ganizir puvat…®, a ghaze, ofa gamir gumaziba me God…®n D…®penim…®n aven Sabat…®n me ingaram. Me ingara, egha God…®n damazim arazir kuraba puvat…®.
\v 6 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, bizir God…®n D…®penim gafirazim a kagh iti.
\v 7 Egha God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® apangkuvir arazim gifonge, k…® ofan k…®nibagh ifongezir puvat…®.‚Äô Ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam g…®fogha, egha ia pura os…®mt…®ziba gumazir aghuibagh ar…®ghan koghai.
\v 8 Ez…® Gumazibar Otarim a Sabat…®n dughiam…®n Ekiam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus gumazir dafarir ekonezim Sabat…®n dughiam…®n a gamiz…®ma a dera
\r (Mak 3:1-6 ko Luk 6:6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Egha Iesus danganir kam ategha nguibar ekiar mam…®n ghua God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghu.
\v 10 Ez…® gumazir mam d…®penir kam…®n aven iti, an dafarir mam bar ekone. Ez…® gumazir maba Iesus akatam a gasasa, egha kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúMoses Osirizir Araziba manmagh…®n m…®gei? E Sabat…®n dughiam…®n gumazibar ar…®mariabar ak…®ram, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan tong…®n itir gumazitam, a sipsip…®n mam ik…®t…®ma, egh Sabat…®n dughiam…®n sipsip…®n kam mozitam…®n mag…®r…®ghtima, eght…® a ti mang…® uam anesigham, o?
\v 12 E fo, gumazim…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim sipsip…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim bar a gafira! Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, e fo Moses Osirizir Araziba en amamangat…®z…®, e Sabat…®n dughiam…®n gumazibar akurvagham.‚Äù
\v 13 Egha a gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim onegh.‚Äù Ez…® gumazim uan dafarim onez…®ma an dafarim dafarir vuem…®n m…®n, ua dera.
\v 14 Ez…® Farisiba d…®kavigha God ko m…®geir d…®penim ategha uari akuvagha Iesus m…®soghasa tuaviba buri.\f + \ft (12:14) Farisiba ghaze, ar…®mariaba agevir arazim uaghan ingangarir mam, egha Sabat…®n arazir kaba uaghan dar anogoroke. Ez…® Farisiba gari, Iesus Sabat…®n ar…®mariaba agevi, kamagh…®n me a baseme, egha a m…®sueghasa tuaviba buri. Luk 13:14 ko Jon 5:16-18…®n gan.\f*
\s1 Iesus a guizbang…®ra God…®n ingangarir gumazim
\p 
\v 15 Farisiba Iesus m…®soghasa tuaviba burima, a men arazir kam g…®foghava nguibar ekiar kam ategha ghu. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba an g…®n zuima, a men ar…®mariaba bar dar k…®rima, me ua dera.
\v 16 Ez…® a men anogorogha ghaze, me an gun igharazibav k…®man markiam.
\v 17 A God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaian m…®g…®r…®g…®am damut…®, an otivasa, egha a kamagh…®n ami. Aisaia kamagh…®n m…®keme,
\b
\q1 
\v 18 ‚ÄúKar nan ingangarir gumazim, k…® uab…® anem…®sefe,
\q2 egha k…® bar a g…®fuegha, a bagha bar akonge.
\q1 K…® uan Duam a dat…®ght…®, a Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba me m…®k…®m suam,
\q2 dughiar k…® men araziba tuis…®ghamim otivam.
\q1 
\v 19 Gumazir kam atar dagarvaghan kogham.
\q2 Me tuavibar an tiarim baraghan kogham.
\q1 
\v 20 Egh ighurunir gavgaviba puvat…®gha d…®p…®rasava amim, a bar d…®p…®righan kogham,
\q2 egha lam…®n pamtem isir puvat…®zim, an anemungeghan kogham.
\q1 Egh kamagh…®ra, a gavgaviba puvat…®zir gumazamizibar asughasugh derav…®ra me damuam.
\q1 A kamagh…®ra damu mang…®, arazir aghuiba dar amut…®ma
\q2 da bar azenim giramin dughiam otogham.
\q1 
\v 21 Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®va
\q2 uarir akurvaghs…®va a m…®zuam ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Me ghaze, Iesus Belsebul…®n gavgavim…®n ingari
