\p 
\v 33 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® temer aghuim ik…®t…®ma, an ov…®zir aghuiba uaghan ikiam. Egh n…® temer kuram ik…®t…®ma, an ov…®zir kuraba uaghan ikiam.
\v 34 Ia gumazir kuraba, ia kuruzir kurabar m…®n iti! Egh manmagh m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuitam m…®kemegham? Puvat…®. Ian navir averiabagh iz…®vazir n…®ghn…®ziba dar amara ian akatoribar otifi.
\v 35 Gumazir aghuim, an navir averiam…®n aven n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba a giz…®fa, egha amara arazir aghuibagh ami. Gumazir kuram, an navir averiam…®n aven n…®ghn…®zir kuraba a giz…®fa, egha amara arazir kurabagh ami.
\v 36 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, God…®n Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, a pura men m…®g…®r…®g…®ar n…®ghn…®ziba puvat…®ziba bagh vaghvagh men azangs…®gh…®va, me tuis…®gham.
\v 37 God g…®n n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh n…®ghn…®gh…®va, n…® tuis…®gham, eght…® n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abara n…® damut…®ma, God gumazir aghuim o gumazir kuram n…® dar…®gham.‚Äù
\s1 Me mirakel…®n tam damuasa Iesus…®n azai
