\p 
\v 38 Ez…®ma Judabar arazibagh fozir gumazir maba ko Farisin maba kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, n…® mirakel…®n arazitam damut…®, an otoght…® e fogh suam, n…® guizbang…®ra God…®n ingangarim gami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizir dughiar kam…®n itiba, me bar gumazamizir kuraba! Egha me guizbang…®ra God baghav…®ra itir puvat…®. Me zurara mirakel…®n tam…®n ganasa. Me tam…®n ganighan kogham. Puvat…®. God mirakel…®n arazir vam…®ra men akagham. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jona batozir mirakel…®n kamra, me an ganam.
\v 40 E fo, Jona arueba ko d…®magarir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n osirir ekiar mam…®n navir averiam…®n ike. Ez…® kamagh…®ra Gumazibar Otarim arueba ko d…®magarir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n nguazim…®n aven ikiam.\f + \ft (12:40) N…® Jona 1:17…®n gan. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jona, uaghan Jonan gun m…®g…®a ghaze, a ghua nguibar ekiam Niniven ghua akam akurima gumazamiziba a baregha uan navibagh ira.\f*
\v 41 Eght…® God Kot…®n Dughiam…®n, Niniven gumazamiziba d…®kavigh ian arazir kurabar gun m…®k…®mam. Ia fo, Nineven adarazi Jona akunizir akam baregha navibagh ira. Ez…® Gumazir dat…®r…®gh…®n ian tong…®n itir mam, a bar Jona gafira!
\v 42 Fom…®ra Seban Atrivir Amizim nguazir kam…®n saghon ikegha Solomon…®n fofozir aghuim…®n akaba baraghasa ize. Ez…® gumazir mam bar Solomon gafiragha ian tong…®n iti. Kamagh…®n, God gumazamizibar Kotim Damuamin Dughiam…®n, Seban Atrivir Amizim tugh dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamizibar arazir kurabar gun m…®k…®mam.‚Äù
\s1 Duar kuram uamategha ize
