\v 28 ‚ÄúEz…® a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòNan apanir mam arazir kam gami.‚Äô Ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba an azai, ‚ÄòN…® ifueght…®ma, e mang…® ogher kam suagham?‚Äô
\v 29 Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄòMark…®. Ia ogher kuraba asighsuva, uaghan witba asiam. Kamagh…®n da asian mark…®.
\v 30 Ia da ateght…®ma da mar witba ko aghung, mang…® dagheba iniamin dughiam…®n otogh. Eght…® k…® ingangarir kam damuamin gumaziba kamagh me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúIa ogher kurar kam faragh anes…®va a dapongs…®va an ik…®zibar amu. Egh…®va ia witba iniva da akuvagh da is…®va nan dagher d…®penim dar…®gham.‚Äù‚Äô‚Äù
\s1 Mastet…®n ov…®zim…®n akar is…®n zuim
