\v 34 Iesus gumazamizibav geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, an akar is…®n zuibara da akuri. Egha a m…®g…®r…®g…®atam abigha me m…®kemezir puvat…®, an akar is…®n zuibara me m…®gei.
\v 35 Fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim kamagh m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® akar is…®n zuibara ia m…®k…®mam. Bizir maba, nguazir kam otozir dughiam…®n da modogha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu, ez…® k…® bizir kabar eghaghanim damuasa.‚Äù Iesus akar kam damut…® an otivasa, kamagh…®n an akar is…®n zuir kabagh ami.
