\v 37 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir wit…®n ov…®zir aghuiba akunizim, a Gumazibar Otarim.
\v 38 Azenim, kar nguazir kam. Wit…®n ov…®zir aghuiba, kar gumazamizir God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikiamiba. Ogher kuraba, kar Satan…®n gumazamiziba.
\v 39 Apanir ogher kuram akunizim, a Satan. Dagheba iniamin dughiam, kar nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam. Ez…® enselba, me dagheba iniamin ingangarir gumaziba.
\v 40 Egha mati gumaziba ogher kuraba akuva dagh aboi, kamagh…®ra enselba nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam…®n, me kamagh…®n damuam.
\v 41 Gumazibar Otarim uan enselba amadaght…®, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven itir gumazamiziba, men tong…®n itir gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba ko gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®ziba, enselba bar me batuegham.
\v 42 Egh me me is…®va, avir ekiam me kunigham. Eght…® me avir kam…®n ik…®va arang…®va atariba kuskugham.
\v 43 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n gumazamizir aghuiba uan Afeziam Bizibagh Ativamin Nguibam…®n aven ik…®, me aruem…®n m…®n s…®gham. Tina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù
\s1 Bizir ivezir bar p…®n kozim…®n akar is…®n zuim
\p 
\v 44 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, me bizir ivezir bar p…®n kozim isava azenim…®n nguazim…®n aven a modo. Ez…® gumazir mam a bato, egha uam anevara. Egha bar akuegha, ghua uan biziba bar da amaga, dag…®aba inigha ghua, azenir kam itir nguazim givese.‚Äù
\s1 Manmaniar ivezir bar p…®n koz…®m…®n akar is…®n zuim
\p 
\v 45 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, dag…®ar ingangarim gamir gumazir mam. Gumazir kam manmaniar bar aghuiba bagha ruiagha arui.
\v 46 Egha ghua manmaniar bar aghuir ivezir bar p…®n kozir mam bato. Egha ghua uan biziba bar dag…®aba bagha da amada. Egha ghua manmaniar bar aghuir kam givese.‚Äù
\s1 Ivem…®n akar is…®n zuim
\p 
\v 47 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúAkar is…®n zuir mam kamak…®n. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, me ivem akuniz…® a d…®par averiam…®n ghuaghira, osirir guar av…®riba, dar akome.
\v 48 Ez…® ivem iz…®vaz…®ma, me a gekuigha d…®par dadarim gat…®. Egha me apiagha osirir aghuiba m…®s…®va da isava itaribav k…®ri. Egha osirir kuraba me da makuri.
\v 49 Nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam kamagh…®ra. Enselba iz…®va gumazir kuraba, gumazir aghuibar tong…®n me am…®s…®vam.
\v 50 Egh me me is…®va, avir ekiam…®n me akunam. Eght…® me avir ekiar kam…®n ik…®, arang…®va atariba kuskugham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 51 Egha Iesus uan suren gumazibar azai, ‚ÄúIa ti akar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fo?‚Äù Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúAre.‚Äù
\v 52 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir manam Judan arazibagh fozir gumazim…®n ikia, egha g…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akabar m…®ngariba a dagh fo, egha a mati d…®penir mam…®n ghuavim…®n m…®n ami. A uan d…®penim…®n aven ghua bizir igiaba ko ghuriba bar da isava azenim gar…®si.‚Äù
\s1 Nasaret…®n itir darazi Iesus…®n aghuagha, ak…®ribagh ragha a gasara
\r (Mak 6:1-6 ko Luk 4:16-30)
\p 
\v 53 Iesus akar kaba akunigha g…®vagha danganir kam ategha
\v 54 uan nguibam…®n ghu. A ghua men God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghugha, God…®n akam…®n gumazamizibar sure gami. Ez…® me an akam baragha d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam managh fofozir kam ini? Egha a mirakelba manmagh…®n dagh ami?
\v 55 E a g…®fo, a d…®penibar ingarir gumazim…®n otarim, ez…® Maria an amebam. Ez…® Jems ko Josep ko Saimon ko Judas, me an doziba.
\v 56 An buaramiziba bar kagh e ko iti. Kamagh…®n a manmagh bizir kabanagh damut…®, da otivam.‚Äù
\v 57 Me kamagh m…®g…®a navir averiaba Iesus…®n ikufi. Ez…® Iesus me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, nguibar igharazibar ziam otifi. Egha a uan nguibam ko uan d…®penim…®n aven, a ziaba puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 58 Me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a nguibar kam…®n mirakel…®n av…®ribagh amizir puvat…®.
\c 14
\s1 Herot ghaze, Iesus ti Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim
\r (Mak 6:14-29 ko Luk 3:19-20 ko 9:7-9)
\p 
\v 1-2 Dughiar kam…®n Galilin Distrigh…®n Atrivim Herot, a Iesus amizir araziba baregha, kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam ti, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim Jon, an aremegha ua d…®kafi. Bizir kam bagha a mirakelbar amuamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù\f + \ft (14:1) Herot…®n kam…®n ziar mam Antipas. A Galilin Distrigh…®n gari. An afeziam atrivim…®n itima, Maria Iesus bate. N…® Matyu 2…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 3-4 Herot fo, a faragha uan dozim…®n Filip…®n amuim Herodias inigha an iti. Ez…® Jon bizir kam bagha Herot m…®g…®av…®ra ikia ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® arazir kuram gamua uan dozim…®n amuim inigha an iti.‚Äù Ez…® Herot bizir kam bagha Jon…®n suiragha a ikegha a isava kalabus gat…®.
\v 5 Egha a Jon m…®sueght…® an aremeghasava n…®ghn…®si. Egha a gumazamizibar atiatingi. A fo, me ghaze, Jon God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® aruer mam…®n gumazir maba iza Herot…®n gara, an amebam a batezir dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gha, a koma apa iti. Ez…® Herodias…®n guivim men guam…®n ighiam gami. Ez…® Herot bar an ighiam bagha bar akonge.
\v 7 Egha Herot overiam dafarim an akua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, n…® bizitizim gifonge, k…® a is…®va n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 8 Ez…® Herodias n…®ghn…®ziba uan guivim gan…®ngi, ez…® guivim ghua kamagh…®n Herot m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n dapanim is…®va itaritam dafagh a inigh iz…® na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù\f + \ft (14:8) Herodias uan guivim ko, aning deraghv…®ra foghasa, Jon guizbang…®ra areme, kamagh…®n amiz…® aning ghaze, n…® an dapanim is…®va itarim dat…®gh a inigh iz…® ga dan…®ngigh.\f*
\p 
\v 9 Atrivim akar kam baregha bar oseme. Egha a fo, a uab…® akar gavgavim gumazir a ko itibar damazim…®n a gamigha, bizir kam…®n aghums…®zim inian aghua. Egha a m…®dorozir gumaziba akar gavgavim me gan…®ngiz…®ma me guivim m…®kemezir mogh…®n ami.
\v 10 A gumazir mam amadaz…®ma, a ghua kalabus…®n m…®dorozir gumazibav geima, me Jon…®n f…®rim atu.
\v 11 Egha Jon…®n dapanim itarir mam dafagha, guivim bagha a inigha iza a isava a gan…®ngi. Ez…® an a inigha ghua uan amebam gan…®ngi.
\v 12 Ez…® Jon…®n suren gumaziba iza an namnam inigha ghua anerefa. Me anerefagha egha ghua Iesus m…®keme.
\s1 Iesus dagheba isa 5,000 gumazibagh an…®ngi
\r (Mak 6:31-44 ko Luk 9:10-17 ko Jon 6:1-13)
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus orazi, me Jon…®n f…®rim atuz…®ma an ovenge, ez…®ma a nguibar kam ategha kurim inigha gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganir mam…®n ghu. A uan suren gumaziba ko ghu. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim orazima, a kagh ghu. Ez…® me nguibar ekiam ategha, a buria uan suebar zui.
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus ghua d…®par dadarim…®n otogha garima, av…®rir bar dafam iti. Ez…® a men apangkuva men areir gumazibar ar…®mariaba agefi.
\p 
\v 15 Aruem gevima, Iesus…®n suren gumaziba iza kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim, ez…® am…®nim p…®rasava ami. Kamagh…®n n…® gumazamiziba amadaght…®, me mang…® nguibabar uari bagh daghebagh ivez.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba kamagh me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe tizim bagh mangam? Ia uari daghetaba me dan…®ngigh.‚Äù
\v 17 Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúE dagher av…®riba itir puvat…®. Kar 5 plan bretba ko osirir pumuningra.‚Äù\f + \ft (14:17) Judaba ingarir bretba ekevezir puvat…®. Da en skonbar m…®n gari. Ez…® bret…®n 5 pla, gumazir pumuningra damam.\f*
\v 18 Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bret…®n maba ko osirimning inigh iz…®.‚Äù
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus gumazamizibav geima, me grazim gapia. Ez…® a 5 plan bretba ko osirir pumuning inigha egha kogha overiam…®n gara Afeziam m…®nabi. Egha bretba b…®gha uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® an suren gumaziba da isava gumazamizibagh an…®di.
\v 20 Ez…® gumazamizir kaba bar amegha, naviba bar iz…®fa. Egha dagher naba itima, me da akuvagha 12 plan ak…®rabagh aghui.
\v 21 Gumazir amezibar d…®bobonim 5,000…®n tu. Me amiziba ko boriba d…®ponezir puvat…®.
\s1 Iesus d…®pam gis…®n tugha zui
\r (Mak 6:45-52 ko Jon 6:16-21)
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba amaga me m…®g…®a ghaze, me faragh bot inigh d…®pam…®n vong…®n mang…®. A uab…® ik…® gumazamiziba amadagham.
\v 23 A gumazamiziba amadagha, egha uab…®ra ikia God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabo. Ez…® am…®nim p…®riz…®ma, Iesus uab…®ra iti.
\v 24 Ez…® bot dadarim…®n saghon ghuz…®ma, am…®nim bot…®n guam…®n d…®kavigha me g…®vaima ongarim men bot…®n m…®sosi.
\v 25 Ez…® am…®nim tiasasava amima, Iesus d…®pam gis…®n tugha uan suren gumaziba bagha zui.
\v 26 Me garima, Iesus d…®pam gis…®n izima, me bar puv atiatiava agoi. Egha me ghaze, kar aser mam. Egha atiatiava arai.
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus zuam…®ra me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gavgafigh, kar k…®rara. Ia atiatingan mark…®!‚Äù
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Pita an akam ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, guizbang…®ra n…®rara, n…® na m…®kemeght…®, k…® d…®pam gis…®n n…® bagh mangam.‚Äù
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Pita bot ategha d…®pam gis…®n Iesus bagha zui.
\v 30 A ghua am…®nir gavgavim…®n gari, a bar ekevez…®ma an atiatia d…®pam…®n aven ghuaghiri. Egha dei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® nan akuragh!‚Äù
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Iesus zuam…®ra uan agharim amadagha Pitan suira. Egha kamagh…®n Pitan m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim sufi. N…® tizim bagha okam n…®ghn…®si?‚Äù
\v 32 Egha aning me gat…®n bot…®n ghuavanabo, ez…® am…®nim pura g…®fa.
\v 33 Ez…®ma bot…®n itir gumaziba Iesus…®n ziam fa ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, n…® God…®n Otarim!‚Äù
\s1 Iesus Genesaretian ar…®mariar gumazir av…®ribar ar…®mariaba ag…®fa
\r (Mak 6:53-56)
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko d…®pam…®n vong…®n ghugha, ghua Genesaret…®n nguibam…®n otifi.
\v 35 Ez…® kagh itir darazi Iesus…®n gara a g…®fo. Egha akam amadaz…®, a nguibar rogh…®ra itibar ghuz…®, me ar…®mariaba itir darazi bar me inigha Iesus bagha ize.
\v 36 Egha me a gakaghora ghaze, a men asught…®ma, ar…®mariaba itiba an korotiar av…®zibar suigham. Ez…® gumazamizir an korotiam suiziba, men ar…®mariaba g…®fa.
\c 15
\s1 God…®n araziba Judan ovavibar arazibagh afira
\r (Mak 7:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n Farisin maba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir maba Jerusalem ategha Iesus bagha ize. Egha me kamagh an azai,
\v 2 ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®, n…®n suren gumaziba en ovaviba an…®ngzir arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®? Egha me damasa uan dafariba ruer puvat…®.‚Äù\f + \ft (15:2) Suren gumazibar dafariba bar m…®zezir puvat…®z…® me api. Puvat…®. Judaba God…®n damazim…®n m…®zan atiatingi, egha bizir m…®z…®r…®zitam…®n suighan aghua. Kamagh…®n amigha me ghaze, me faragh uan dafariba ruegh, egh God…®n damazim…®n zuegh, egh daghebar amam.\f*
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikaragha kamagh me m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh amigha ia God…®n arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®, egha uan arazibar g…®n zui?
\v 4 E fo, God ghaze, ‚ÄòIa uan afeziaba ko amebabar akaba baregh men apengan ik…®‚Äô, egha ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazitam akar kuratam uan afeziam ko amebam m…®kemeght…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.‚Äô
\v 5 Ez…® ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazitam uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akurvaghs…® dag…®aba at…®gha, egha ua g…®n aning…®n akuraghan aghuagha, kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guan akuraghasa at…®zir dag…®aba, gua mark…®. K…® da is…® God dan…®ngam.‚Äù ‚Äô A kamagh…®n m…®k…®m…®va, amebam ko afeziam g…®n…®ghn…®gh deragh aning…®n akurvaghan kogham.
\v 6 Ia kamagh…®n amuava, ian arazir kabar, ia God…®n araziba ategha, uan ovavibar araziba faragha dar…®si. Egha God…®n akam gamima, a mati pura bizim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ia uarira uarigh gifarir gumazibara! God…®n akam inigha izezir gumazim Aisaia guizbang…®ra ian arazibar gun kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\v 8 ‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba, me uan akatoribar nan ziam fe, egha men naviba ko n…®ghn…®ziba bar saghon iti.
\v 9 Me gumazibar akabar uari sure gamua uari gifara egha ghaze, kar God…®n akam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me nan ziam guizbang…®ra a fer puvat…®.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir bizibav gei
\r (Mak 7:14-23)
\p 
\v 10 Egha Iesus gumazamizibar diaz…®ma me a bagha izima a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh, egh deragh n…®ghn…®gh!
\v 11 Bizir gumazibar akatoribar ikegha ghuaghiriba, da me gamima, me God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. Bizir navibar ikia akatoribar otiviba, da gumazibagh amima, me God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.‚Äù
\v 12 Ez…® g…®n an suren gumaziba iza kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ti kamagh…®n fos, Farisiba n…® m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha men muriaba bar ikufi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, an azenim iti. Egha bizir a d…®kezir puvat…®ziba, a biba sara da asiam.
\v 14 Ia gumazir kabagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Me damazir okav…®r…®ziba, egha me tuavim isava gumazir igharazim…®n akakasi. Eght…® gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zim tuavim isava gumazir okav…®r…®zir mam…®n akakagh, egh aning v…®rara mang…® mozim…®n mag…®r…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Pita Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúN…® gumazamiziba m…®kemezir akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim e bagh anebight…®, e a g…®fogham?‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh ami, ia ti uaghan gumazir igharazibar m…®rara fozir puvat…®ghav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\v 17 Ia ti kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, bizir akatorim…®n aven zuiba ghua navim…®n zuima, muriam da batozima, ez…® gumazim dagh avi.
\v 18 Ez…® bizir akatoribar otiviba da n…®ghn…®zim…®n ikegha ize. Egha da gumazibagh amima, me God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.
\v 19 K…® gumazibar n…®ghn…®zibar otivir bizir kabanagh m…®gei, n…®ghn…®zir kuraba, ko gumaziba m…®soghar…®zir araziba, ko gumaziba ko amiziba tintinibar uari isava akuir araziba, ko poroghamiba uari bakeir araziba, ko ok…®mak…®ar araziba, ko kotiabar gumazibagh ifarir araziba, ko gumazibar ziabagh as…®ghas…®zir araziba.
\v 20 Arazir kaba gumazibagh amima, me God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. Gumaziba dafariba ruer puvat…®gha api, arazir kam me gamima me God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®.
\s1 Kenanian amizim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n iti
\r (Mak 7:24-30)
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus nguibar kam ategha ghua nguibar ekiamning Taia ko Saidon…®n nguazim…®n ghu.
\v 22 Ez…® Kenanian amizir mam danganir kam…®n ikegha iza kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® Devit…®n Otarim, n…® nan apangkuvigh! Duar kuram nan guivim gapazagha a gas…®ghas…®si.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®atam a ikarvazir puvat…®. Ez…® an suren gumaziba a bagha iza a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAmizir kam d…®aghdiagha en g…®n izi. N…® anemadaght…® a mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me ikara, ‚ÄúGod Israelbar akurvaghasav…®ra na amada. Me sipsipba gumazir dar ganamiba puvat…®z…® mogh…®n iti.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® amizir kam Iesus…®n borogh…®ra iza, tevimning ap…®righa aviragha uan guam nguazim gat…®gha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® nan akuragh.‚Äù
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúKar arazir kuram, gumazim…®n boribar dagheba inigh afiabav k…®nam.‚Äù \f + \ft (15:26) Iesus amizir kam d…®kab…®nasava amir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n ifonge, a faraghav…®ra God…®n akar aghuim is…®va Israel…®n adarazir an…®ngigh, eght…® g…®n igharaziba oragham. Kamagh…®n Iesus akar is…®n zuir kam gamua ghaze, Israelba boribar m…®n itima, igharazir darazi afiabar m…®n iti. Da afiar atiaba puvat…®, en afiar e ko d…®penibar akuiba. Ez…® Iesus amizir kam…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n garava an akura.\f*
\v 27 Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei. Ez…® afiaba uaghan uan ghuavim…®n dakozim…®n apengan itir dagher muzemziariba api.‚Äù
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus akar kam baregha kamagh amizim m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmizim, n…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar ekefe. Bizir n…® bativasa n…® ifongezim, a mar n…® batif.‚Äù Ez…®ma dughiar kamra an guivim ua dera.
\s1 Iesus ar…®mariaba itir gumazir av…®riba, men ar…®mariaba ag…®fa
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus nguibar kam ategha Galilin d…®par dadarim…®n zui. Egha ghua m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n anaboghava apera. Ez…® avirir ekiam a bagha izi.
\v 30 Egha suer kurabar ko, damazir okav…®r…®ziba ko, soroghafarir ik…®z…®r…®ziba ko, m…®geir puvat…®ziba ko, ar…®mariar igharaziba uaghan, me da inigha iza Iesus…®n suemning…®n borogh…®n me ar…®ki. Ez…® a bar men ar…®mariaba batozima, me ua dera.
