\c 16
\s1 Me Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, a mirakel…®n tam damuam
\r (Mak 8:11-13 ko Luk 12:54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Farisiba ko Sadyusiba Iesus basamasa a bagha izi. Me iza ghaze, a mirakel…®n arazitam damight…®, an otoght…® me kamagh…®n fogham, a guizbang…®ra God…®n ingangarim gami.
\v 2 Ez…® a kamagh…®n men m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa guarat…®zibar ghaze, overiam aghevez…®, ez…® gurum…®n dughiam deragham.
\v 3 Egha m…®zarazibar ia ghaze, ghuariam korogha p…®z…®ma, aruem aghevez…®, ez…® ia ghaze, amozim dat…®r…®gh…®n iz…®t…®ma, dughiam deraghan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, ia overiam…®n otivir biziba derav…®ra dagh fo. Egha ia dughiar kam…®n otivir arazibar gara da ab…®zir puvat…®.\f + \ft (16:2-3) Fofozir gumazir av…®riba ghaze, ves 2 ko ves 3…®n itir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, gumazir igharazir mam g…®n da osiri. Egha ghaze, Matyu da osirizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 4 Gumazamizir dughiar kam…®n itiba, me bar gumazamizir kuraba! Egha me guizbang…®ra God baghav…®ra itir puvat…®. Me zurara mirakel…®n tam…®n ganasa. Me tam…®n ganighan kogham. Puvat…®. God mirakel…®n arazir vam…®ra men akagham. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jona batozir mirakel…®n kamra, me an ganam.‚Äù Egha Iesus me ategha ghu.
\s1 Farisiba ko Sadyusibar yis…®n akar is…®n zuim
