\v 8 Ez…® Iesus me m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh fo, egha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir muziariba itiba! Ia tizim bagha uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, e bretba puvat…®?
\v 9 Ia ti fozir puvat…®? Ia ti ok…®n…®ghn…®ki, k…® bret…®n 5 pla inigha gumazir 5,000 pla dagheba me gan…®ngi. Me amez…®, ez…® ia ak…®raba manmagh…®n dagh aghui, ia dagh n…®ghn…®si, o puvat…®?
\v 10 Egha ia ti fo, k…® bret…®n 7 pla inigha gumazir 4,000 pla dagheba me gan…®ngi. Ez…® g…®n men dagher naba itima, ia ak…®raba manmagh…®n dagh aghui?
\v 11 Ia manmagh…®n amigha bizir kam g…®fozir puvat…®, k…® bretbagh n…®ghn…®gha ia m…®geir puvat…®? K…® ghaze, ia Farisiba ko Sadyusibar yis bagh deragh uari bagh gan.‚Äù
\v 12 Ez…® me akar kam baregha fo, Iesus bret bagha amir yis…®n m…®geir puvat…®. Me fo, a Farisiba ko Sadyusiba sure gamir akabagh n…®ghn…®gha, egha ghaze, ia akar kaba bagh derav…®ra uari bagh gan.
