\v 17 Ez…® Iesus a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúSaimon, Jon…®n otarim, nguazim…®n gumazitam m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam n…®n akazir pu. Puvat…®. Nan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itimra, n…®n aka. Kamagh…®n n…® bar akongegh.
\v 18 Ez…® k…® n…® m…®gei, n…® Pita. Egh dag…®ar kam gis…®n k…® uan sios…®n ingaram, eght…® Ovevem…®n Gavgavim an suiragh anep…®righ…®va a gas…®ghasighan kogham.\f + \ft (16:18) Grigh…®n akam…®n aven, ziar kam Pita, an m…®ngarimra kara, Dag…®am.\f*
\v 19 Eght…® k…® God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n kiba is…®va n…®n dafarim dat…®gham. Eght…® bizir manam n…® nguazim…®n a ikeght…®, eght…® God uan Nguibam…®n uaghan a ikegham. Eght…® n…® nguazim…®n bizir manam a f…®right…®, eght…® God uan Nguibam…®n uaghan kamagh…®ra a f…®righam.
\v 20 Egha Iesus pamten uan suren gumaziba anogorogha ghaze, me tong an gun tav m…®k…®m suam, a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim.‚Äù
\ms1 Iesus ovengasa, egha uan suren gumaziba m…®g…®a ghaze, me uaghan an amir araziba, dar amuam
