\v 21 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n ikegha ghua, Iesus uan suren gumaziba bighav…®ra me m…®g…®a ghaze, a Jerusalem…®n mangam, eght…® gumazir aruaba, ko ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, koma Judabar arazibagh fozir gumaziba, a men dafarim…®n bar m…®zazir ekiaba koma os…®mt…®ziba iniam. Eght…® me an aghuagh…®va a m…®sueght…®ma an aremegham. Egh dughiar m…®kezim…®n a ua d…®kavigham.
