\v 25 Gumazir manam uan ik…®r…®m…®rim suiraghs…® n…®ghn…®ght…®, an ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®vagham. Eght…® gumazir manam na bagh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ategh…®va, uan ik…®r…®m…®rim iniam.
