\v 4 Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n gara, egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, bar deragha e kagh iti! N…® ifueght…®ma, k…® averpenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ingaram. N…® bagh tam, Moses bagh tam, egh Elaija bagh tam.‚Äù
