\v 20-21 Ez…® a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar sufi, ez…® ia a batoghan ibura. K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim zuravarim mastet…®n ov…®zitam…®n m…®n ik…®va, ia m…®ghs…®ar kam m…®k…®m suam, n…® s…®vagh munagh mang…®, eght…® a mangam. Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®, ia guizbang…®ra biziba bar dar amuam.‚Äù\f + \ft (17:20-21) Fofozir gumazir maba n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam uaghan vez…®n kam…®n iti. A kamak…®n: ‚ÄúDuar kurar kaba batozir arazir vam…®ra. E dagheba ataghragh egh uaghan God ko m…®k…®mam. Bar tuavir kamra e duar kuraba batogham, ua tuaviba puvat…®.‚Äù\f*
\s1 Iesus ua ghaze, an ovegh d…®kavam
