\v 6 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúTina n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itir borir katam damight…® an arazir kuratam damight…®, a hel…®n mang…®va, a bar ivezir kuram inigham. Kamagh…®n dera, me dag…®ar ekiam an f…®rim dafagh…®va ongarir konim m…®k…®night…® an aremegham.
