\v 7 ‚ÄúK…® ghaze, gumazir nguazim…®n ikiava igharaz darazigh amima me arazir kurabagh amiba, mevzika! Me kuram iniam! Arazir kuraba guizbang…®ra otifi, ez…® arazir kurabagh amima da otivir gumazim, k…® ghaze, Noka! N…® kuram iniam!
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEght…® n…®n dafarim o suem n…® damut…®, n…® arazir kuratam damigh…®va, anetugh a makunigh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…® dafarir vam…®ra ko suer vam…®ra ik…®va zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim…®n aven mangam. N…® dafarir pumuning o suer pumuning ik…®t…® me n…® is…®va avir munger puvat…®zim m…®k…®nigham.
\v 9 Egh n…®n damazim n…® damut…® n…® arazir kuratam damigh…®va, anesigh a makunigh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…® damazir vam…®ra ik…® egh uaghan zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim…®n aven mangam. N…® damazir pumuning ik…®t…®ma me n…® is…®va hel…®n avim m…®k…®nigham.
\p 
\v 10-11 ‚ÄúIa deragh uari bagh gan! Ia borir dozir kabar tong…®n tav g…®nighnigh kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, a pura bizim.\f + \ft (Akar 18:10-11…®n faraghav…®ra itim) Grigh…®n akam ghaze, ‚Äúborir dozir kaba.‚Äù Akar otevir kam uaghan, ves 6 ko ves 14…®n iti. Akar kam Matyu 10:42, uaghan an iti, egha ghaze, ‚Äúsuren gumazir ziaba puvat…®ziba.‚Äù Iesus ti boribara m…®geir puvat…®, a uaghan uan suren gumazir igharazibav gei.\f* Puvat…®. K…® ia m…®gei, men enselba zurara nan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim…®n damazim…®n iti.‚Äù\f + \ft (18:10-11…®n akar abuananam) Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir mam uaghan vez…®n kam…®n iti. Akar kam ghaze, ‚ÄúE fo, Gumazibar Otarim gumazamizir tuavim ataghiziba iniasa ize.‚Äù\f*
\s1 Sipsip…®n ovengezim…®n akar is…®n zuim
\r (Luk 15:3-7)
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si? Gumazitam 100 plan sipsipba ikiam, eght…® vam…®ra oveght…®, a ti manmagh…®n damuam? A ti a burian kogham, o? Puvat…®. A 99 plan sipsipba m…®ghs…®am…®n da ategh egh mang…® ovengezir kam buriam.
\v 13 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, an a batogh egh bar akuegham. Egh an agoroger ekiar kam, an agoroger 99 plan ovengezir puvat…®zir kaba bagha itim, bar a gafiragham.
\v 14 Kamagh…®ra ian Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim, borir katam ovengan an aghua.‚Äù
\s1 Aveghbuar arazir kuram n…® gamizim
\p 
\v 15 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®n aveghbuam arazir kuram n…® damight…®ma, n…® an bighan mang…® egh gua uaningra ik…®va n…® a ko gua bizir kam anek…®righ. A n…® baragham, eght…® n…® ua uan aveghbuam inigham.\f + \ft (18:15) Vez…®n kam…®n itir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevim, ‚Äún…® damight…®ma,‚Äù fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir ti igharazim an osiri. Matyu uab…® puvat…®.\f*
\v 16 Eght…® a n…® baraghan aghuagham, n…® mang…® gumazir igharazir mam, o gumazir igharazir pumuning, uam me inigh. Eght…® me n…®n g…®n mang…®. E fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® gumazitam…®n arazir kuram an gun a m…®k…®masa, gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezim gavgavim n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar an…®ngam.‚Äô
\v 17 Egh gumazir n…® m…®geir kam uaghan men akam baraghan aghuaght…®ma, n…® an arazibar gun Sios…®n adarazi m…®k…®mam. Eght…® a uaghan me baraghan aghuaght…®ma, n…® God g…®fozir puvat…®zir gumazim o dag…®aba isir gumazim…®n m…®n a damu.
\p 
\v 18 ‚ÄúKi guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, bizir manam ia nguazim…®n a ikeght…®, eght…® God uan Nguibam…®n uaghan a ikegham. Eght…® ia nguazim…®n bizir manam a f…®right…®, eght…® God uan Nguibam…®n uaghan kamagh…®ra a f…®righam.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúEgha k…® ua ia m…®gei, gua taning kagh nguazim…®n bizitam bagh n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ikia a iniasa a bagha God ko m…®gei, nan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim a is…®va gua dan…®ngam.
\v 20 Egh gumazir pumuning, o pumuning ko m…®kezim nan ziam uari akuvagh ik…®t…®, k…® uab…® men tong…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus igharaz darazir arazir kuraba da g…®n amangasa akar is…®n zuim akuri.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Pita iza kamagh Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® manmagh…®n dughiabar arazir kurabar na gamizir gumazim…®n araziba g…®n amangam. Ti 7 plan dughiaba?‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® 7 plan dughiabar an arazir kuraba g…®n amanagasa n…® m…®geir puvat…®. N…® zurazurara an arazir kuraba g…®n amang.
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄúIa oragh. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, atrivir mam ko an ingangarir gumazibar eghaghanim. Atrivim uan dag…®aba isa uan ingangarir gumazibar dafarim gat…®gha ghaze, me g…®n ua da ikarvagham. Dughiar mam atrivim me a ikarvaghamin bizim ak…®rasa.
\v 24 An adar k…®rir dughiam, me gumazir atrivim da 10 milien Kina inizim…®n akua izi.
\v 25 Ez…® a dag…®ar inizir kabar ikarvaghan ibura. Kamagh…®n atrivim me m…®g…®a ghaze, me gumazir kam inigh an amuiroghboriba sara dag…®aba bagh me amadagh, egh men ivezim inigh. Egh me ateght…® me gumazir igharazim…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ik…®. Egh an biziba bar da amadagh, dag…®aba inigh egh a na da inizir biziba ikaragham.
\v 26 Ez…® ingangarir gumazir kam kamagh…®n oragha atrivim…®n guam…®n ir…®gha kamagh m…®g…®a a gakaghori, ‚ÄòN…® nan apangkuvigh, egh na m…®zuam. Eght…® k…® n…® da inizir biziba bar da ikarvagham.‚Äô
\v 27 Ez…® atrivim an apangkuvigha, a inizir biziba uaghan da g…®n amada.
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúEz…® ingangarir gumazir kam atrivim…®n d…®penim ategha ghua a ko ingaritav bato. A ko ingarir gumazir kam, faragha a da 10 Kina inigha a ikarazir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazir atrivim ko ikegha izir kam, magh…®rama an f…®rm…®n suigha anegoava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® na da inizir dag…®aba bar da ikaragh.‚Äô
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir kam an guam…®n ir…®gha a gakaghora ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® nan apangkufigh, egh na m…®zuam. Eght…® k…® n…® da inizir biziba ua da ikarvagham.‚Äô
\v 30 Ez…® gumazir kam a baraghan aghua, egha a inigha ghua kalabus gat…®, eght…® a ik…® mang…® dag…®ar kaba ikaragham.
\p 
\v 31 ‚ÄúEz…® aning ko ingarir marazi, arazir kam…®n ganigha men naviba bar men ikufi. Egha me ghua atrivim batogha gumazir kam, a ko ingarir gumazim gamizir arazibar gun a m…®keme.
\v 32 Ez…® atrivim gumazir kam…®n diaz…®ma, a uam a bagha ghu. Ez…® a kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® bar ingangarir gumazir kuram! N…® faragha na gamuava araima, k…® dag…®ar n…® iniziba bar da g…®n amada.
\v 33 K…® n…®n apangkufi, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, n…® tizim bagha n…® ko ingarir tav…®n apangkuvan aghua?‚Äô
\v 34 Egha atrivim atarava gumazir kam isava, m…®zaziba agasamin gumazibar dafarim gat…®. Eght…® a kagh…®ra ik…® mang…®, a biziba bar da ikarvaghamin dughiam…®n tugham.
\p 
\v 35 ‚ÄúEght…® ia uan aveghbuabar arazir kurar me ia gamiba, ia guizbang…®ra uan navir averiabar aven, da g…®n amangan koght…®ma, nan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim uaghan kamagh…®ra ia damuam.‚Äù
\c 19
\s1 Iesus poroghamiba uari ataghrazir arazibav gei
\r (Mak 10:1-12 ko Luk 16:18)
\p 
\v 1 Iesus m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba a g…®vagha, egha Galilin Distrigh ataki, egha Judian Distrigh…®n ghua Jordan d…®pam…®n vong…®n ghu.
\v 2 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim an g…®n zui, ez…® a danganir kam…®n men ar…®mariaba ag…®fa.
\v 3 Ez…® Farisiba Iesus basamasa iza kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si? Gumazim uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua uan amuim puram anetaghragh…®s…® damut…®, Judan Araziba ti an amamangat…®gham, o ti puvat…®gham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúIa ti God…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba itir Ak…®nafarim…®n ganizir puvat…®? Akar kam ghaze, ‚ÄòGod faraghav…®ra bizibar ingara, gumazamizibar ingari egha me gamiz…®, me gumazim ko amizim…®n oto.‚Äô
\v 5 Ez…® God ghaze, ‚ÄòKamagh…®n amiz…®ma, gumazim uan afeziam ko amebam ategh…®va a uan amuim ko aning uaning…®n porogham. Egh aning nivaf…®zir vam…®ram otogham.‚Äô
\v 6 God kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®ma, aning ua gumazir pumuning puvat…®. Aning nivaf…®zir vam…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, God bizir pumuning isafuraght…®ma, gumazitam aning abighan kogham.‚Äù
\v 7 Ez…® Farisiba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®ma, Moses osira ghaze, gumazim amuim ataghraghs…®va, a bagh ak…®nafarim osirigh a dan…®ngigh, egh amuim batueght…®ma a mang…®?‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazir akaba barazir puvat…®ziba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Moses ian amamangat…®z…®ma, ia uan amuiba ataghrasi. Faraghav…®ra arazir kam puvat…®.
\v 9 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, gumazitam…®n amuim, a gumazir igharaziba tintinibar me isava akuir arazitam damighan koght…®ma, eght…® an a batuegh egh amizir igharazitam inigh an ikiam, gumazir kam poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba akar kam baregha egha kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúArazir kabanagh poroghamibar tong…®n ik…®t…®ma, gumaziba amibar ikian markiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumaziba ko amiziba bar akar kam inian kogham. Puvat…®, God gavgavir kam isava gumazir vabaram an…®ngi. Kamagh…®n me amuibar ikian kogham.
\v 12 Guizbang…®ra, marazi amebaba me batima, men nivaf…®ziba ikufi. Marazi, me me aghori, eght…® me boriba inian kogham. Marazi God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gha amuiba ko pabar ikian aghua. Tina akar kam inis…®va a mar a ini.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, Ia boriba ateght…®, me na bagh iz…®
\r (Mak 10:13-16 ko Luk 18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba boriba inigha Iesus bagha zui. Me ghaze, a dafarim me dar…®gh egh me bagh God ko m…®k…®mam. Ez…® an suren gumaziba, gumazamizir boriba isa izibar atari.
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tina God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ik…®s…®, borir dozir kabar m…®n ik…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma borir doziba ateght…®ma, me na bagh iz…®, egh men anogoroghan mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Egha Iesus dafarimning boribagh is…®n arigha, egha danganir kam ategha ghu.
\s1 Gumazir igiar bizir av…®riba itim iza Iesus ko m…®gei
\r (Mak 10:17-31 ko Luk 18:18-30)
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® gumazir mam iza kamagh Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® manmagh…®n damigh zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha arazir aghuiba bagha nan azai? Gumazir vam…®ra, a dera. Egh n…® zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim inis…®va, God…®n akabar g…®n mang…®‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® gumazir kam kamagh…®n Iesus…®n aza ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n akar gavgavir manabav gei?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazitam m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®, ia poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuan mark…®, ia ok…®man mark…®, egh ia pura gumazibagh ifar…®va, me is…® kotiam dar…®ghan mark…®,
\v 19 egh ia uan amebaba ko afeziabar apengan ik…® egh me baragh, egh ia uari g…®fongez…® mogh…®n gumazir igharazibagh ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir igiar kam kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúAkar kabanagh, k…® bar dar g…®n zui. K…® ua tizim damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® bar deragh otivan ifuegh…®va, egh mang…® uan biziba bar da amadagh. Egh dar dag…®aba inigh egh da is…®va gumaziba ko amizir biziba puvat…®zibar an…®ngigh. N…® kamagh…®n damigh, bizir bar aghuiba n…® bagh God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiam. Egh n…® nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Gumazir igiar kam, a bizir bar av…®riba ikia, kamagh…®n oregha navim bar an osemez…®, a ghu.
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra k…® ia m…®gei, gumazir dag…®ar av…®riba itiba, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mangan iburagham.
\v 24 Egha k…® ua ia m…®gei, kamel…®n tam iniba isair d…®konir torim…®n aven mang…®s…® ingangarir dafam damigh aven mangam. Eght…® gumazir biziba av…®rasemeziba, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n mang…®s…® guizbang…®ra bar iburagham!‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® an suren gumaziba akar kam baregha d…®gavir kuram gamigha ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n damight…®ma, tinara zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuir kam iniam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus damazim meraram asaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir kaba gumazim…®n bar osemegham. Bizir kaba God…®n osemezir puvat…®. A biziba bar dagh ami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 A kamagh m…®kemez…®, Pita an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ge, e uan biziba bar da ategha, n…®n g…®n ize. E tizitam iniam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, God nguazim ko overiar igiam ak…®ramin dughiam…®n Gumazibar Otarim ziar bar ekiam iniam, egh atrivir dabirabim daperagham. Eght…® ia nan g…®n aruizir darazi, ia uaghan 12 plan atrivir dabirabibar dapiagh Israelian anabar 12 plan ganam.
\v 29 Eght…® tina nan ziam bagh n…®ghn…®gh, uan d…®peniba ko aveghbuaba ko amiziba ko afeziam ko amebam ko boriba ko nguazim, da ateght…®, God gumazir kam ivezir bar aghuim a dan…®ngam. Ivezir kam, a nguazir kam…®n itir bizir kaba bar dagh afiragham. Eght…® a uaghan zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim…®n aven ikiam.
\v 30 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n faragha itir darazi, me g…®n ik…®t…®ma, eght…® g…®n itir darazi me faragh ikiam.‚Äù
\c 20
\s1 Wain…®n azenim…®n ingarir gumazibar akar is…®n zuim
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® gumaziba faragh faragh ikiasa m…®geir n…®ghn…®zim k…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®masa. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, gumazir mam wain…®n azenir ekiam iti. Egha a m…®zarazimra ghua wain…®n azenim…®n ingarasa ingangarir gumazir maba ini.
\v 2 Ez…® gumazir kaba a ko akam ak…®ri, egha wan kina wan kina aruer vam…®ra iniasa ifonge, ez…® gumazir ekiam me amadaz…® me an wain…®n azenim…®n ingarasa ghue.
\v 3 Ez…® gumazir ekiar kam 9 klok kamagh…®n ghua biziba amadir danganim…®n gumazir mabar gari, me iti.
\v 4 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa uaghan mang…® nan wain…®n azenim…®n ingar, eght…® k…® ian ingangarim…®n m…®rara ia g…®vezam.‚Äô
\v 5 Ez…® me ingarasa ghue. Ez…® gumazir ekiar kam 12 klok ko 3 klogh…®n ghua arazir kamram amua ua gumazir maba ini.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEgha 5 klok ko kamagh…®n ghua ua gumazir mabar gari, me pura tuivighav iti. Ez…® a kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄòIa manmagh…®n amigha aruer kam…®n pura iti.‚Äô Ez…® me a m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 7 ‚ÄòTav ingangaritam e gan…®ngizir puvat…®.‚Äô Ez…® gumazir ekiam me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa uaghan mang…® nan wain…®n azenim…®n ingar.‚Äô
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEz…® aruem g…®vaz…®ma gumazir ekiam uan ingangarir gumazibar garir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazibar diagh men ivezim me dan…®ng. Egh n…® gumazir bar g…®n izezibar ikegh ivezim me dan…®ng, mang…® faragha izezibar g…®fagh.‚Äô
\v 9 Ez…® gumazir 5 klogh…®n izeziba iza wan kina, wan kina isi.
\v 10 Ez…® g…®n gumazir faraghav…®ra ingariba iza n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, me ti dag…®ar ekiatam iniam. Puvat…®, me uaghan wan kina wan kina ini.
\v 11 Egha me dag…®ar me inizibar gara wain…®n azenim…®n ghuavim…®n atara kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 12 ‚ÄòGumazir kaba bar g…®n izegha auan vam…®ran ingari, ez…® e m…®zaraghara izegha ingangarir ekiam gamima, aruem e gaponge. Ez…® n…® ivezir vam…®ra bar e gan…®ngi.‚Äô
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúEz…® azenim…®n ghuavim akar kam baregha kamagh…®n men mav m…®gei, ‚ÄòNamakam, k…® arazir kuratam ia gamizir puvat…®. Ia ti faragha, ia wan kina iniasa akam ak…®ri?
\v 14 N…® uan ivezim inigh mang…®. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, k…® dag…®aba gumazir g…®n izezim g…®vezir mogh…®ra n…® g…®vesi.
\v 15 Kar nan bizimra. K…® ti uan dag…®aba uan ifongiam…®n dar an…®ngan kogham? Egha k…® arazir bar aghuim gumazir kabagh amiz…®ma n…® tizim bagha navir averiam…®n na baseme?‚Äô‚Äù
\v 16 Egha Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra gumazir g…®n izeziba faragh ikiam, eght…® faragha itiba me g…®n mangam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus uan ovever dughiam, dughiar m…®kezim…®n uam a m…®gei
\r (Mak 10:32-34 ko Luk 18:31-33)
\p 
\v 17 Egha Iesus uan suren gumazir 12 pla ko Jerusalem…®n zui. Egha me ghua a me inigha danganir m…®riar mam…®n ghua me uarira ikiava, egha kamagh…®n a me m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 18 ‚ÄúIa oragh, E nguibar ekiam Jerusalem…®n ghuavanadi. Eght…® gumazitam Gumazibar Otarim is…®va, Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba koma ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar an…®ngam. Eght…® me a is…® kotiam dat…®gh…®va, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremeghs…®va me akabar k…®ram, egh me kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, N…® aremegham.
\v 19 Egh me a inigh Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazibar dafaribar an…®ngt…®, eght…® gumazir kaba a d…®povam, egh a ifozorogh…®va egh a is…®va temer ighuvim gafught…® an aremegham. Eght…® aruer m…®kezim g…®vaght…®ma, a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù
\s1 Jems ko Jon ekiamning…®n otivasa
\r (Mak 10:35-45)
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Sebedin amuim uan otarimning ko Iesus bagha izi. Me izava aning…®n amebam itevimning ap…®righa, egha ua bagha bizitam damuasa an azai.
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus an azara, ‚ÄúN…® tizim baka?‚Äù Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n na bagh damu, n…® Atrivir Ekiam…®n otogh, egh nan otarimning ateght…®, tav n…®n agharir guvim dapit…®ma, tav n…®n agharir ik…®riam daperagh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus akam baregha egha kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúIa azangs…®zir bizir kam, ia an m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®, egha ia a bagha nan azai. Gua ti k…® ateramin os…®mt…®zim, uaghan an ateramin gavgavim iti?‚Äù Ez…® aning ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, ga gavgavim iti.‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, gua k…® ateramin os…®mt…®zim, gua a iniam. Egha k…® tav am…®seveght…® a nan ik…®riam ko guvim…®n dapiamin bizim, a nan bizim puvat…®. Ez…® danganir kabanang, nan Afeziam dar apiasa gumazir maba am…®sevegha, egha me bagha dar k…®righa g…®fa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® suren gumazir 10 pla akar kam baregha aning…®n atari.
\v 25 Ez…®ma Iesus men diaz…®, me izima a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa fo, Kantrin Igharazibar atriviba pamten me gamima, me bar men apengan iti. Ez…® men gumazir dapaniba uan akaba baraghasa puv…®ra me ab…®raghb…®rasi.
\v 26 Eght…® arazir kaba ian tong…®n ikian kogham. Gumazir manam ian tong…®n ekiam…®n ik…®s…®, a ingangarir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®.
\v 27 Eght…® gumazir manam ian faragh mang…®s…®, a bar ian ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ik…®.
\v 28 Ez…® kamagh…®ra Gumazibar Otarim iza, gumazamizibar amut…® me a bagh ingarasa, a izezir pu. Puvat…®, a me bagh ingarasa ize. Egha a gumazamizir av…®riba bagh aremegh ua me givezegh me iniasa ize.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus gumazir damazir kurar pumuning gamiz…®, aning gari
\r (Mak 10:46-52 ko Luk 18:35-43)
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko Jerikon nguibar ekiam ategha zui. Ez…® av…®rir ekiam an g…®n zui.
\v 30 Ez…® gumazir damazir kurar pumuning tuavir ap…®nim…®n aperaghav iti. Egha aning orazima Iesus tuavir kam…®n izima, aning pamten kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúN…® Devit…®n Otarim, n…® gan apangkufigh.‚Äù
\v 31 Ez…® gumazamiziba aning barazi, aning deima, me pamten aning…®n anogorogha ghaze, gua uan akamning dukuagh. Me kamagh…®n aning…®n m…®geima, aning tiarim akarava dia ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® Devit…®n Otarim, n…® gan apangkufigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Iesus tugha aning…®n dia ghaze, ‚ÄúGua tizim gifonge, eght…® k…® gua bagh a damuam?‚Äù
\v 33 Ez…® aning a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® gan damaziba kuight…®, ga ua ganasa.‚Äù
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus aning…®n apangkuvigha egha dafarim aning…®n damazibagh at…®z…®, aning…®n damaziba magh…®ra ua deraz…®, aning ua gari. Egha magh…®ra Iesus…®n g…®n zui.
\c 21
\ms1 Iesus Jerusalem…®n otogha gumazamizibar sure gami
\mr (Sapta 21-25)
\s1 Iesus atrivim…®n m…®n Jerusalem…®n aven zui
\r (Mak 11:1-11 ko Luk 19:28-40 ko Jon 12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko me Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n izava Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n iza Betfagen nguibam…®n oto. Egha Iesus uan suren gumazir pumuning amaga,
\v 2 kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nguibar munagh itim…®n mang…®, egh gua gant…®ma, donkin mam me a ikez…®ma a uan nguzir asem ko iti. Aning…®n benim f…®righ na bagh aning inigh kagh iz…®.
\v 3 Eght…® gumazitam guan azangt…®ma, gua a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòEkiam ingangarim aning…®n iti.‚Äô Eght…® gumazir kam zuam…®ra puram aning ateght…®, aning izam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia faragha m…®kemezir akaba otivasa, bizir kaba otifi. Akar kam kamak…®n,
\v 5 ‚ÄúN…® akar kam is…®va Saion…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamizibav keme. Ia gan, ian atrivimra mara, ia bagha izi! A gumazir k…®nir ziaba puvat…®zir mam…®n m…®n donkin mam gaperagha izi, kar donkin amebam…®n nguzir asem.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumazimning ghua a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\v 7 Egha aning donkin amebam nguzir asem sara aning inigha iza, egha uan korotiar azenan azuiba suegha donkining…®n ak…®rimning gis…®n at…®z…®, Iesus korotiar kabagh is…®n apera.
\v 8 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba uan korotiar azenim…®n azuiba suegha tuavim mughara zui. Ez…® marazi temer aguaba oka da isa tuavir torim gar…®si.
\v 9 Ez…® gumazamizir faragha zuiba ko Iesus…®n g…®n iziba, uan tiariba akara ghaze, ‚ÄúHosana! Ia Devit…®n Otarim…®n ziam f…®. An Ekiam…®n ziam…®n izir gumazim, eght…® God derav…®ra a damu. Hosana! Ia God…®n bar p…®n itim…®n ziam f…®!‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus Jerusalem…®n aven ghuz…®, an itir gumazamiziba d…®gavir kuram gamigha tintinibar uarir azai,
\v 11 ‚ÄúKar gumazir manam?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus…®n g…®n izezir darazi ghaze, ‚ÄúKar Iesus, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim. A Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam Nasaretian gumazim.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven biziba amadir gumaziba, me batosi
\r (Mak 11:15-19 ko Luk 19:45-48 ko Jon 2:13-22)
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus ghua God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n gumazibar garima, me biziba amadi, ez…® a me batosi. Egha gumazir dag…®aba uarir ikarvazibar dakoziba, ko kuarazir bunbaba amadir gumazibar dabirabiba, da fava egha da ighavk…®ri.\f + \ft (21:12) Gumaziba God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n ik…® bizibagh ivez…®s…®, ofa gamir dag…®abar dagh ivezam. Me Rom ko Grigh…®n dag…®abar ivezan kogham. Kuaraziba ko bizir me kagh iveziba, da God…®n ofa gamir biziba.\f*
\v 13 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim akar kam iti. ‚ÄòNan d…®penim, me ziar kam a dar…®gham, Gumazamiziba God ko M…®geir D…®penim. Ez…® ia a gamima, an ok…®mak…®ar gumazibar mogomer danganim…®n oto!‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Egha a God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itima, damazir okav…®r…®ziba ko suer am…®r…®ziba a bagha izima, a men ar…®mariaba gefi.
\v 15 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba koma Judabar arazibagh fozir gumaziba izava an amir arazir iv…®nbabar gari. Egha me orasi, boriba God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n ikia dia ghaze, ‚ÄúHosana! Devit…®n Otarim…®n ziam f…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bizir kaba bagha atari.
\v 16 Egha kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúN…® boriba m…®geir akaba barasi, o?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, ia ti God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n ganizir puvat…®? A ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® borir iririviba ko otem apav…®ra itibagh amima, me derav…®ra n…®n ziam fe.‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Egha me ategha ghua Jerusalem…®n nguibam ategha Betanin nguibam…®n ghu, egha kagh akui.
\s1 Iesus temer figh m…®kemez…®, a m…®s…®ngi
\r (Mak 11:12-14 ko 11:20-24)
\p 
\v 18 Egha m…®zaraghara Iesus d…®kavigha ua Jerusalem…®n zui. A zuima, m…®tiriam an azi,
\v 19 ez…® a tuavir ap…®nim…®n temer figh…®n mam…®n garima, a iti. Ez…® a rogh…®ra ghua garima, figh…®n ov…®ziba puvat…®. A pura dafarir k…®niba iti. Ez…® Iesus temer kam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ua ban kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù Ez…® temem magh…®ra m…®s…®ngi.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® an suren gumaziba bizir kam…®n ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha, egha ghaze, ‚ÄúTemem manmagh…®n amigha zuam…®ra m…®s…®ngi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®va, egh okam n…®ghn…®ghan kogh, egh ia, k…® figh…®n temem gamizir arazim, ia uaghan a damuamin gavgavim ikiam. Egha anar…®ra puvat…®, ia uaghan m…®ghs…®ar kam m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® d…®kavigh mang…®, uab…® is…® ongarim m…®k…®nigh.‚Äô Eght…® a ia m…®kemezir mogh…®n otivam.
\v 22 Egh ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®va God ko m…®k…®m…®va, ia bizir manaba bagh God…®n azangs…®gh, egh ia da iniam.‚Äù
\s1 Judan gumazir dapaniba Iesus…®n gavgavim bagha an azai
\r (Mak 11:27-33 ko Luk 20:1-8)
\p 
\v 23 Egha Iesus ghua Jerusalem…®n otogha God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven gumazamiziba God…®n akam men sure gami. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar arazibagh fozir gumaziba iza kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® gavgavir manam…®n amodogh…®n bizir kabagh ami? Ez…® tina gavgavir kam n…® gan…®ngi?‚Äù
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® azangs…®zir mam ia damuasa. Ia derav…®ra a ikaraght…®ma, k…® ia m…®k…®mam, k…® gavgavir manam…®n amodogh…®n bizir kabagh ami.
\v 25 K…® Jon bagha ian azai, tina gavgavim Jon gan…®ngiz…® a gumaziba rue? A ti God…®n Nguibam…®n gavgavir kam ini, o a ti gumaziba dama a ini?‚Äù
\p Ez…® me uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE suam, ‚ÄòAn rurim God…®n ize,‚Äô eght…® a ua kamagh…®n en azaragham, ‚ÄòIa manmagh…®n amigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Jon damuan aghua?‚Äô
\v 26 Eght…® e suam, ‚ÄòJon…®n rurim gumazibar ize,‚Äô e kamagh…®n gumazamizibar atiatingi. E fo, me bar Jon m…®g…®a ghaze, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam.‚Äù
\v 27 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE fozir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, k…® uan gavgavim inizir tuavim…®n, gun ia m…®kemeghan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus gumazir mam…®n otarimning akar is…®n zuim m…®gei
\p 
\v 28 Egha Iesus uam ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si? Gumazir mam otarir pumuning iti. Egha ghua kamagh otarir avebam m…®gei, ‚ÄòOtarim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…®, wain…®n azenim…®n aven ingar.‚Äô
\v 29 Ez…® otarim ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® aghua.‚Äô Egha ua g…®n, n…®ghn…®zim g…®ragha ghua ingari.
\v 30 Ez…® afeziam ghua otarir dozim kamagh…®ra an azara. Ez…® otarim ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® mang…®, ingaram.‚Äô Egha g…®n ghuzir puvat…®.
\v 31 Ez…® ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, otarir kamning…®n manamra afeziam…®n akam baragha an g…®n zui?‚Äù Ez…® me Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúOtarir avebam.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazir dag…®aba isiba ko amizir arazir kurabagh amiba, me ia gafiragha faragha God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven zui.
\v 32 Guizbang…®ra, Jon otogha arazir aghuim…®n tuavim ian aka, ez…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an akam…®n ikian aghua. Ez…® dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko amizir arazir kurabagh amiba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba an iti. Ia bizir kam…®n ganigha uan n…®ghn…®zibagh irazir puvat…®, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Jon…®n akam…®n itir puvat…®.‚Äù
\s1 Wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumazir kurabar akar is…®n zuim
\r (Mak 12:1-12 ko Luk 20:9-19)
\p 
\v 33 Egha Iesus gumazir dapaniba ua kamagh me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa akar is…®n zuir kam baragh. Gumazir mam wain…®n azenim…®n ingarigha, egha an d…®vazim aghui. Egha wain…®n ov…®ziba m…®rm…®ramin itarim gukuigha azenir d…®penim…®n ingari, eght…® ingangarir gumaziba an ik…® azenim…®n ganam. Egha azenir kam isa gumazir mabar agharim gat…®gha ghaze, me g…®n wain…®n d…®pataba uam a ikaragham. Egha d…®kavigha nguibar saghon itim…®n ghu.\f + \ft (21:33) Wain…®n azenim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, Iesus Aisaia 5:1-2…®n da ini, egha God Israelba damuamin akar is…®n zuim m…®keme. Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, God uab…®, gumazir azenim…®n ingarizim. Ez…® Israelba wain…®n azenim…®n m…®n iti.\f*
\v 34 Ez…® wain…®n temeba ber dughiam rogh…®ra izez…®ma, gumazir kam uan ingangarir gumazir maba amadaz…®ma, me wain…®n ov…®zi taba iniasa ghue.
\v 35 Ez…® azenim…®n garir gumaziba ingangarir gumazir kaba inigha, mam m…®suegha, egha mam me a m…®soghez…®ma an areme, egha dag…®aba mam ginifi.
\v 36 Ez…® azenim…®n ghuavim g…®n ua ingangarir gumazir igharaziba amangi. Me av…®raseme, egha men d…®bobonim faragha izezibagh afira. Ez…® wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumazir kaba kamagh…®ra uam azenim…®n ghuavim…®n ingangarir gumazibagh ami.
\p 
\v 37 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®ma, azenim…®n ghuavim abuan uan otarim amada. Afeziam ghaze, ‚ÄòMe nan otarim…®n akam baragh deragh a damuam.‚Äô
\v 38 Puvat…®, gumazir kaba otarim…®n gari, a izima, me uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄòGumazir kam iz…®va uan afeziam…®n biziba bar da inigham. Aria. E a m…®sueght…®, an aremegham. Eght…® e uari bagh wain…®n azenim iniam.‚Äô
\v 39 Kamagh…®n, me magh…®ra an suigha, wain…®n azenim…®n azenan anekunigha, otarim m…®soghez…® an areme.
\p 
\v 40 ‚ÄúEght…® wain…®n azenim…®n ghuavim iz…® manmagh…®n gumazir kabar amuam? Ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si?‚Äù
\p 
\v 41 Ez…® me a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA gumazir kurar kaba puv me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghregham. Eght…® an azenim is…®va gumazir igharazibar anigam, eght…® wain…®n ov…®ziba iniamin dughiam…®n me a bagh pozim daghuigh a dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 42 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúIa God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir osizirir kabar gani, o puvat…®? Osizirir kaba kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄòKar d…®penir ak…®nir ingangarir gumaziba aghuazim,
\q2 a dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®penim aterir guarim gava.
\q1 Ekiam uab…® arazir kam gamiz…®ma an oto.
\q2 Ez…® e an garima, a bar dera.‚Äô
\m 
\v 43 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n, k…® ia m…®gei, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, God ia dama a inigh a is…®va, gumazamizir dughiar kam…®n aven ik…® arazir aghuibar amuamibar an…®ngam.
\v 44 Eght…® gumazir manam dag…®ar kam gis…®n ir…®gh…®va, an aghariba d…®p…®righregham. Eght…® dag…®ar kam gumazitam gis…®n ir…®gh…®va, bar anem…®sarigham.‚Äù\f + \ft (21:44) Baibel…®n fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, akar ves 44…®n aven itiba, Matyu da osirizir puvat…®, ti gumazir igharazim g…®n da osiri. Luk 20:18…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 45 Ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Farisiba akar is…®n zuir kam baregha fo, Iesus akam isa, me gasara.
\v 46 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an suighasava amuava, egha gumazamizir av…®ribar gara atiatingi. Me fo, gumazamiziba Iesus…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam.
\c 22
\s1 Poroghamir isar ekiam…®n akar is…®n zuim
\r (Luk 14:16-24)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus uam akar is…®n zuir mam…®n gumazir dapanibagh amua kamagh…®n me m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, atrivir mam…®n otarim amuim…®n ikiasava amima, an a bagh isar ekiam gami.
\v 3 Isar dughiam t…®ghar otivam, a faraghav…®ra gumazamizir mabav g…®a ghaze, ia iz…®. Dughiam otoz…®ma, a uan ingangarir gumaziba amadi, eght…® me mang…® gighamizir gumazamizibar diaght…®, me izam. Puvat…®, gumazamizir a gighamiziba, me izan aghua.
\v 4 Ez…® a uan ingangarir gumazir maba amaga, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa mang…®, gumazir k…® gighamiziba kamagh me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄúIa oragh. K…® dagheba tuegha g…®fa, nan kaun apuriba k…® dav suegha, egha uaghan uan as…®zir ekiabav soke. Ez…® isam…®n biziba bar g…®fa. Ia poroghamir isar ekiam…®n iz…®.‚Äù ‚Äô
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúEz…® ingangarir gumaziba ghua akar kam…®n gumazibav gei. Ez…® me oraghan aghuagha tintinibar zui. Mav uan azenim…®n zui, mav uan dag…®ar ingangarim bagha zui.
\v 6 Marazi atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazibar suigha, puv me m…®soghez…® me ariagh…®re.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim puv atari, egha kamagh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba amada. Ez…® me ghua an ingangarir gumazibar m…®sogheziba, me m…®sogha bar me ag…®vaghava, men nguibar ekiam gaboroz…® a isi.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEz…® atrivim uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄòPoroghamir isam…®n dagheba isigha g…®fa. Ez…® gumazir k…® gighamiziba, me gumazir kuraba, kamagh…®n me isam…®n ikian kogham.
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia mang…® tuavir akaba bar dar mang…®, egh gumazir manaba ia me bativigh, egh ia men diaght…®, me poroghamir isar kam…®n iz…®.‚Äô
\v 10 A kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®ma, an ingangarir gumaziba tuaviba bar dar ghuava gumazamiziba bar me akufa, gumazir aghuiba ko kuraba sara. Ez…® me iza damasava apiaz…® d…®penim bar iz…®fa.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazamiziba apiaz…®ma, atrivim men ganasa aven zui. Egha a ghua gumazir mam…®n garima, a isam…®n izasa adiariar aghuitam aruzir puvat…®.
\v 12 Ez…®ma atrivim an azai, ‚ÄòNamakam, manmagh…®n amiz…®, n…® adiarir aghuitam aruzir puvat…®gha, puram aven ize?‚Äô Ez…® gumazim m…®k…®man asa.
\v 13 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim ingangarir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa an soroghafariba ikegh, a is…®va azenan m…®tatem…®n anekunigh. Danganir m…®tater kam…®n me puv…®ra tuavara atariba kuskusi.‚Äô
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúIa oragh. God gumazamizir av…®ribar dei, egha vaghvazibara a me am…®sevima, me aven zui.‚Äù
\s1 Gumaziba dag…®aba Atrivim Sisar dan…®ngam, o markiam?
\r (Mak 12:13-17 ko Luk 20:20-26)
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Farisiba ghua akabav suegha Iesus…®n suighasa tuaviba buri. Egha me ghaze, a bizitam a paza m…®kemegham, eght…® me an m…®g…®r…®g…®am baghav…®ra an suigham.
\v 16 Egha me uan suren gumazir maba ko Herot…®n g…®n zuir darazi amada, ez…® me Iesus bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e fo n…® guizbang…®ra bizibav geir gumazim. N…® God…®n Arazibar gumazibar sure gamuava guizbang…®ra me m…®gei. N…® tav…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Akar vam…®ra n…® gumazir ziaba itiba, ko gumazir k…®niba uaghara, me m…®gei.
\v 17 Kamagh…®n, n…® deragh e m…®k…®m. Judan araziba manmagh…®n m…®gei? E dag…®aba is…®va Atrivim Sisar dan…®ngt…®ma, arazir kam God…®n damazim…®n dera, o puvat…®? N…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si?‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Iesus men n…®ghn…®zir kurar kam g…®fo, egha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazir ifavaribagh amiba, ia tizim bagha na gifarasava ami?
\v 19 Ia gavman gan…®dir dag…®atam nan akagh.‚Äù Ez…® me dag…®ar mam inigha iza a gan…®ngi.
\v 20 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúKar tinan nedazim ko tinan ziam?‚Äù
\v 21 Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúMar Sisar…®n nedazim ko an ziam.‚Äù Ez…® a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, ia Sisar…®n biziba Sisar dan…®ng…®va, egh God…®n biziba is…®, God dan…®ng.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha d…®gavir kuram gamigha, egha anetegha ghue.
\s1 Sadyusiba gumazir aremegha ua d…®kavizibar arazim bagha Iesus…®n azai
\r (Mak 12:18-27 ko Luk 20:27-40)
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® aruer kamra, Sadyusiba Iesus bagha ize. Sadyusiba ghaze, gumazir aremeziba ua d…®kavir puvat…®. Egha me kamagh…®n Iesus…®n azai,
\v 24 ‚ÄúTisa, Moses kamagh…®n m…®keme, Gumazir manatam boriba puvat…®gh aremeght…®, an aveghbuatam an amuim inigh an ik…®t…®, amizir kam boriba bat…®, eght…® an aveghbuam…®n ik…®zim kuvaremeghan kogham.
\v 25 Ez…® fom…®ra aveghbuar 7 pla, en tong…®n ike. Men avebam amuim…®n ikiava boritam inizir puvat…®, egha areme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an dozir mam an amuim inigha an iti.
\v 26 Ez…® an dozir kam uaghan boritam inizir puvat…®gha areme. Ez…® aning…®n dozir m…®kezim ko an g…®n iziba kamagh…®ram ami.
\v 27 Egha me bar aremegha g…®fa, ez…® abuan amizir kam uaghan areme.
\v 28 Kamagh…®n n…® e m…®k…®m, gumaziba ua d…®kavamin dughiam…®n, amizir kam tinan amuimra? N…® n…®ghn…®gh, me bar an ike!‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus me ikarvagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir akam g…®fozir puvat…®, egha ia uaghan God…®n gavgavim g…®fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, ia paza m…®gei.
\v 30 Gumazamizir aremeziba ua d…®kavamin dughiam…®n, paba amuibar ikian kogham, uaghan me amuiba is…® pabar ar…®ghan kogham. Me enselbar m…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiam.
\p 
\v 31 ‚ÄúEz…® k…® ua d…®kavamin dughiam bagh ian azangasa. Ia ti God ia m…®kemezir akar kam…®n ganizir puvat…®, o? A ghaze,
\v 32 ‚ÄòK…® Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop…®n God.‚Äô God gumazir nivaf…®zir ariagh…®ribar God puvat…®, a gumazir duar angamra itibar God.‚Äù
\p 
\v 33 Ez…®ma gumazamiziba an akar kam baregha d…®gavir kuram gami.
\s1 God…®n arazir faraghav…®ra itim
\r (Mak 12:28-31 ko Luk 10:25-28)
\p 
\v 34 Farisiba orazima, Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba Sadyusibagh amiz…®ma, me m…®k…®man ibura. Ez…® me uari akuvagha a bagha izi.
\v 35 Me ko izir gumazir mam, a Judabar arazibagh fo. Egha a Iesus basamasa kamagh…®n an azai,
\v 36 ‚ÄúTisa, God…®n arazir manamra maba bar dagh afira egha faraghav…®ra iti?‚Äù
\p 
\v 37 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uan God, n…®n Ekiam, bar a gifongegh, egh n…® uan navir averiam ko uan duam ko uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n, uan God gifongegh.
\v 38 Kar arazir bar ekiam, egha a mabar a faraghav…®ra iti.
\v 39 An g…®rara itim, bar an m…®rara. A kamak…®n: n…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongegh.
\v 40 Moses Osirizir Araziba ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba, da bar arazir kamning gis…®n tu.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim bagha Farisibar azai
\r (Mak 12:35-37 ko Luk 20:41-44)
\p 
\v 41 Farisiba uari akuvagha ikiav itima, Iesus men azai,
\v 42 ‚ÄúIa God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, manmagh…®n a g…®n…®ghn…®si? A tinan otarim?‚Äù Ez…® me an m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA Devit…®n Otarim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 43 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n Duam n…®ghn…®ziba Devit gan…®dima, Devit gumazir kam ‚ÄòEkiam‚Äô a gat…®, egha Devit kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze,
\b
\q1 
\v 44 ‚ÄòEkiam, nan Ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei,
\q2 ‚ÄúN…® nan agharir guvim daperagh, egh na ko atrivim…®n ikiam.
\q1 Egh mang…® dughiar k…® n…®n apaniba,
\q2 me damight…® me n…®n apengan ikiam.‚Äù ‚Äô
\b
\m 
\v 45 Eght…® ia n…®ghn…®gh, Devit uab…® gumazir kam…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, a nan Ekiam. Ez…® manmagh…®n, gumazir kam ua Devit…®n Otarim…®n m…®n iti?‚Äù
\p 
\v 46 Ez…® men tav bar Iesus ikarvaghan buraghburaki. Egha me aruer kam…®n ikegha ghua ua g…®n bizitam bagha an azangan atiati.
\c 23
\s1 Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba arazir kurabagh ami
\r (Mak 12:38-39 ko Luk 11:43 ko 11:46 ko 20:45-46)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus g…®n gumazir av…®riba ko an suren gumazibagh eghari.
\v 2 Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúJudan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, me Moses…®n danganim inigha me Moses Osirizir Araziba ia geghari.
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ia m…®geir akaba, ia da baragh dagh eghari mogh…®n ia damu. Egh me amir araziba ia men g…®n mang…® dar amuan mark…®. Me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar av…®ribagh amua egha uari dar g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 4 Me kamagh…®n amua, mati me bizir bar os…®mt…®ziba isava gumazibagh isaghpuima, ez…® me da ateran buraghburasi. Egha me tong uan dafarpuzitam…®n men akurvaghan n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúArazir me amiba, me uarir ganasa oda dagh ami. Me God…®n Akar maba, uan daveriaba ko guaghaf…®vibar da osirigha, egha dagh amiz…®, da bar ekefe, ez…® me da azui. Egha korotiar ap…®nir sazir bar ruariba, me da azui. Egha ghaze, e arazir kam…®n me uari akakagh suam, e guizbang…®ra God…®n akabar g…®n zui.\f + \ft (23:5) God ko m…®geir daveriaba, kar Judaba ak…®nafarir dozibar God…®n akar maba osiri, egha da isava m…®tarir nguzir mabagh aghui. Egha da isava uan agharir ik…®riabagh aghui, egha maba isava uan guabagh afe. Kisim Bek 13:9 ko 13:16 ko Lo 6:8 ko 11:18, dar gan. Judaba uaghan Ak…®nafarim Namba 15:37-41…®n garava sazir oteviba uan korotiabagh itui. Iesus Judabar arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba m…®g…®a ghaze, me daveriar ekiaba aghuigha, egha sazir ruariba azui, egha uari akakagha ghaze, e guizbang…®ra God…®n akabar g…®n zui. Kar me uarir ganasa odava arazir kabagh ami.\f*
\v 6 Egha isar ekiabar me danganir ziaba itiba isava, God ko m…®geir d…®penibar danganir faragha itibar apiaghiri.
\v 7 Egh me biziba amadir danganibar mang…®t…®, gumazamiziba ‚ÄòTisaba‚Äô me dar…®gh, men ziaba fasa me bar akonge.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúK…® ghaze, gumazitam ia ‚ÄòTisa‚Äô a dar…®ghan mark…®. Bar mark…®. Ian tisan bar vam…®ra, ia bar aveghdiariba.
\v 9 Egh ia nguazim…®n kagh gumazitam ‚ÄòAfeziam‚Äô a dar…®ghan mark…®. Ian Afeziar bar vam…®ra, a uan Nguibam…®n iti.
\v 10 Egh me ‚ÄòGumazir Dapanim‚Äô ian tav dar…®ghan mark…®. Ian Gumazir Dapanir vam…®ra iti, a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim.
\v 11 Ian gumazir ekiaba pura ian ingangarir gumazibar m…®n ik…®.
\v 12 Te uarira uan ziaba fe, God me ab…®raght…®, me apengan ikiam. Eght…® te apengan iti, God me feght…® me ziar ekiaba iniam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba men arazir kurabar gun me m…®gei
\r (Mak 12:40 ko Luk 11:39-52 ko 20:47)
\p 
\v 13-14 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika, ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n tiam asaraz…®, gumazamiziba azenan iti. Egha ia uaghan aven mangan aghua. Ez…® gumazamiziba aven mangasava amima ia men tuaviba ap…®ri.\f + \ft (23:13-14) Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, akar kamnagh uaghan kagh ikiam. A kamak…®n, ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika. Ia gumazir m…®zer pumuning itiba, ia amizir paba ovengezibagh ifarava men d…®penibar ok…®ava, oda m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar ruariba God ko dagh ami. Kotiam…®n Dughiam…®n ia bar ikuvigham.‚Äù N…® Mak 12:40…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 15 ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia ongariba ko nguazir igharaziba bar dar ghua, suren gumazir vam…®ra iniasa ruiagha arui. Eght…® ia gumazitam batogh Judabar arazibar a geghant…®, eght…® a ian n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n mang…®, egh a bar ian m…®rara uaghan hel…®n mangam. Ia a damight…®ma, a bar ia gafiragh arazir kurabar amuam.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúIa damazir okav…®r…®ziba, egha ia gumazir igharaziba tuavim men akakaghasa! Iavzika, ia bar ikuvigham! Ia kamagh…®n gumazibar sure gamua ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazir manam guiz…®n m…®k…®ms…®va, God…®n D…®penim…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an araziba pura bizim. Egh gumazir kam guiz…®n m…®k…®ms…®va, gol…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itibar akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, kar a guizbang…®ra m…®gei, egha a m…®kemezir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®, a damu.‚Äô
\v 17 Ia gumazir onganir damazir okav…®r…®ziba, tizim God…®n damazim…®n ekefe? Ti gol, o ti God…®n D…®penim? Ia fo, gol…®n kam God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti, egha tuavir kam…®n gol…®n kam God…®n bizim…®n oto.
\v 18 Egha ia uaghan kamagh…®n men sure gamua ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazitam uan m…®g…®r…®g…®abar amut…® da guiz…®n otivs…®, altan akakaght…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba pura biziba. Eght…® gumazim altan itir ofabar akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, kar a guizbang…®ra m…®gei, egh a m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®n mang…®.‚Äô
\v 19 Ia damazir okav…®r…®ziba, bizir manam God…®n damazim…®n ekefe, ti altan itir ofaba, o alta uab…®? Ia fo, ofaba altan iti, egha tuavir kam…®n ofan kam God…®n bizim…®n oto.
\v 20 Eght…® kamagh…®n, gumazim guizbang…®ra m…®k…®ms…®va altan akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba alta ko altan ofaba v…®rara aning…®n akakasi.
\v 21 Egh gumazim guizbang…®ra m…®k…®ms…®va God…®n D…®penim…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba God…®n D…®penim, ko God…®n uan D…®penim…®n aven itim, v…®rara aning…®n akakasi.
\v 22 Eght…® gumazitam guizbang…®ra m…®k…®ms…®va God…®n Nguibam…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba God…®n atrivir dabirabim, ko God…®n uan atrivir dabirabim gaperazim, uaghara aning…®n akakasi.
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika, ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia is…®ngt…®zim daghebagh an…®dir zuravarir 10 plan dafaribar aghava, egha dafarir vam…®ra God gan…®di. Egha Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir arazir ekiaba ataghrasi. Ia, gumazamiziba deragha me gamir arazim, ko arazir apangkuvim itiba, ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itir arazim, ia da g…®n amadi. Ia faragh arazir ekiar kabar g…®n mang…® dar amu, egh uaghan arazir dozir ia amiba sara, uaghan dar amu.
\v 24 Ia damazir okav…®r…®ziba, egha gumazir igharaziba tuavim men akakaghasa! Ia mati, gumazim sibaba d…®pars…®zim…®n itima, a bar derav…®ra gara da isa da makuri. Ez…® asizir ekiam kamel, a d…®pars…®zim…®n aven itima, an an garir puvat…®gha, a tui.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia bar deraghav…®ra kapba ko itaribar azeniba rue, ez…® dar aven itir dagher kaba bar iz…®fa. Ia, ok…®mak…®ar araziba ko uarira uarigh n…®ghn…®zir arazibar tuavim…®n, dagher kaba ini.
\v 26 Ia Farisiba, ian damaziba okafi! Ia faraghv…®ra kapbar averiaba ruegh, eght…® dar ot…®gh…®naba uaghan zuegham.
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham. Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia mati, me matmatiam pen…®n ghurghurim a gaghui, ez…® azenan matmatiam…®n ganganim bar dera. Ez…® an aven gumazir kuabar aghariba ko bizir kuriba bar iz…®fa.
\v 28 Ia uaghan kamagh…®n iti. Me azenan ian gara ghaze, ia gumazir aghuiba. Ez…® ifavarir araziba ko arazir bar kuraba, guizbang…®ra ian navir averiabagh iz…®fa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia, fom…®ra itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, men moziba deraghv…®ra dar k…®rm…®gha, egha gumazir arazir aghuibagh amizibar moziba deraghav…®ra dar adiaribagh ami.
\v 30 Egha kamagh uariv gei, ‚ÄòE ti uan inazibar dughiam…®n ikia, egha ti men akuragha God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav soghezir puvat…®ghai.‚Äô
\v 31 kamagh m…®g…®a uari akakagha ghaze, ‚ÄòE God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav soghezir gumazibar boriba!‚Äô
\v 32 Aria, mang…®, ia uan inaziba amuataghizir arazir kuraba, bar da g…®fagh!
\p 
\v 33 ‚ÄúIa kuruziba! Ia dab…®r…®zir anababa! God uan kot…®n aven ian araziba tuis…®gh…®va, ia is…® hel…®n avir ekiam…®n ia amangam! Ia man tuavitam…®n ang…®, hel…®n avim gitagham? Bar puvat…®gham!
\p 
\v 34 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia oragh, k…® ia bagha God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, ko gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, ko gumazir God…®n Ak…®nafarim itir arazibagh foziba, me amangam. Eght…® ia men tarazi m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, egh tarasi is…®va temer ighuvibagh afugham, egh tarazi ian God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven benibar me fozorogham. Egh ia uan nguibar ekiabar me batogh men g…®n t…®ght…®, me ar…® nguibar igharazibar mangam.
\v 35 Eght…®ma arazir aghuibagh amir gumaziba bar, me m…®soghezir gumazibar ivezir kuram, ia a iniam. Gumazir aghuibav sozir arazir kam, gumazir aghuim Abel…®n dughiam…®n ikegha, iza Berekian otarim Sekaraian dughiam…®n tu. Gumazir kam, ia God…®n D…®penim ko ofa gamir danganim t…®zim…®n ia a m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® iarara ivezir kuram uan arazir kuram bagh a iniam.
\v 36 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, arazir kurar kabar ivezir kuram, a dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba me bativam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus Jerusalem…®n apangkufi
\r (Luk 13:34-35 ko 19:41-44)
\p 
\v 37 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúOio, ia Jerusalem…®n adarazi, k…® ian apangkufi! Ia God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav sozi me ariagh…®ri, egha God ia bagha amadir gumaziba, ia dag…®aba isa, me ginivi, me ariagh…®ri. Dughiar av…®ribar k…® ian boriba akuv me mughasa, mati tuarir amebam uan av…®ziming…®n nguziba avaraz…® mogh…®n, k…® ia damuasa. Ez…® ia na bagh izan aghua.
\v 38 Ia oragh! Ian nguibam, God anetaki, ez…® a nguibar soriam gava.
\v 39 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia ua nan ganan kogh, kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar ia suam, ‚ÄòGod uan ziam…®n gumazir kam anemada! God deragh a damu!‚Äô‚Äù
\c 24
\s1 Iesus ghaze, God…®n D…®penim akarighr…®gham
\r (Mak 13:1-2 ko Luk 21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam ategha azenan zuima, an suren gumaziba a bagha izi. Egha me God…®n D…®penim an akakasi.
\v 2 Ez…® an akar kam…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa D…®penim…®n itir bizir aghuir kabar gari? K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, dag…®ar kaba, gumaziba bar da pueght…® da bar mogh…®ra dagh iregham. Eght…® tam tam gis…®n ikeghan kogham.‚Äù\f + \ft (24:2) Kar Matyu osirizir Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ruarir abuananam (4 pla faragha g…®fa). Akar kaba, da 24:2-25:46…®n iti. Da nguazim g…®vamin dughiam…®n arazibar gun m…®gei.\f*
\s1 Iesus ghaze, os…®mt…®zir av…®riba g…®n otivam
\r (Mak 13:3-13 ko Luk 21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Egha Iesus ghua Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n aperaghav itima, an suren gumaziba uarira iza kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®k…®m, bizir kaba dughiar manam…®n otivam? Arazir manamnagh faragh otoght…®, e fogh suam, ‚ÄòN…® ua izam,‚Äô eght…® nguazir kam uaghan g…®vam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan, gumazitam iz…® ia gifaran mark…®.
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir bar av…®riba iz…®, nan ziam is…®va uari gas…® suam, ‚ÄòK…®rara, k…® Gumazir God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezim.‚Äô Egh me gumazamizir av…®ribagh ifaram.
\v 6 Eght…® ia rogh…®ra itir m…®dorozir ekiabar n…®g…®niba baragh, egh saghon itir m…®dorozir ekiabar akaba baragham. Egh ia d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. Arazir kaba otivam, eght…® nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam t…®ghar izam. Eght…® ia rogh…®ra itir m…®dorozir ekiabar n…®g…®niba baragh, egh saghon itir m…®dorozir ekiabar akaba baragham. Egh ia d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. Arazir kaba otivam, eght…® nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam zuam…®ra otoghan kogham.
\v 7 Kantrin mam…®n itir darazi d…®kavigh kantrin igharazim…®n itir darazi ko m…®sogham. Eght…® atrivir mam…®n adarazi d…®kavigh atrivir igharazim…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham. Danganir mabar dagheba bar puvarat…®ght…®ma, gumazamiziba m…®tiriamra ikiam. Eght…®ma m…®k…®mk…®ziba uaghan otivam.
\v 8 Os…®mt…®zir kaba mati, amizim otasa faraghav…®ra m…®zazim barazi mogh…®n.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n me ian suigh…®va os…®mt…®ziba ia dar…®gh…®va ia m…®soght…®, ia ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar nan ziam bang…®n ian aghuagham.
\v 10 Egh dughiar kam…®n gumazamizir av…®riba, me uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir nan itim ategham. Egh paz…® uarira uari damuva, uari is…®va apanibar agharim dar…®gham.
\v 11 Eght…® akar ifavarim akurir gumazir av…®riba otivigh, gumazamizir av…®ribagh ifaram.
\v 12 Eght…® arazir kuraba bar iz…®vaght…®, kamagh…®n gumaziba uarigh ifongezir arazim, g…®vagham.
\v 13 Eght…® tina arazir kabar tong…®n gavgavigh ik…®, mang…® dughiar nguazir kam g…®vaghamim otoght…®, God uam a iniam.
\v 14 Eght…® God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar aghuir kam, me a inigh a is…®va nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®mt…®ma, me a baragham. Eght…®ma g…®n nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam otivam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, bizir bar kuram otogham
\r (Mak 13:14-23 ko Luk 21:20-24)
\p 
\v 15 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gant…®ma, bizir bar kurar God ifongezir puvat…®zim, God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ikiam. Fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Daniel bizir kam…®n gun m…®keme. (Gumazir osizirir kam…®n garim, a deraghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh egh a g…®fogh.)
\v 16 Dughiar kam…®n Judian Distrigh…®n itir gumazamiziba ar…® danganir m…®ghs…®abar mang…®.
\v 17 Egh gumazir manam d…®penim…®n p…®n itir avughsazir danganim…®n ikegh, nguazim…®n mag…®r…®, egh uam aven mang…® uan bizitam inis…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.
\v 18 Egh gumazir manam azenir ekiam…®n ikegh, egh uamategh d…®penim…®n mang…® uan azenan azuir korotiam inian mark…®.
\v 19 Ia naviba adair amiziba ko boriba oteba apir amebaba Iavzika! Dughiar izamin kaba bar ian ikuvigham!
\v 20 Ia amozim…®n dughiam ko Sabat…®n dughiatam…®n aran aghuagh…®va, uari bagh Ekiam ko m…®k…®m.
\v 21 Dughiar kam…®n os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam otivam, nguazim igiamra otozir dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n itir dughiam…®n tu, os…®mt…®zir kamagh…®n ititam fom…®ra otozir puvat…®, egh g…®n tam kamagh…®n uam otivan kogham.
\v 22 Egha God uan gumazamizir m…®sevezibagh n…®ghn…®gha, egha dughiar kurar kam…®n dughiar maba aghorez…®, da mong otefe. A ti dar aghorezir puvat…®z…®, gumazamiziba bar ariaghreghai.
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam dughiar kam…®n kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa gan, God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, a kagh iti,‚Äô o ‚Äòa muna munagh iti,‚Äô ia gumazir kam…®n akam baraghan mark…®.
\v 24 Gumazitaba iz…®va ia gifar suam, ‚ÄòK…®rara, God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim,‚Äô o ‚Äòk…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam,‚Äô egh me mirakel…®n bar ekiaba koma d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibar amut…® da otivam. Me kamagh…®n ifonge, me gumazamiziba bar me gifaraght…®, me onganigham. Egh me gavgavim ik…®, uaghan God ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamiziba, me uaghan me gifarasa. Kamagh…®n me mirakel…®n kabar amuam. Egh dughiataba me me gifars…® damuva avegham.
\v 25 Ia oragh! Bizir k…® faragha ia m…®kemeziba, da otivam.
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, me ia m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa gan. A muna gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti,‚Äô eght…® ia mangan mark…®. Egh me suam, ‚ÄòIa gan. A kara, d…®penir kam…®n aven modoghav iti,‚Äô ia men akam baraghan mark…®.
\v 27 Ia fo, on…®marim taghtagha, an angazangarim aruem anadi nagh…®n ikegha nguazim bar anevaragha ghua aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n tu. Eght…® Gumazibar Otarim ua izamin arazim, uaghan kamagh…®ram otivt…®, nguazim…®n itir darazi bar an ganam.
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúDanganir manam gumazir kuam ir…®ghav iti, a gis…®rara isaba uari akufi, eght…® gumaziba fogham, kuar mam kagh iti. Kamagh…®ra, Gumazibar Otarim iz…®t…®ma, gumaziba bar an ganam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, Gumazibar Otarim g…®n izam
\r (Mak 13:24-27 ko Luk 21:25-28)
\p 
\v 29 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúOs…®mt…®zir ekiar kaba otivigh g…®vaght…®,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄòAruem m…®tategham,
\q2 eght…® iakinim isiraghan kogham,
\q1 eght…® m…®koveziba overiam…®n asigh…®ram,
\q2 overiam…®n itir bizir gavgaviba bar uarira uari s…®vaghs…®vagh,
\q3 uan danganiba ataghragham.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 30 ‚ÄúEght…®, Gumazibar Otarim izamin dughiam, an arazarazim overiam…®n otivt…®ma, nguazim…®n itir nguibaba bar aziam. Dughiar kam…®n gumaziba gant…® Gumazibar Otarim ghuariabagh is…®n ik…®, uan gavgavir ekiam koma angazangarir ekiam sara izam.
\v 31 Eght…® s…®gham bar pamten arangt…®, a uan enselba amadaght…®, me mang…® nguazim ko overiam…®n danganiba bar dar mang…®, a ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamiziba akuvam, egh enselba nguazim…®n oteviba bar, me akuvagh…®va, men aku a bagh izam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, ia temer figh…®n gan fogh
\r (Mak 13:28-31 ko Luk 21:29-33)
\p 
\v 32 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTemer figh…®n aguaba ua d…®z murt…®, ia fogh suam, amozim…®n dughiam rogh…®ra ize. Ia temer figh…®n gan n…®ghn…®zim iniam.
\v 33 Kamagh…®ra ia bizir kabar gant…® da otivt…®, ia fogh suam, Gumazibar Otarim a ua izamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize. A tiar akam…®n tughav iti.
\v 34 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei dughiar kam…®n itir gumazamizir kaba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® bizir kaba bar otivam.
\v 35 Overiam ko nguazim givagham, eght…® nan m…®g…®r…®g…®atam g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ghaze, a ua izamin dughiam, tav a g…®fozir puvat…®
\r (Mak 13:32-37 ko Luk 17:26-30 ko 17:34-36)
\p 
\v 36 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir k…® ia m…®geir kaba otivamin dughiam, tav a g…®fozir puvat…®. Ensel…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n itiba ko God…®n Otarim uaghan fozir puvat…®. Afeziam bar uab…®ra fo.
\v 37 Ez…® bizir Noan dughiam…®n otiviziba, da uaghan Gumazibar Otarim izamin dughiam…®n otivam.
\v 38 D…®par ekiar nguazim bar anevarazim t…®ghar izamin dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba apava, d…®par onganiba apava, egha amuiba ko pabar iti. Me kamagh…®n amua ikiav itima, Noa kurim…®n aven ghu.
\v 39 Me bizir me bativamin tam g…®fozir puvat…®, egha pura ikiav itima, aperiar ekiam otogha bar me avaragha me avigha ghue. Gumazibar Otarim izamin dughiam, uaghan kamagh…®rama otivam.
\v 40 Gumazir pumuning azenim…®n ik…®t…®, God tav inight…®, tav ikiam.
\v 41 Amizir pumuning bretbar amus…® flaua m…®rm…®r…®va ik…®t…®, God tav inight…®, tav ikiam.
\p 
\v 42 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, ia deragh gan ik…®. Ian Ekiam izamin dughiam, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®.
\v 43 Ia arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Gumazir manam, ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba d…®magarim…®n izava an d…®penim akarasava amima, a men dughiam g…®fogha, egha men arafa. Egha me ataghiz…® me an d…®penim akar…®zir puvat…®.
\v 44 Kamagh…®ra, ia uaghan aravagh ik…® gan. Guizbang…®ra, dughiar ia Gumazibar Otarim m…®zuaman koghamim, a dughiar kamram otogham.‚Äù
\s1 Ingangarir gumazir aghuim ko ingangarir gumazir kuram…®n akar is…®n zuim
\r (Luk 12:42-46)
\p 
\v 45 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazir manamra n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ikia derav…®ra uan ingangarim gami? An gumazir ekiam a damut…®, a ingangarir gumazir igharazibar ganam. Egh dughiar an gumazir ekiam ifongezim…®n, a dagheba is…® ingangarir gumazibar an…®ngam.
\v 46 Ingangarir gumazir kam ingara itima, an gumazir ekiam izava a batogha an ingangarir kam…®n garima, gumazir kam…®n navir averiam bar an dera.
\v 47 Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ingangarir gumazir kam…®n ekiam a damight…®ma, an an ingangarir gumazir mabar ekiam…®n ik…®va an biziba bar dar ganam.
\v 48 Eght…® ingangarir gumazir kam guizbang…®ra ikuvigh, egh kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham, ‚ÄòNan ekiam zuam…®ra izeghan kogham.‚Äô
\v 49 Egha uaghan a ko ingarir darazi m…®sogh…®va, d…®par onganibar am…®va, gumazir d…®par onganiba apiba ko ikiam.
\v 50 Eght…® an ekiam, dughiar an ingangarir gumazim a bagha garir puvat…®zim…®n, an otogham. A dughiar a fozir puvat…®zim…®n uamategham.
\v 51 Ingangarir gumazir kam…®n gumazir ekiam bar pazav, a damigh, ivezir bar kuram a dan…®ngam. Egh a is…®va ifavaribagh amir gumazibar tong…®n anet…®gham. Eght…® a danganir kam…®n ik…®va, arang atariba kuskugh ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\c 25
\s1 Iesus 10 plan guivir igiabar akar is…®n zuim m…®gei
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua Gumazibar Otarim ua izamin dughiam m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, guivir igiar 10 plan eghaghanim…®n m…®n mangam. Gumazir mam igiamra amuim…®n ikiasa izi. Ez…® guivir igiar maba uan lamba inigha tuavim…®n anapuasa zui.
\v 2 Men 5 pla, n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itima, 5 pla n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®.
\v 3 Egha 5 plan n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itir puvat…®ziba, uan lamba isa, da bagha borer taba inizir puvat…®.\f + \ft (25:3) Israel…®n adarasi oliv…®n borem isava, uan lambagh ruava dagh aboi, me en m…®n karasin lambagh aboir puvat…®.\f*
\v 4 Ez…® guivir igiar n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, uan lamba isa, egha uaghan borem itir m…®sevir maba sara, ini.
\v 5 Ez…®ma gumazir amuim…®n ikiamim zuam…®ra izezir puvat…®, ez…® guivir kaba pariam men azima, me akui.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEz…® d…®magarir ar…®zim…®n gumazir mam dia ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazir amuim…®n ikiamim, a rogh…®ra izi. Ia iz…®, e mang…®, tuavim…®n a batogh a ko izam.‚Äô
\v 7 Ez…® guivir igiar kaba d…®kavigha uan lambar k…®ri.
\v 8 Ez…® guivir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®ziba, n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itibar aza ghaze, ‚ÄòEn lamba mungasava ami. Kamagh…®n, ia borer taba e dan…®ng.‚Äô
\v 9 Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itir guiviba, me ikarvagha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòPuvat…®gham! Borem bar en tughat…®ghan kogham. Ia mang…®, borer amadir danganitam…®n uari bagh tabagh ivesegh.‚Äô
\v 10 Ez…® guivir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zir kaba ghuez…®ma, gumazir amuim…®n ikiamim oto. Ez…® guivir boreba itiba, a ko isar ekiam bagha d…®penim…®n aven ghue. Ez…® gumaziba tiam asara.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEz…® g…®n guivir ghueziba uamategha iza kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam! Ekiam, n…® iz…® e bagh tiam kuigh.‚Äô
\v 12 Ez…® a me ikarvagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, k…® ia g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äô‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Egha Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n, ia deraghav…®ra gan. Ian Ekiam, aruem ko dughiar ia fozir puvat…®zim…®n, an otogham.‚Äù
\s1 Ingangarir gumazibar dag…®aba inizim…®n, akar is…®n zuim
\r (Luk 19:11-27)
\p 
\v 14 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, gumazir mam nguibar saghon itim…®n mangasava ami mogh…®n. Gumazir kam uan ingangarir gumazibar diaz…® me izima, a uan biziba is…®, me danight…®ma, me a bagh dar ganam.
\v 15 A gumazibar araziba ko gavgavibar gara, dag…®aba tuiragha da isa me gan…®ngi. A mav 5,000 Kina a gan…®ga, mav 2,000 Kina a gan…®ga, mav 1,000 Kina a gan…®ngi. A kamagh…®n amigha ghu.
\v 16 A ghuz…®ma, gumazir 5,000 Kina inizim magh…®ra an ingara, 5,000 Kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.
\v 17 Ez…® gumazir 2,000 Kina inizim kamagh…®ra amua, uaghan 2,000 Kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.
\v 18 Ez…® gumazir 1,000 Kina inizim ghua mozim okoregha uan ekiam…®n dagiaba isava mozim gat…®gha egha da modo.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir ekiam dughiar ruarim…®n saghon ikegha uamategha ize. Egha uan ingangarir gumazibar ingangaribagh fofoghasa men dei.
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir 5,000 Kina inizim, 5,000 Kinan mam a dibagha, a inigha iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, n…® 5,000 Kina na gan…®ngi. N…® ge, k…® dag…®ar ingangarim gamua, 5,000 Kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúEz…® an ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazir aghuim, n…® ingangarir aghuim gami. N…® bizir doziba derav…®ra dar gari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, n…® ingangarir ekiabar ganasa, k…® ifonge. N…® iz…® uan ekiam…®n isam…®n aven ik…®, egh a ko bar akuegham.‚Äô
\v 22 Ez…® gumazir 2,000 Kina inizim iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, n…® 2,000 Kina na gan…®ngi. N…® ge, k…® dag…®ar ingangarim gamua, 2,000 Kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.‚Äô
\v 23 Ez…®ma an ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazir aghuim, n…® ingangarir aghuim gami. N…® bizir doziba derav…®ra dar gari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, n…® ingangarir ekiabar ganasa, k…® gifonge. N…® iz…®, uan ekiam…®n isam…®n aven ik…®, egh a ko bar akuegham.‚Äô
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir 1,000 Kina inizim uaghan izava, egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, k…® fo, n…® gumazir apangkuviba puvat…®zim. N…® gumazir igharaziba oparir azeniba, n…® uaghan daghebagh tui. Egha gumazir igharazim dagher ov…®ziba akurima, n…® uaghan pura dar aghafi.
\v 25 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® atiatingi, egha n…®n 1,000 Kina inigha ghua nguazir mozim gat…®gha egha da modo. N…®n dag…®abar kara.‚Äô
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄúEz…® an ekiam a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazir kuram! N…® gumazir am…®r…®zim. N…® na g…®fo, k…® gumazir igharaziba oparir azenibar daghebagh tui. Egha uaghan gumazir igharazim dagher ov…®ziba akurima, k…® uaghan pura dar aghavam.
\v 27 Ez…® n…® tizim bagha nan dag…®aba isava, dag…®abar ingaribagh amir d…®penitam gat…®zir puvat…®? Eght…® k…® ua iz…®va, uan dag…®aba iniva dag…®ar igharazitaba dagh is…®n da iniam.
\v 28 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia ada 1,000 Kina inigh, a is…®va 10,000 Kina itir gumazim dan…®ngigh.
\v 29 Arazim kamagh…®n iti, gumazir biziba itiba, k…® ua taba me dan…®ngam. Egh gumazir biziba puvat…®ziba, bizir vaghvazir me itiba k…® uaghan me dama, da inigham.
\v 30 Ez…® ingangarir gumazir bar kurar kam, ia a is…®, azenan itir danganir m…®tatem…®n anekunigh. Danganir kam…®n me puv…®ra tuang…®va arang, atariba kuskugh ikiam.‚Äô‚Äù
\s1 Gumazibar Otarim, gumazamiziba bar me is…® uan kotiam…®n aven men araziba tuis…®gham
\p 
\v 31 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazibar Otarim, Atrivim…®n m…®n otogh uamategh uan enselba bar me ko iz…®va, egh uan atrivir dabirabim daperagham.
\v 32 Eght…® nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar iz…®va an guam…®n uari akuvagham. Eght…® a me tuiragh, egh b…®zir pumuning damuam, mati sipsipbar garir gumazim sipsipba isava, b…®zir mam…®n me amaga, memeba b…®zir mam…®n me amadi.
\v 33 A sipsipba is…® agharir guvim…®n da amang, egh memeba is…® agharir ik…®riam…®n amangam.
\v 34 Egh Atrivim kamagh…®n agharir guvim…®n itir gumazamizibav k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa iz…®, nan Afeziam deragh ia damuasa ifonge! Ia iz…®va, danganir Afeziam fom…®ra ia bagha inabazim inigh, a nguazir kam otozir dughiam…®n a ia bagha danganir kam ak…®ri.
\v 35 K…® faragha m…®tiriam nan azima, ia dagheba na gan…®ngi; ez…® kuarim nan p…®rima, ia d…®pam na gan…®ngi; ez…® k…® nguibar igharazim…®n gumazim…®n m…®n itima, ia na inigha uan d…®penim…®n ghu;
\v 36 ez…® k…® bibiamra itima, ia korotiaba na gan…®ngi; ez…® k…® areima, ia nan akurvasi; ez…® k…® kalabus…®n itima ia iza nan gari. Kamagh…®n, ia aven iz…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 37 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazamizir aghuiba kamagh…®n a ikaragham, ‚ÄòEkiam, dughiar manamra, m…®tiriam n…®n azima, e dagheba n…® gan…®ngi? Ez…® dughiar manam, kuarim n…®n p…®rima, e d…®pam n…® gan…®ngi?
\v 38 Ez…® dughiar manam, n…® nguibar gumazir igharazim…®n m…®n itima, e n…® inigha uan d…®penibar ghue? Ez…® dughiar manam, n…® bibiamra itima, e korotiaba n…® gan…®ngi?
