\v 2 ‚ÄúIa fo, aruer pumuning g…®vaght…®ma, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isar ekiam otivam. Eght…® me Gumazibar Otarim is…®va apanibar agharim dat…®ght…®ma me a is…®va temer ighuvim gafugham.‚Äù
