\v 31 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa d…®magarir kam…®n na bativamin arazibar gan…®va ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir nan itim g…®vaght…®ma, ia na ategh aregham. Egh God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n otivam, ‚ÄòK…® sipsipbar garir gumazim m…®sueght…®ma, sipsipba tintinim…®n aregham.‚Äô
