\v 69 Ez…® Pita d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven an m…®riam…®n aperaghav iti. Ez…® ingangarir amizir mam an borogh…®ra iza ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uaghan Galilin gumazim Iesus ko ike.‚Äù
\v 70 Ez…® Pita uab…®n ghuara, ez…® me bar an garima, a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® m…®geir akar kam, k…® a g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 71 Egha g…®n ghua d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n itir tiar akar ekiam…®n ghua tughav iti. Ez…® ingangarir amizir igharazir mam iza an ganigha, gumazamizir an borogh…®n itiba kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam, a Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus ko ike.‚Äù
\v 72 Ez…® Pita ua uab…®n ghuaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, k…® God…®n damazim…®n ia m…®gei, k…® gumazir kam g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 73 Ez…® g…®n gumazir rogh…®ra tuivighav itiba iza kamagh…®n Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, n…® men mav…®ra, n…® men m…®rara m…®gei.‚Äù
\v 74 Ez…® Pita ua bagha pamten m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra k…® God…®n damazim…®n ia m…®gei, k…® gumazir kam g…®fozir puvat…®. K…® ifart…®ma, God na gas…®ghas…®gh.‚Äù A kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, tuarim magh…®ram ake.
\v 75 Ez…® Pita Iesus m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®am gin…®r…®, ‚ÄúTuarim t…®ghar akegham, eght…® n…® faraghv…®ra dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim, na m…®k…®m suam, n…® na g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù Egha Pita azenim…®n ghua bar puv…®rama azi.
\c 27
\s1 Me Iesus inigha Pailat bagha zui
\r (Mak 15:1 ko Luk 23:1-2 ko Jon 18:28-32)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…®ma am…®nim dutuz…®ma ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan gumazir dapaniba Iesus m…®sueght…®ma an aremighasa akabar k…®ri.
\v 2 Egha me g…®n senbar a ike, egha a inigha ghua Rom…®n gavman…®n gumazir ekiam Pailat…®n agharim gat…®.\f + \ft (27:2) Pailat Rom…®n gumazim. Rom…®n gavman Judan atrivim…®n anet…®. Judaba uari Iesus…®n m…®sueghan kogham. Rom…®n gavmanra gumazibav soght…®ma da ar…®m…®ghiram. Kamagh…®n Judaba Iesus inigha Pailat bagha ghu. Jon 18:31…®n gan.\f*
\s1 Judas…®n ovevem
\r (Aposel 1:18-19)
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Judas, gumazir Iesus isava apanibar agharim gat…®zim, a garima me paza Iesus gamuava a isa kotiam gar…®gha, egha ghaze, an aremegham. Ez…® Judas gara ghaze, k…® uab…® arazir kuram gami. Egha uan n…®ghn…®zibagh ira. Egha dag…®ar silvan 30 plan ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan gumazir dapaniba a gan…®ngiziba inigha ua me dan…®ngasa zui.
\v 4 Egha ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Gumazir k…® ian dafaribagh at…®zim, arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®. Ez…® ia purama a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.‚Äù Ez…® me an akam ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar en bizim puvat…®. N…®n bizimra.‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® Judas dag…®ar silvan kaba isa God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven da kunigha, egha ghua uab…® aguragha areme.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, dag…®ar silvan kaba inigha ghaze, ‚ÄúDag…®ar kaba, gumazir ghuzim…®n ivezim. E fo, Moses Osirizir Araziba ghaze, e da is…® ofa gamir dag…®aba sara dar at…®ghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 7 Egha me akam m…®suegha dag…®ar kaba inigha ghua M…®nebar Ingangarir Gumazim…®n Nguazim givese. Me ghaze, nguazir otevir kam, gumazir saghon izezibar afamin matmatiam…®n otogham.
\v 8 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguazir otevir kam, me ziar kam ‚ÄúGhuzir Nguazim‚Äù a gat…®. Ez…® me dughiar kam…®n ikegha iza, dat…®r…®gh…®n, nguazir kam me ziar kamra a gar…®gha iti.\f + \ft (27:8) M…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam ‚Äúme dughiar kam…®n ikegha iza, dat…®r…®gh…®n, nguazir kam me ziar kamra a gar…®gha iti,‚Äù an en dughiam m…®geir puvat…®. A Matyu akar kaba osirizir dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia m…®kemezir akaba guiz…®n otifi. A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe 30 plan silvan dag…®aba ini, kar Israelba gumazir kam givezasa at…®zir ivezim.
\v 10 Egha Ekiam na m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, me dag…®ar kabar M…®nebar Ingarir Gumazim…®n Nguazim givese.‚Äù
\s1 Pailat Iesus…®n azai, ‚ÄúN…® Judabar atrivim, o?‚Äù
\r (Mak 15:2-5 ko Luk 23:3-5 ko Jon 18:33-38)
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus ghua gavman…®n gumazir ekiam Pailat…®n damazim…®n tuz…®ma Pailat kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® Judabar atrivim, o?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra.‚Äù
\v 12 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba koma Judabar gumazir dapaniba akar av…®riba isava Iesus gasi. Ez…® a men akatam ikarvazir puvat…®.
\v 13 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pailat ua kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® me n…® gasir akar av…®rir kaba, n…® da barazi, o?‚Äù
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus Pailat…®n akatam ikarvazir puvat…®, ez…® Pailat n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami.
\s1 Pailat Iesus is…®va ter ighuvim gafughasa m…®gei
\r (Mak 15:6-15 ko Luk 23:13-25 ko Jon 18:38-19:16)
\p 
\v 15 Azeniba bar, Rom…®n gavman…®n gumazir ekiam arazir kam gami, a isar ekiar kam…®n dughiam…®n, a kalabus…®n itir gumazitam ateght…®, an azenim…®n mangam. Kalabus…®n itir gumazir manam gumazamiziba ifongezim, Pailat a is…® me bagh anemadagham.
\v 16 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n gumazir arazir kurabar ziam itir mam, a kalabus…®n iti. An ziam Barabas.
\v 17 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba izava uari akufa, ez…® Pailat kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúIa tina gifonge, eght…® k…® ia bagh anetaghragham. K…® Barabas ataghragham, o Iesus, me a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim,‚Äô k…® anetaghragham?‚Äù
\v 18 Pailat fo, men naviba pura Iesus…®n ikuvigha egha a inigha kotiam…®n ize, egha kamagh…®n men azai.
\p 
\v 19 Egha Pailat uaghan kotiabagh amir dabirabim…®n aperaghav itima, an amuim a bagha akam amaga m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® d…®mangan irebam…®n arazir kuraba puvat…®zir gumazir kam…®n gani, egha bar oseme. Kamagh…®n, n…® arazitam a damuan mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba koma Judabar gumazir dapaniba, gumazamizir av…®rim…®n navibagh iniva ghaze, me Pailat…®n azangt…®, a Barabas ategh, egh Iesus m…®sueght…®, an aremegham.
\v 21 Ez…® gavman…®n gumazir ekiam ua men aza ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazir manam gifonge, eght…® k…® anetaghragham?‚Äù Ez…® gumazamiziba dia ghaze, ‚ÄúE Barabas gifonge.‚Äù
\v 22 Ez…® Pailat men azai, ‚ÄúEght…®, Iesus me a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄòGod Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim,‚Äô k…® manmagh…®n a damuam?‚Äù Ez…® me bar dia ghaze, ‚ÄúA is…® ter ighuvim gafugh!‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® Pailat men azai, ‚ÄúManmagh su? An arazir kurar manam gami?‚Äù Ez…® me bar pamten dia ghaze, ‚ÄúA is…® ter ighuvim gafugh!‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Pailat dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, me an akatam bareghan kogham. Egha a gari, m…®dorozir ekiam otivasava ami. Egha d…®pam inigha men damazibar uan dafariba rua ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam…®n ovevem, a nan os…®mt…®zim puvat…®. Kar ian bizimra.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® gumazamiziba a ikarvagha ghaze, ‚ÄúAn ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim mar en ik…®, egh en boribar ik…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pailat me bagha Barabas ataki. Egha m…®dorozir gumazibav geima, me benibar Iesus ifozoroke. Egha g…®n a isa m…®dorozir gumazibar agharim gat…®, eght…® me a is…® ter ighuvim gafugham.
\s1 M…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus d…®pofi
\r (Mak 15:16-20 ko Jon 19:2-3)
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® gavman…®n gumazir ekiam…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus inigha, gavman…®n d…®penir ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n aven ghuez…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba bar uari akuvaz…®, Iesus men tong…®n tughav iti.
\v 28 Egha me an korotiaba suegha, korotiar aghevir ruarir mam isa a garu.
\v 29 Egha me benir d…®konibar atrivibar amianim…®n m…®n an ingari, egha a isa an dapanim garu. Egha difizir mam isava an agharir guvim gat…®z…®, an an suira. Ez…® me tevibar ap…®ra a d…®pova ghaze, ‚ÄúJudabar Atrivim, n…®rara atrivir ekiam!‚Äù\f + \ft (27:29) M…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus d…®povasa atrivim…®n m…®n an adiarim gami. Dughiar kam…®n, atriviba kamagh…®n adiaribagh ami, me korotiar agheviba aghuava atrivibar dapanir asuaba azui. Egha me atrivibar dabirabibagh apia uaghan uan difizibar suisi.\f*
\v 30 Egha me a giparava a suirazir difizim inigha an dapanim m…®sosi.
\v 31 Me arazir kabar a gamua a d…®povegha g…®vagha, a da korotiar me a agaghuiziba suegha, ua ananaba agaghui. Egha a isa ter ighuvim a gafughasa an akua zui.
\s1 Me Iesus isa ter ighuvim gafu
\r (Mak 15:21-32 ko Luk 23:26-43 ko Jon 19:17-27)
\p 
\v 32 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus inigha, nguibar ekiam ategha ghua, me Sairinian nguibam…®n gumazir mam bato. An ziam Saimon. Egha me a gakaghorima, a Iesus…®n ter ighuvim gisaghpu.
\v 33 Egha me ghua danganir mam…®n ziam Golgata, me an otifi. (Danganir kam…®n ziam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n, Dapanir Agharir Danganim.)
\v 34 Ez…® me danganir kam…®n Iesus damasa me d…®par an…®nganir mam wain sara a veregha, egha mam inigha Iesus gan…®di. Ez…® a muziarir mam inigha anetaki.
\v 35 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus isava ter ighuvim gafu. Egha an korotiaba tuiragh uari dan…®ngasa satu gikararai.
\v 36 Egha danganir kam…®n apiagha anesavsuisi.
\v 37 Me an dapanim gis…®n, an kotim gamizir m…®g…®r…®g…®am osiri. Me osirizir akam ghaze, ‚ÄúKar Iesus, a Judabar Atrivim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 38 Me gumazir ok…®ava m…®dorozibagh amizir pumuning, Iesus…®n borogh…®n uaghan aning agura. Me mav isa Iesus…®n agharir guvim…®n itir ter ighuvim gafu, egha mav isa agharir ik…®riam…®n itir ter ighuvim gafu.
\v 39 Ez…® gumazamiziba mang…® izegh gamua Iesus d…®pova, uan dapaniba roava a d…®pova ghaze,
\v 40 ‚ÄúN…®, gumazir God…®n D…®penim akarigh aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n uam an ingarasa m…®kemezim! N…® uab…® uab…®n akuragh! Egh n…® guizbang…®ra God…®n Otarim, n…® ter ighuvim ategh izighir…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 41 Ez…® kamagh…®ra ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Judabar gumazir dapaniba izava a d…®pova ghaze,
\v 42 ‚ÄúA gumazir igharazibar akurvasi, egha uab…® uab…®n akurvaghan ibura. A Israelbar Atrivim, kamagh…®n a ter ighuvim ategh izighir…®, eght…® e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam.
\v 43 A n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia, egha ghaze, k…® God…®n Otarim. Eght…® God guizbang…®ra ifongiam an ik…®va, dat…®r…®gh…®n an akuraght…®, e ganika!‚Äù
\v 44 Ez…® kamagh…®ra ok…®mak…®ar gumazir Iesus borogh…®n ter ighuvimning…®n guraghav itimning, uaghan akar kabar a d…®pova a m…®gei.
\s1 Iesus areme
\r (Mak 15:33-41 ko Luk 23:44-49 ko Jon 19:28-30)
\p 
\v 45 Ez…® aruem iza pazaghar torim gatima, m…®tatem nguazim…®n itir nguibaba bar da avaragha ghua, dughiam ghua 3 klogh…®n guarat…®zim…®n tu.
\v 46 Egha dughiam 3 klogh…®n borogh…®ra izima, Iesus pamten kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúEli, Eli, lama sabaktani?‚Äù Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúNan God, nan God, n…® tizim bagha na ataki?‚Äù
\p 
\v 47 Ez…® gumazir an borogh…®n tuivighav itiba akar kam baregha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam ti Elaijan dei.‚Äù
\p 
\v 48 Egha men mav zuam…®ra ivegha ghua d…®pam…®n suizir bizir mam inigha wain…®n afangt…®zim isava a gat…®. Ez…® wain a giz…®vaz…®ma, an a isa aghorir mam gat…®. Egha aneremasa a isa Iesus…®n amadi.
\v 49 Ez…® marazi m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tegh, e ganika, Elaija ti iz…®va an akuragham, o puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 50 Ez…® Iesus ua pamtem diagha uan duam suegha areme.
\p 
\v 51 Ez…® dughiar kamra, God…®n D…®penim…®n guraghav itir inir ekiam p…®n ikegha tong…®ra bigha, ghuaghira v…®n otogha akuar pumuning ir…®. Ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zim otoz…®ma, dag…®ar ekiaba b…®aghire.
\v 52 Ez…® matmatiaba kuagh…®rima, God…®n gumazamizir av…®rir ariaghreziba ua dikavigha,
\v 53 egha uan moziba ataki. Eght…® g…®n Iesus d…®kavight…®ma, me nguibar ekiam Jerusalem…®n aven mangam. Eght…® av…®rir ekiam men ganam.
\v 54 Ez…® 100 plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir ekiar mam, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me garima m…®k…®mk…®zim otoz…®ma, arazir kaba otivima, me bar puv…®ram atiati. Egha me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, gumazir kam God…®n Otarimra.‚Äù
\v 55 Amizir av…®riba uaghan izegha iti. Me Galilin Distrigh ategha Iesus…®n akurvaghasa an g…®n ize. Amizir kaba mong saghon tuivighav ikia gari.
\v 56 Men tong…®n, Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria, ko Jems ko Josep…®n amebam Maria, ko Sebedin otarimning…®n amebam.
\s1 Me Iesus…®n kuam isa, dag…®ar torim gat…®
\r (Mak 15:42-47 ko Luk 23:50-55 ko Jon 19:38-42)
\p 
\v 57 Ez…® am…®nim p…®rasava amima, Arimatean nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam izi. An ziam Josep, a dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazim.
\v 58 A uaghan Iesus…®n suren gumazir mam. Egha Pailat bagha ghua Iesus…®n kuam iniasa an azai. Ez…® Pailat m…®dorozir gumazibav kemez…®, me Iesus…®n kuam isa Josep gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 59 Ez…® Josep a inigha inir ghurghurir aghuir mam…®n a r…®ki.
\v 60 Egha an kuam inigha ghua, a isa ua bagha okorezir mozir igiam gat…®. Egha Josep dag…®ar ekiar mam poghpuegha ghua mozim…®n akam gasaragha, anep…®ri. A kamagh…®n amigha ghu.
\p 
\v 61 Ez…® Maria, Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim, koma Marian igharazir mam, aning mozim…®n borogh…®n aperaghav ikia, an gara iti.
\s1 M…®dorozir gumaziba mozim…®n gara iti
\p 
\v 62 Ez…® Sabat bagha bizibar k…®rir dughiam g…®fa, ez…® an g…®n izir dughiam…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Farisiba Pailat bagha ghue.\f + \ft (27:62) Kar Sabat…®n dughiamra.\f*
\v 63 Me ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, e gumazir ifavarir kam ikia m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam gin…®r…®. A ghaze, ‚ÄòAruer pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…®ma k…® ua d…®kavam.‚Äô
\v 64 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® m…®kemeght…®, me mozim aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n deragh anep…®righ. Puvat…®ght…®ma, an suren gumaziba an kuam okemegh, egh gumazamizibav k…®m suam, a ua d…®kafi. Eght…® an ifavarir akar kam, a faragha amizir ifavarir akam gafiragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 65 Ez…® Pailat kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh me m…®k…®mt…®ma, me mozim…®n gan ik…®. Egh ia mang…®, mozim ap…®rasa ifongez…® mogh…®n, ia damuva, egh bar anep…®righ.‚Äù
\v 66 Ez…® me ghua mozim ap…®ri. Egha ifevim…®n m…®n bizir mam mozir akam gighufa, egh me fogham, gumazitam dag…®am g…®raghan kogham. Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba ataghiz…®ma, me mozim…®n gara iti.
\c 28
\s1 Iesus ua d…®kafi
\r (Mak 16:1-10 ko Luk 24:1-10 ko Jon 20:1-18)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Sabat…®n dughiam g…®vaz…®ma, Sanden bar m…®zaraghara aruem anadima, Makdalan amizim Maria, ko Marian igharazim uamategha mozim…®n ganasa izi.\f + \ft (28:1) Wikbar dughiar faragh zuim, a Sandera.\f*
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zir ekiam magh…®ram oto. Ez…® God…®n ensel…®n mam God…®n Nguibam ategha izagh…®ra, dag…®ar Iesus…®n mozir akam…®n itim poghpuegha, mong mozir ap…®nim…®n ghugha, egha dag…®am gaperaghav iti.
\v 3 Ensel…®n ganganim, mati on…®marim taghtazi mogh…®n gari, ez…® an korotiaba bar ghurghuri.
\v 4 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba an atiatia, in…®gha egha aremez…® mogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n amizir kamning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua atiatingan mark…®. K…® fo, gua me ter ighuvim gafuzir gumazim Iesus bagha gara izi.
\v 6 A kagh itir puvat…®. A faragha m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ua d…®kavigha g…®fa. Gua iz…®, a kagh ir…®ghav ikezir danganim…®n gan.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúEgh gua zuam…®ra mang…®, an suren gumazibav k…®m suam, a ua d…®kavigha g…®vagha mozim…®n itir puvat…®. Ia oragh. A ia bativasa faragha Galilin zui. Ia mang…®, munagh an ganam. K…® bizir kam…®n gun gua m…®k…®masa ize.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® amizimning puv atiatiava, egha uaghan bar akonge. Egha zuam…®ra mozim ategha, ivegha Iesus…®n suren gumazibav k…®masa zui.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Iesus tuavim…®n magh…®ra aning bato, egha ghaze, ‚ÄúM…®zarazir aghuim.‚Äù Ez…® aning an borogh…®n ghua, an dagarimning suiragha an ziam fe.
\v 10 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua atiatingan mark…®. Gua mang…®, nan aveghbuabav k…®m suam, me Galilin mang…® egh munagh nan ganam.‚Äù
\s1 M…®dorozir gumaziba m…®kemezir akam
\p 
\v 11 Amizimning Iesus…®n suren gumaziba bagha zuima, m…®dorozir gumazir mozim…®n gara ikeziba Jerusalem…®n aven ghue. Egha otivizir araziba bar dar gun ofa gamir gumazir ekiabav keme.
\v 12 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, Judabar gumazir dapaniba inigha akar mam ak…®ri. Egha dag…®ar av…®ribar m…®dorozir gumazibagh ivezegha,
\v 13 egha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, e akuima, an suren gumaziba d…®magarim…®n izava an kuam okemegha ghue.
